\id JER
\h Irmiya 
\toc1 Irmiya 
\toc2 Irmiya 
\toc3 Irm. 
\mt1 Irmiya  
\c 1
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Irmiya  
\m
\v 1 Awařen n Irmiya, mmis n Ḥilqiya, zeg ikehhanen nni \add iǧan\add* di Ɛanatut, di temmurt n Binyamin,  
\v 2 wenni ɣar dd-yusa wawař n SIDI deg wussan n ujeǧid Yuciya, mmis n Amun, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg useggʷas wiss třeṭṭac n řeḥkamet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt 2 Ij. 21:26; 22:1-23; 2 Im. 34:1-30\x*  
\v 3 Yusa-dd \add wawař n SIDI\add* ɣares uřa deg wussan n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ař mani ikemmeř useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n Ṣidqiya, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ařami dd-iwyen Urcalim ɣar lmenfa deg uyur wiss xemsa. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Ij. 23:34; 24:17; 25:8; 2 Im. 36:4, 10-23; Irm. 52:1-30\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 5 “Qbeř ma ggiɣ cek d aseymi deg uɛeddis \add n yemmac\add*, tuɣa ssneɣ cek, u qbeř ma dd-teffɣed zi řemřawet, aqa ssqeddseɣ cek. Necc areccḥeɣ cek d anabi i řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Gal. 1:15\x*  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ: “Ah, Sidi inu, SIDI! Xzar, necc war zemmareɣ ad ssiwřeɣ, necc \add ɛad\add* d aḥudri.” \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt Uf. 3; 4; 6:11, 29\x*  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* SIDI yarra-dd xafi: “War qqar: ‘Necc \add ɛad\add* d aḥudri!’, maɣar mani ma cek i ɣa ssekkeɣ ad din traḥed, u marra min d ac ɣa umureɣ, ad \add t\add* tinid.  
\v 8 War zzaysen tteggʷed, maɣar Necc akidek, ḥima ad cek fekkeɣ!”, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Aɛwd. 31:6, 8; Yac. 1:5; Ḥiz. 3:9\x*  
\v 9 Isswiẓẓeḍ SIDI afus nnes, iḥada aqemmum inu uca inna ayi SIDI: “Xzar, Necc ggiɣ ac awařen inu deg uqemmum nnec.\x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Ica. 6:6, 7; Irm. 5:14\x*  
\v 10 Xzar, deg wass-a ad cek areccḥeɣ x řegnus u x tgeldawin, ḥima ad tqeřɛed u ad thedmed, ḥima ad tareddǧed u ḥima ad tɣeḍřed, ḥima ad tebnid u ad teẓẓud.” \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Irm. 18:7; 2 Kur. 10:4, 5\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna: “Min tᵉttwařid, Irmiya?” Necc arriɣ-dd: “Necc ttwařiɣ ict n tseṭṭa n ǧewz.”  
\v 12 Inna ayi SIDI: “Cek teẓrid nican, maɣar Necc ttɛesseɣ x wawař inu ḥima ad t ggeɣ.”   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI i twařa wiss tnayen, inna: “Min tᵉttwařid?” Necc arriɣ-dd: “Ttwařiɣ taydart ittnennan, abuḍ nnes imeyyeř \add ɣar da\add* zi ccamal.”  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* inna ayi SIDI: “Zi ccamal i dd ɣa ihwa řɣar\add -a\add* x marra imezdaɣ n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Irm. 4:6\x*  
\v 15 Maɣar, xzar, Necc ad řaɣiɣ x marra řaǧat n tgeldiwin n camal, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, uca nitni ad dd-asen uca ad ssbedden řekrasi nsen ɣar wadaf n tewwura n Urcalim u ḍidd i marra řeḥyuḍ nnes i d as dd-innḍen u ḍidd i marra tineddam n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Irm. 5:15; 6:22; 10:22; 52:4, 5\x*  
\v 16 Necc ad xasen neṭqeɣ marra řeḥkamat inu, x marra tuɛeffna nsen: aqa semḥen dayi uca bexxaren i irebbiten nneɣni uca sejden i min ggin ifassen nsen.  
\v 17 Cek \add xenni\add*, ḥezzem tijɛinnatin nnec uca kkar, barreḥ asen marra min d ac ɣa umureɣ. War ttnexřiɛ zzaysen niɣ ad cek ssnexřɛeɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen.  
\v 18 Xzar, Necc ad cek ggeɣ d tandint ifaryen, d ijj n upilar n wuzzař d řeḥyuḍ n nnḥas ḍidd i marra tammurt: ḍidd i ijeǧiden n Yahuda, ḍidd i řḥukkam nnes, ḍidd i ikehhanen nnes u ḍidd i řgens n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 1:18 \xt Irm. 6:27; 15:20\x*  
\v 19 Nitni ad kidek mmenɣen, \add maca\add* war cek arennyen, maɣar Necc akidek, ḥima ad cek fekkeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Tasřit iɣḍaren  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “Uyur, barreḥ deg umezzuɣ n Urcalim, ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Necc ttxarraṣeɣ dayem, di tmexsiwt icewwaren n temẓi nnem, x tayri n wussan n tnexḍabt nnem, umi dd ayi dd-teḍfared di řexřa, di temmurt tamessucit.  
\v 3 Israil tuɣa d amqeddes i SIDI, tamezwarut n ṣṣabet nnes. Marra wi zzayes iccen, iddakkwař dayes řɛib, iwḍa-dd xasen řɣar, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 4 “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, kenniw zi taddart n Yaɛqub, d marra řaǧat n taddart n Israil.  
\v 5 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Man řɣecc nni dayi ufin řejdud nwem ařami xafi ḥeyyḍen uca ḍfaren \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen uca dewřen \add simant nsen\add* di řbaṭeř, \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Mixa 6:3, 4\x*  
\v 6 war sseqsin: Mani iǧa SIDI, wenni d aneɣ dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra, wenni d aneɣ issecnen abrid di řexřa, x ict n temmurt n řexřa d ixendraq, x ict n temmurt n řaẓaɣ d tiři n řmewt, x ict n temmurt war xas iɛdu uřa d ijj u war dayes izdiɣ uřa d ijj n bnadem?  
\v 7 Necc iwyeɣ kenniw ɣar ict n temmurt isseɣmayen ḥima ad zzayes teccem řɣiǧet d řxar. \add Maca\add* umi \add din\add* tiwḍem, tessxemjem tammurt inu u tarrim tasɣart inu d jjɛifect.  
\v 8 Ikehhanen war sseqsin: Mani iǧa SIDI?, uca inni tuɣa iḥeṭṭan Ccariɛa war d ayi ssinen u imeksawen ɛeddun-dd xafi u inabiyyen ttnabben s Baɛal uca ḍfaren min war ineffɛen. \f ◼ \fr 2:8 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Rum. 2:20\x*  
\v 9 S uya Necc ad arniɣ ad mcubbceɣ akidwem, uřa ak-d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nwem ad mcubbceɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “Ẓwam ɣar tegzirin n ayt n Kittim, aqa sekkem \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar Qidar, beytem uca xzarem mliḥ, ma imsar ɛemmarṣ am man aya! \f ◼ \fr 2:10 \ft \+fk Kittim\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘Qubrus’. \fk Qidar\ft  - ict n jjihet n jjwayeh n temmurt n Weɛraben.\f*  
\v 11 Ma ɛemmarṣ ibeddeř ca n řgens irebbiten nnes, \add waxxa\add* war ǧin d irebbiten? Řgens inu maca iwca řɛezz nnes deg wemcan n min war ineffɛen. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Izhd. 106:20\x*  
\v 12 Iřim d ignawen x man aya, \add kenniw a\add* ijenwan, ggʷedem, nxeřɛem ař ṭṭarf, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Aɛwd. 32:1; Ica. 1:2\x*  
\v 13 Maɣar řgens inu igga tnayen n řeɛyub: Necc, Řɛunṣar n waman iddaren, aqa semḥen dayes maḥend ad ɣzan anuten i yixef nsen, anuten s tazzect i ixwan zeg waman.\x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Izři 4:15; Irm. 17:13\x*  
\v 14 Ma Israil d ismeɣ niɣ d ijj ittwaru \add d ismeɣ\add* di taddart? Mayemmi idweř i zzardet \add xenni\add*?  
\v 15 Ssbuɛruten xas wayraden imeẓyanen, ggin ad sřen i tmijja nsen. Nitni arrin tammurt nnes d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ tineddam nnes ttwasscemḍent ařami war iqqim izeddeɣ daysent uřa d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Ica. 5:29; Irm. 4:7\x*  
\v 16 Ɛad ḥeffen ayt n Nuf d Taḥfanis aceqquf n uzeǧif nnec.  
\v 17 Ma war teggid ca manawya i yixef nnem, \add minzi\add* cem tsemḥed di SIDI, AREBBI nnem am Netta indeḥ i cem deg webrid?”   
\b  
\m
\v 18 “Řexxu, min din jar am d jar webrid n Miṣra maḥend ad teswed \add din\add* aman zi Cixur, \add zeg iɣzar d abarcan\add*? Min jar am d jar webrid n Accur ařami \add din\add* i ɣa teswed aman n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*? \f ◼ \fr 2:18 \ft \+fk Cixur\ft  - wanita d isem nneɣni i yeɣzar n ‘Nil’. Cixur ixs ad yini ‘abarcan’, minzi iɣzar n Nil idweř d abarcan zi ssibbet n ubeǧaɛ d ubaryuḍ i dayes iǧan.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:18 \xt Ica. 31:1\x*  
\v 19 Tuɛeffna nnem ad cek tarebba u ibriden n uweddar nnem ad cem ɛaqben. Ssen u xzar, mammec war iḥři u mecḥař yarzeg aqa tsemḥed di SIDI, AREBBI nnem, u war zzayi tᵉtteggʷeded, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat.” \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Ica. 3:9; Ḥuc. 5:5\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 “Aṭṭas zeg wami tarẓid \add a\add*zayřu nnem, tcarrged iceddiyyen nnem. Cem tennid: ‘War xseɣ ad ac sexxareɣ!’ Minzi x kuř řgeɛɛdet yuɛřan u sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt tuḍared am temɣart n farq-ccɣeř. \f ◼ \fr 2:20 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  
\v 21 Necc maca tuɣa ẓẓuɣ cem d tazayart taḥurrit, d zzariɛet icnan aṭṭas. Mammec tdewřed ɣar tseḍwin n tzayart n řexřa tabarranect? \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt Uf. 15:17; Izhd. 44:3; 80:9\x*  
\v 22 Waxxa tessirded ixef nnem s llixiyya uca tarnid asray s ṣṣabun, \add ɛad\add* ad teqqim řmuɛṣiyyet nnem zzat i wudem inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Ayub 9:30\x*   
\m
\v 23 “Mammec tzemmared ad tinid: ‘Necc war ttwassxemjeɣ ca, necc war ḍfareɣ ca ‘Ibaɛlen!’ Xzar ɣar webrid nnem di teɣzurt, ɛqeř min teggid, cem d tařɣemt tefsus tᵉttazzeř, tenni ittemxarwaḍen deg ibriden nnes!  
\v 24 Aqa-tt d taɣyuč n řexra, innumen di řexřa, tenni ittcemman arriḥ deg wenẓar nnes umi tḥaj. Wi tt i ɣa issbedden di nnecwet nnes? Qaɛ wi tt yarezzun war iḥdij ad issiḥeř ixef nnes, ad tt yaf deg uyur \add n nnecwet\add* nnes.  
\v 25 Ḥḍa war ittiři uḍar nnem břa tisiřa uřa tmijja nnem war tᵉttiẓeɣ s ufadi! Cem maca teqqared: ‘War xas nessiwiř, ɛemmarṣ! Maɣar necc ɛecqeɣ di midden, xseɣ ad uyureɣ awarni asen!’”   
\m
\v 26 “Am uxewwan inneḥṣeř iseḍḥa, ammu i ɣa seḍḥan inni n taddart n Israil, nitni d ijeǧiden nsen d řḥukkam nsen d ikehhanen nsen d inabiyyen nsen.  
\v 27 Nitni qqaren i ukeccuḍ: ‘Cek d baba!’, u i weẓru: Cek tejjid ayi-dd!, maɣar nitni wcin ayi s weɛrur, war iǧi s uɣembub, \add maca\add* di řeḥṣaret nsen qqaren: ‘Kkar, senjem aneɣ!’  
\v 28 Mani ǧan řexxu irebbiten nnec, inni teggid i yixef nnec? Ejj i-ten ad dd-kkaren, mařa zemmaren ad cek fekken ɣar řweqt n řeḥṣaret nnec, maɣar irebbiten nwem am lɛadad n tneddam nnec, \add a\add* Yahuda!” \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Ica. 2:8; Irm. 11:13\x*   
\m
\v 29 “Mayemmi akidi temcubbucem kenniw? Kenniw marra tᵉttɛeddam xafi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 30 X baṭeř i wtiɣ iḥenjiren nwem, war jjin ixef nsen ad areyyḍen. Ssif nwem icca inabiyyen nwem am wayrad iɣarrṣen. \x ◘ \xo 2:30 \xt Ica. 1:5; Irm. 5:3\x*  
\v 31 \add A\add* kenniw, \add a\add* jjiř \add n yiḍa\add*, ḥḍam awař n SIDI. Ma tuɣa ayi d řexřa i Israil, niɣ d tammurt n taǧest d tabarcant? Mayemmi \add xenni\add* iqqar řgens inu: ‘Aqa neccin nennufṣeř zzayek, war i dd ɣarek neddikkwiř ɛad’? \x ◘ \xo 2:31 \xt Mt. 23:26-39\x*  
\v 32 Ma ad tᵉttu teɛzarect talwizt nnes niɣ \add ad tᵉttu\add* tesřit taḥezzamt nnes \add izewwqen\add*? Waxxa amenni i d ayi ittu řgens inu aṭṭas n wussan břa řeḥsab. \x ◘ \xo 2:32 \xt Irm. 3:21\x*  
\v 33 Mecḥař tessned mliḥ ad tarzud abrid n tayri? S uya i tessřemded di ibriden nnem timesřayin tiɛeffanin i yixef nnem.  
\v 34 Uřa deg ubeḥrur n warruḍ nnem ufin idammen n řeɛmurat iḍeɛfen izdigen, inni war temniɛed umi ucaren \add tudrin\add*, \add wah,\add* zi ssibbet n marra man aya \add aqa imsar\add*. \f ◼ \fr 2:34 \ft \+fk zi ssibbet n marra man aya\ft  - idammen war uzziřen ca umi ṭṭfen iceffaren niɣ ixewwanen di Israil uca nɣin ten, maca idammen uzzřen umi nɣin inabiyyen n SIDI (xzar 2 Ij. 21:16 u 2 Ij. 24:4). Tuɣa ayt n Israil d ixewwanen d idarɣařen di řmeɛna arruḥani umi ɛebden laṣnam ifennan, war iǧi AREBBI i iǧan i řebda.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:34 \xt Amb. 11:9\x*  
\v 35 Uca \add ɛad\add* teqqared: ‘S tidett, necc d tamezdagt, aqa aɣḍab nnes iḥeyyed xafi!’ Xzar, Necc ad kim carrɛeɣ, minzi teqqared: ‘Necc war ggiɣ ddnub!’  
\v 36 Mayemmi tᵉtteggʷjed aṭṭas uca tbeddřed \add řebda\add* abrid nnem? Uřa \add tammurt n\add* Miṣra ad cem tecmet, am mammec i d am tecmet Accur.  
\v 37 Uřa ssenni ad teggʷejed s ifassen nnem x uzeǧif, maɣar SIDI inḍar marra inni x tᵉttecřed, ařami war ittiři aya uřa akidsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Tařaɣit i weɛqab ɣar SIDI AREBBI  
\m
\v 1 “Qqaren: ‘Xzar, ijj n weryaz iǧef i temɣart nnes u nettat tuyur xas, tedweř d tamɣart n ijj nneɣni, ma iɛeddeř ad ɣares dd-iɛqeb \add xenni\add*? Ma war tefsed temmurt nni aṭṭas?’ Cem maca tegged ffarq-cɣeř nnem ak-d ijj n ubarru n imeddukkař, ma \add xenni\add* tzemmared ad ɣari dd-tɛeqbed, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Aɛwd. 24:1-4\x*  
\v 2 Sgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnem di řegɛudi \add i xef wehhben tiɣarṣa\add*, xzar, mani war cem xarḍen? Aqa tuyured ad teqqimed deg ibriden marra am yijj n Weɛrab di řexřa. \add Ammu\add* i tessfesded tammurt s farq-ccɣeř nnem d řɣar nnem.  
\v 3 S uya ittwamneɛ wenẓar uca war dd-iwti wenẓar ajuri. \add Maca\add* cem tuɣa ɣarem tanyart teqjar n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, war texsed ad tseḍḥid.  
\v 4 Ma war tebdid mɣir i cwayt n řweqt waha ad ayi tᵉttřaɣad ‘Baba! Cek d Ameddukkeř inu zi temẓi inu!  
\v 5 Ma \add xenni\add* ad iqqim weɣḍab nnes ittbedda i řebda? Ma Netta ad t iḥḍa i řebda?’ Xzar, \add ammu i\add* teqqared, \add am\add* tᵉttegged mařa timesřayin nni tiɛeffanin u \add tᵉttxarrṣed\add* aqa aya iɛeddeř \add ad ittwagg.\add*”   
\m
\v 6 SIDI inna ayi deg wussan n Yuciya: “Ma teẓrid min tegga \add temɣart\add* Israil ikfaren? Nettat tgeɛɛed kuř adrar yuɛřan, tezzeř sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt uca tegga din am temɣart n farq-ccɣeř! \f ◼ \fr 3:6 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Irm. 2:20\x*  
\v 7 Awarni řami tegga aya, nniɣ: \bd ‘Ad dd-tedweř ɣari!’\bd*, maca nettat war dd-tedwiř ca. \add Xenni\add* teẓri aya učmas iɣeddaren Yahuda.  
\v 8 Ẓriɣ, umi d as ǧfeɣ zi ssibbet n marra min zi tezna \add temɣart\add* Israil ikfaren u wciɣ as tabrat n waǧaf, aqa aya war issnexřiɛ učmas taɣeddart Yahuda, \add maca\add* nettat tuyur, tessefsed ixef nnes uřa d nettat s farq-ccɣeř nnes.  
\v 9 S farq-ccɣeř nnes ihewnen, tᵉttwassefsed temmurt, \add maɣar\add* nettat tezna s weẓru d ukeccuḍ.  
\v 10 Di marra aya war dd ɣari teɛqib učmas Yahuda taɣeddart s marra uř nnes, \add maca\add* tessniɛmiř waha, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 11 \add S uya\add* inna ayi SIDI: “\add Tawečmat\add* Israil ikfaren, aqa tarra ixef nnes tban-dd tsegged ktar x \add učmas\add* Yahuda taɣeddart.  
\v 12 Uyur, řaɣa awařen-a ɣar ccamal, ini: \bd ‘Dweř-dd, \+bdit a cem\+bdit* \+bdit temɣart\+bdit* Israil ikfaren!’\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Aɣembub inu war ittbarcin, maɣar Necc ccureɣ s tmexsiwt icewwaren, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Necc war ttiřiɣ ttfugmeɣ řebda. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Izhd. 86:15; 103:8, 9; 145:17\x*  
\v 13 Maca nɛem s řmuɛṣiyyet nnem, aqa tɛeddid x SIDI, AREBBI nnem, uca teffɣed zeg webrid ɣar marra iɣezdisen ɣar ibarraniyyen, sadu kuř tacejjart tazizawt, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim ca ɣar tmijja inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 14 \bd “Dewřem-dd, a tarrawt ikfaren!\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar Necc d aryaz nwem, Necc ad kenniw qebřeɣ \add ɛawed\add*, ijj zeg ict n tendint u tnayen zeg ijj n řaǧ, u Necc ad kenniw awyeɣ ɣar Ṣihyun.  
\v 15 Necc ad awem wceɣ imeksawen i ixs wuř inu, inni kenniw i ɣa yarewsen s tussna d řeɛqeř. \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Irm. 23:4; Ḥiz. 34:23; Afa. 4:11\x*  
\v 16 Xmi ɣa temmarenyem deg wussan nni, ad dd-tawyem řɣiǧet di temmurt, iqqar SIDI, ad tafed war qqaren \add ɛad\add* ‘Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI!’ War dd asen tᵉttaři ɣar řbař, war tt ttidaren, war tt feqqden \add ɛad\add* uca war tt ttsennaɛen.”   
\m
\v 17 “Di řweqt nni ad inin i Urcalim ‘Řkursi n SIDI!’, uca marra řegnus ad ɣares dd-nnyarwen di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem n SIDI, ɣar Urcalim, uca war ttɣimin gguren ca ɛlaḥsab řeqsaḥet n wuř nsen aɛeffan.  
\v 18 Deg wussan nni ad tuyur taddart n Yahuda ɣar taddart n Israil uca nitenti ad ffɣent munent zi temmurt n ccamal ɣar temmurt nni wciɣ d tasɣart i řejdud nwem.”   
\m
\v 19 “Necc tuɣa nniɣ: ‘Mammec zemmareɣ ad kenniw arreɣ d iḥenjiren inu uca ad awem wceɣ tammurt iɛizzen, tasɣart \add nni iǧan d\add* talwizt n řɛeskarat n řegnus?’ Necc nniɣ: ‘Kenniw ad ɣari řaɣan: Baba! uca war xafi tᵉttḥeyyidem \add ɛad\add*!’  
\v 20 S tidett, am temɣart teɣdar ameddukkeř nnes, ammu uřa d kenniw tiɣdarem ayi, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Ittwaseř ijj n řḥess x tewririn iqeccaren, anixses d tutra n ayt n Israil, minzi nitni uyuren ibriden farɣen uca SIDI, AREBBI nsen, ttun t.   
\b  
\m
\v 22 \bd “Dewřem-dd, a tarrawt ikfaren!\bd*, Necc xseɣ ad ssgenfiɣ akfar nwem.”  
\b  
\m “Xzar, aqa aneɣ da, neccin nusa-dd ɣarek, maɣar Cek d SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ!  
\v 23 Nican x walu \add i ittraja bnadem\add* zi řegɛudi n \add tewhibin\add* d ǧɣareɣ x idurar. Nican, di SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, aqa iǧa usenjem n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 3:23 \xt Izhd. 121:1\x*  
\v 24 Řefḍiḥet tecca řxedmet n řejdud nneɣ zi temẓi nneɣ: uǧi nsen d ifunasen d tfunasin nsen, iḥenjiren nsen d tḥenjirin nsen.  
\v 25 Neccin nezzeř di řefḍiḥet nneɣ uca řeḥya nneɣ tedřa aneɣ, maɣar neccin nexḍa ak-d SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, neccin d řejdud nneɣ, zi temẓi nneɣ ař iḍa. Neccin war nesři ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Břa ttubet war ittiři weɛqab  
\m
\v 1 “Mařa texsed ad dd-tɛeqbed, \add a\add* Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ɛqeb-dd ɣari, u mařa tekksed marra nnɛawat n l’aṣnam x wudem inu, war ttɣimi ca teddurid waha.  
\v 2 Jaǧ s tidett, s řḥeqq u s tsegda, \add ini\add*: ‘\add S tidett\add* am iddar SIDI!’, \add xenni\add* ad zzayes ttwabarken řegnus uca ad dayes ssɛuǧen ixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt Amz. 22:18; Ica. 48:1\x*  
\v 3 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI i yeryazen n Yahuda u i Urcalim: ‘Carzem iyyar ixwan i yixef nwem, \add maca\add* war zarrɛem deg isennanen. \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Ḥuc. 10:12\x*  
\v 4 Xetnem ixef nwem i SIDI u ssiggʷejem řeɛdařeyyat n wuřawen nwem, kenniw iryazen n Yahuda d kenniw imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ḥima asɛar inu war ittareẓẓi am tmessi, ad icmeḍ břa ma izemmar uřa d ijj ad issexsi, zi ssibbet n tmegga nwem tiɛeffanin.’” \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt Aɛwd. 10:16; 30:6; Ica. 65:5\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ahjam zi řgens i dd-yusin zi ccamal  
\m
\v 5 “Barrḥem \add tt\add* di Yahuda u jjem ad \add as\add* sřen di Urcalim, inim: ‘Suḍem deg uyicc n icarri di temmurt!’, sɣuyyem s tmijja ijehden, inim: ‘Smunem, asem-dd ɣar tneddam ifaryen!’  
\v 6 Sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant i Ṣihyun, war ttɣimim tbeddem, maɣar Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ řɣar zi ccamal, lmuṣiba tameqqrant.  
\v 7 Ayrad igeɛɛed-dd zi cbarq \add n řmargeḥ\add* nnes, amteḥḥay n řegnus iruḥ deg webrid, iffeɣ-dd zeg wemcan nnes maḥend ad yarr tammurt nnem d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ. Tineddam nnem ad ttwareddǧent ařami war \add daysent\add* ittɣimi uřa d ijj n umezduɣ. \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Ica. 5:29; Irm. 2:15; 5:6\x*  
\v 8 S uyenni, arḍem tixuncay \add n wecḍan\add*, ceḍnem u weɛɛḍem, maɣar war xaneɣ iḥeyyed řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Ica. 32:12\x*   
\m
\v 9 \add Ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: “Deg wass nni ad imsar, aqa uř n ujeǧid d uřawen n řḥukkam ad asen traḥ taryast, ikehhanen ad nnxeřɛen uca inabiyyen ad tbehten.”   
\m
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ: “Ax, Sidi inu, SIDI, s tidett, aqa Cek tcemted řgens-a d Urcalim umi tennid: ‘Ad ɣarwem yiři řehna!’ Xzar, ssif yudef-dd ɛad ɣar řeɛmar \add nneɣ\add*!”   
\m
\v 11 “Deg wass nni ad inin i řgens-a u i Urcalim: ‘Asemmiḍ issecmaḍ zi tewririn tiqeccarin di řexřa aqa-t deg webrid ɣar yeǧis n řgens inu, war ittiři i uzuzzar niɣ i uṣeffi.  
\v 12 Ad iffeɣ zi ɣari ijj n usemmiḍ ijhed x wanita. Řexxu Necc \add simant inu\add* ad ten ḥekmeɣ.  
\v 13 Xzar, igeɛɛed am yiseynuten uca ikarruten nnes ggin am tḥaryaḍt, iysan nnes ttizwaren i igidaren. Uct nneɣ, neccin nettwareddeǧ!’”   
\m
\v 14 “Sird uř nnem zi tuɛeffna, \add a\add* Urcalim, maḥend ad tᵉttwassnejmed! Mecḥař ɛad i ɣa kken zeddɣen ixarriṣen iɛeffanen deg wuř nnem? \f ◼ \fr 4:14 \ft \+fk deg wuř nnem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘di daxeř nnem’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Ica. 1:16\x*  
\v 15 Minzi tmijja tᵉttbarreḥ zi Dan uca tᵉttwaseř tecti tameqqrant \add i-dd-ittqarraben\add* zeg idurar n Ifrayim.  
\v 16 Barḥem \add zzayes\add* di Yahuda u jjem ad as sřen di Urcalim, inim: ‘Inni i ɣa iḥṣaren aqa usin-dd zi temmurt tiggʷej, nitni ssgeɛɛaden tmijja nsen ḍidd i tneddam n Yahuda.’  
\v 17 Nnḍen as-dd am yiɛessasen deg iyyaren, maɣar nettat tɣewweɣ xafi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 18 Tabridt nnem d tmegga nnem iwyen am-dd aya. Aqa-t d actab abarcan nnem, yarzeg, iřeqqef \add i cem deg\add* wuř nnem.”   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “\add Ɛawen ayi,\add* aɛeddis inu, aɛeddis inu, necc ttfarfireɣ s řewjeɛ, \add a\add* iɣezdisen n wuř inu, uř inu ineggez, necc war zemmareɣ ad seɣdeɣ, maɣar asuḍi n uyicc n icarri yudef ɣar řeɛmar inu, \add uct,\add* iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Ica. 21:4; Irm. 8:23\x*  
\v 20 ‘Ticti x tecti!’, \add ammu i\add* sɣuyyun, minzi marra tammurt txarreb. Deɣya ttwahedmen iqiḍan inu, deg wermac n wabřiwen tjartiřin n uqiḍun inu! \f ◼ \fr 4:20 \ft \+fk Ticti x tecti\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Tareẓẓit x tareẓẓit’.\f*  
\v 21 Ař meřmi \add ɛad\add* ad twařiɣ taɛeǧant \add n umenɣi\add* uca ad sřeɣ i usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri?  
\v 22 Řgens inu d abuhaři, nitni war d ayi ssinen. Nitni d iḥenjiren břa řeɛqeř u war ɣarsen teǧi řefhamet. Nitni d imiɣisen maḥend ad ggen řɣar, \add maca\add* war ssinen ad ggen min iṣebḥen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 23 “Necc ẓriɣ tammurt, xzar, tuɣa-tt d řexřa d řxawi u war \add ufiɣ\add* tafawt deg ujenna.  
\v 24 Necc ẓriɣ idurar, xzar, ttarjijin uca marra tiwririn ttenhezzant \add ttraḥent d ttasent i-dd\add*.  
\v 25 Necc twařiɣ, xzar, war din \add uřa d ijj n\add* bnadem, u marra ijḍaḍ n ujenna tuɣa ḍwin.  
\v 26 Necc ẓriɣ, xzar, tammurt isseɣmayen tuɣa d řexřa u marra tineddam nnes ttwahedment di ssibbet n řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI.”   
\m
\v 27 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Marra tammurt-a ad tedweř d tammurt d řexřa, \add maca\add* Necc war \add tt\add* qeṭṭɛeɣ marra. \x ◘ \xo 4:27 \xt Irm. 5:10, 18; 30:11; 46:28\x*  
\v 28 S uya i ɣa tecḍen temmurt, ad bbarcnen ijenwan sennej, maɣar aqa Necc nniɣ t, Necc ggiɣ xas. Necc war ndimeɣ ca u Necc war ddikkwiřeɣ deg wawař.  
\v 29 Zi ddriz n imnayen \add n yeysan\add* d imjebbaden n řqews tarweř tendint marra. Nitni arezzun ad dd-adfen deg izeɣran uca ad geɛɛden x řejruf, tandint marra tᵉttwajj, war dayes iqqim uřa d ijj n umezduɣ.’”   
\m
\v 30 “Min ɣa tegged \add xenni\add*, \add a cem\add* tandint tᵉttwareddeǧ? Waxxa ad tyarḍed \add arruḍ d\add* azeggʷaɣ niɣ ad teqqned řehzuṭ n wureɣ niɣ ad tkeḥḥřed tessemɣarid tiṭṭawin nnem, aqa baṭeř ad tzewwqed ixef nnem. Imeɛcaqen ad cem ssḥeqqaren, ad arzun ad cem nɣen. \f ◼ \fr 4:30 \ft \+fk ad arzun ad cem nɣen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad arzun řeɛmar nnem’.\f*  
\v 31 Maɣar necc ttesřiɣ tmijja, axmi zi temɣart ittarwen, axmi zeg icten tḥeṣṣar di tarwa tamezwarut, tmijja n yeǧis n Ṣihyun, třeqqeḍ-dd nnefs, tesswaẓẓaḍ s ifassen nnes, \add tesɣuyyu\add*: ‘Uct inu, maɣar řeɛmar inu ifna s yinni ixsen ad ayi nɣen!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\m
\v 1 “Uyurem di dcurat n Urcalim, uca xzarem mliḥ. Iřim tfetnem u arzum deg wazzayen nnes, ma ad tafem ijjen, ma din ijj ittegg tasegda, ijjen wenni yarezzun tidett, \add xenni\add* Necc ad as ɣfareɣ \add i Urcalim\add*. \f ◼ \fr 5:1 \ft \+fk Necc ad as ɣfareɣ\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini, aqa Arebbi ad iɣfar i tendint n Urcalim.\f*  
\v 2 Nitni qqaren: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI!’, \add maca\add* waxxa amenni ttjaǧan ẓur.”   
\m
\v 3 “\add A\add* SIDI, ma war \add ḥeṭṭant\add* tiṭṭawin nnec x tidett? Cek tewtid ten, maca war ucin ak-d řeḥriq, Cek teqḍid ten, \add maca\add* war xsen ad ttwarebban. Nitni ggin tanyart nsen iqesḥen x weẓru, nitni ugin ad dd-dewřen. \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Ica. 1:5; 9:12; Irm. 2:30\x*  
\v 4 Necc nniɣ: ‘Ah, nitni d řmusakin, tteggen tubbuheřya, minzi nitni war ssinen abrid n SIDI, tasegda n AREBBI nsen.  
\v 5 Necc ad uyureɣ ɣar imeqqranen uca ad kidsen ssiwřeɣ, minzi nitni war ssinen ca abrid n SIDI, tasegda n AREBBI nsen.’ Nitni jmiɛ \add maca\add* arẓin zzayřet, qeṭṭsen iseɣwan.  
\v 6 X uya iwwet i-ten wayrad n tagant, imezzeq i-ten wuccen zi řewḍat, ittḥama uɣiřas tineddam nsen. Kuř ijj wenni dd ɣa iffɣen \add zi tendint\add*, ad t carrgen, maɣar iɛeddiyen nsen d aṭṭas u aḥeyyed nsen imɣar aṭṭas.” \f ◼ \fr 5:6 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Irm. 4:7\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Mammec \add zemmareɣ\add* ad awem ɣfareɣ man aya? Iḥenjiren nnec semḥen dayi, ttjaǧan ɣar min war iǧi d AREBBI. \add Řami\add* ten ssjiwneɣ, zennan nitni, ssmunen s ddḥas ɣar wexxam n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř.  
\v 8 Nitni d ikidaren iɛeřfen itteliɛen. Kuř ijj issneḥniḥ ɣar temɣart n wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Ḥiz. 22:11\x*  
\v 9 Ma war ttɛiqibeɣ x man aya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, niɣ war ittentiqim řeɛmar inu zi řgens am wanita?” \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Irm. 5:29; 9:9\x*   
\m
\v 10 “Geɛɛdem x řeḥyuḍ nnes uca hedmem ten, \add maca\add* war ten messḥem qaɛ zi temmurt. Qeřɛem izbiren nsen, maɣar nitni war \add ǧin\add* ca n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Irm. 4:27\x*  
\v 11 Taddart n Israil d taddart n Yahuda \add maca\add* ɣdaren ayi s waṭṭas, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt Irm. 3:20\x*  
\v 12 Nitni nekkaren SIDI, qqaren: ‘Netta war \add din\add* iǧi, war d aneɣ iřeqqef řɣar, war nettwiři ssif uřa d řaẓ.  
\v 13 Inabiyyen ad dewřen am usemmiḍ uca war din iǧi wenni zzaysen issawařen. Ammu i d asen ɣa imsar.’”   
\m
\v 14 “S uya iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat: ‘Minzi kenniw teqqarem awař-a, xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ awařen inu deg uqemmum nnec d timessi, řgens-a \add ad t ggeɣ\add* d akeccuḍ, uca ad ten tecc \add tmessi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Irm. 1:9\x*  
\v 15 Xzar, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, Necc ad xawem ssiwḍeɣ ijj n řgens zi řaggʷaj, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Aqa-t d řgens iwɛar, řgens zeg wecḥař uya, řgens i zi war tessined cek awař nnes, u war tfehhmed min qqaren nitni. \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt Aɛwd. 28:49; Irm. 1:15; 6:22\x*  
\v 16 Azeɛbuř nnes \add n fřitcat\add* \add igga\add* am yijj n wenḍeř yarezmen, nitni marra d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt.  
\v 17 Ad icc \add řgens nni\add* ṣṣabet nnem d weɣrum nnem, ad icc iḥenjiren nnem d yessim, ad icc uǧi nnem d ifunasen d tfunasin nnem, ad icc tazayart nnem d wartu nnem, \add uca\add* s ssif ad iwwet tineddam nnem ifaryen min xef tᵉttecřed.’” \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Lawi 26:16; Aɛwd. 28:31,33\x*   
\m
\v 18 “\add Maca\add* uřa deg wussan nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, Necc war kenniw qeṭṭiɣ marra. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Irm. 4:27\x*  
\v 19 Mařa xenni kenniw teqqarem: ‘Mayemmi d aneɣ igga SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, marra aya?’, \add xenni\add* ad asen tinid: ‘Am mammec kenniw dayi tsemḥem, tᵉttsexxarem i irebbiten \add iɣriben\add* di temmurt nwem, ammu i ɣa tsexxarem i ibarraniyyen di temmurt war teǧi nwem.’” \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Irm. 16:10\x*   
\m
\v 20 “Barrḥem aya i taddart n Yaɛqub, jjem ad \add t\add* sřen di Yahuda, ini:  
\v 21 ‘Sřem i waya, \add a cek\add* řgens abuhaři, nehřa wuř! Ɣarwem tiṭṭawin, \add maca\add* war ttwiřint, imezzuɣen, \add maca\add* war ttesřin. \x ◘ \xo 5:21 \xt Ica. 6:9, 10\x*  
\v 22 Ma war d ayi tteggʷedem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Ma war tᵉttexsem tᵉttarjijim zzat i wudem inu, \add i Necc\add* wenni iggin i řebḥar ijdi d weymir, d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda tenni war zemmaren ad ɛdun \add řemwaj\add*. Aqa ttenhezzan řemwaj, \add ɛad\add* war zemmaren, tthajan řemwaj, \add ɛad\add* war tt ɛeddun.’\x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Ayub 38:10, 11; Izhd. 33:7; 104:9\x*  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* řgens-a ɣares uř iḥeyyden d iɣewwɣen. Nitni ḥeyyden \add x webrid\add* uca ffɣen.  
\v 24 Nitni war qqaren deg yixef nsen: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad neggʷed SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ nni itticen anẓar di řweqt nnes, anẓar n zic d wenẓar n řexmim, wenni iḥeṭṭan i neccin ssimanat ittwaggen n tmeyra.’ \x ◘ \xo 5:24 \xt Aɛwd. 11:14\x*  
\v 25 Řmuɛṣiyyat nwem menɛent man aya u ddnub nwem ṭṭfen xawem min icnan.  
\v 26 Maɣar ufin iɛeffanen di řgens inu. Nitni ttḥaman am yiyemmaren n yejḍaḍ. Ssbeddan ijj n řfex ineqqen, arezzun ad ṭṭfen iwdan.  
\v 27 Am řeqfez iccur s ijḍaḍ, ammu tudrin nsen ccurent s řɣecc. X uya dewřen nitni d imeqqranen d ayt n bu-wagřa.  
\v 28 Aqa nitni uffen s tadunt, aqa aten d iḥraymiyyen, \add s tmegga nsen\add* ssɛeddun nitni timegga tiɛeffanin aṭṭas. War ḥekkmen s řḥeqq di ddeɛwet, uřa di ddeɛwet n uyujiř, waxxa amenni feřḥen nitni. Ɛawed war cciten x tesɣart n imezřaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 5:28 \xt Aɛwd. 32:15; Ica. 1:23; Zak. 7:10\x*  
\v 29 Ma war ttɛiqibeɣ x man aya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ma war xeǧfeɣ Ixef inu zi řgens am wanita?” \x ◘ \xo 5:29 \xt Irm. 5:9; 9:9\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 30 “Min ittenexřaɛen u min iǧan d nnɛi aqa imsar di temmurt.  
\v 31 Inabiyyen ttnebban s ixarriqen uca ikehhanen ttṣeǧḍen sadu ufus nsen. Uca řgens inu ittexs i-t ammu. Min ɣa teggem xmi dd ɣa yaweḍ qeṭṭu?” \x ◘ \xo 5:31 \xt Irm. 14:18; 23:25, 26; Ḥiz. 13:6\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\m
\v 1 “Siwḍem ixef nwem di řaman zi řwest n Urcalim, \add a\add* ayt n Binyamin, uca suḍem deg uyicc n icarri di Taquɛa. Sgeɛɛdem acenyal \add s ddexxan\add* zi Bayt-Ha-Karim, minzi issigʷad řɣar zi ccamal, lmuṣiba tameqqrant. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt Irm. 1:13, 14\x*  
\v 2 Tamɣart icewwaren d ittwassubuḍen, yeǧis n Ṣihyun, ad tt sshellkeɣ.  
\v 3 Imeksawen ad ɣares dd-asen ak-d tḥimriwin nsen, nitni ad as dd-qewwaren, ad wten iqiḍan \add nsen\add* xas, kuř ijj ad yarwes di tesɣart nnes. \f ◼ \fr 6:3 \ft \+fk Imeksawen\ft  - niɣ: ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 4 \add Ad inin\add* ‘Qeddsem amenɣi ḍidd nnes, kkarem, jjem aneɣ ad \add ɣares\add* ngeɛɛed s uziř. Uct xaneɣ, maɣar ass ɛřayen iɛdu, minzi tiřiwin n tmeddit ttsarrḥent-i-dd.  
\v 5 Kkarem, jjem aneɣ ad ngeɛɛed s ǧiřet, ad nehdem řeqṣur nnes!’  
\v 6 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řeskarat: Qessem ticejjura, sbeddem acbar i řeḥṣaret ḍidd i Urcalim. Ta d tandint i ɣa tᵉttwaɛaqeb, aqa ddeǧ di řwest nnes marra.  
\v 7 Am wanu ittejja aman nnes ttbeqbuqen, ammu i tᵉttejja \add Urcalim\add* ad ibeqbeq min war iḥřin. \add Řḥess n\add* lɛunf d wareddeǧ ittwaseř dayem, řeḥřac d teyyita aqa-tent řebda zzat i tiṭṭawin inu.  
\v 8 Ejj i cem ad tᵉttwawebbxed, \add a\add* Urcalim, ḥima řeɛmar inu war xam tᵉttemsebḍi, ḥima war cem ttarriɣ d tammurt ittwareddǧen d tammurt ixřan zeg imezdaɣ.”   
\m
\v 9 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Am tzayart ad řeqḍen min iqqimen n Israil s cḍaret. Arr afus nnec ɣar tseḍwin am wenni iřeqqḍen aḍiř.’\x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Ica. 24:13\x*  
\v 10 Wi ɣar i ɣa ssiwřeɣ niɣ umi ɣa ɛeřmeɣ necc, \add ḥima\add* ad sřen? Xzar, amezzuɣ nsen war ittwaxten, \add ařami\add* war zemmaren ad sřen i walu. Aqa da, awař\add en\add* n SIDI ttafen \add ten\add* d aḥecci, war ten ḥdijen.” \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt Irm. 7:26\x*   
\m
\v 11 “S uyenni ccureɣ s wesɛar n SIDI, aqa uḥřeɣ ad t menɛeɣ. ‘Zeǧeɛ \add asɛar nnec\add* \add xenni\add* x iḥenjiren deg webrid uřa x umuni n iḥudriyyen, maɣar ɛad aryaz d temɣart ad ten ḥebbsen, ammu uřa d amɣar d uwessar.  
\v 12 Tudrin nsen ad dewřent i inneɣni, jmiɛ ak-d iḥwicen, uřa d timɣarin, maɣar Necc ad swiẓẓḍeɣ s ufus inu ḍidd imezdaɣ n temmurt\add -a\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt Aɛwd. 28:30\x*  
\v 13 Maɣar zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran arezzun marra nitni tizi nsen, u zeg unabi ař akehhan marra tcemmet. \x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Ica. 56:11; Irm. 8:10\x*  
\v 14 Tareẓẓit n řgens inu xsen ad tt ssgenfan s řehwen, qqaren: ‘Řehna, řehna!’, maca war din iǧi řehna. \f ◼ \fr 6:14 \ft \+fk qqaren: ‘Řehna, řehna!’, maca war din iǧi řehna.\ft  - man aya ixs ad yini ‘qqaren ‘Mliḥ, mliḥ!’, maca war din min iǧan d lemliḥ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt Irm. 8:11; Ḥiz. 13:10\x*  
\v 15 Ma ad seḍḥan minzi tteggen jjɛifect? Nitni war ttseḍḥin ca, řeḥya war t ssinen. S uya nitni ad wḍan jar inni iweṭṭan. Ɣar řweqt nni ad zzaysen xeřfeɣ ad nnqarḍen!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 16 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Beddem ɣar ibriden, uca ḥdam, seqsam x ibriden n wecḥař uya, mani iǧa webrid nican uca uyurem xas, \add xenni\add* ad tafem arraḥet i řeɛmar nwem!’ Nitni \add maca\add* qqaren: ‘Neccin war \add xas\add* neggur!’ \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Mt. 11:29\x*  
\v 17 Necc ggiɣ awem iɛessasen, nniɣ: ‘Sřem i usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri!’, \add maca\add* nitni qqaren: ‘Neccin war \add ɣares\add* nesḥessi ca!’  
\v 18 S uya sřem, \add a kenniw\add* řegnus, u \add cem, a\add* tamesmunt!, ssen min ɣarsen i ɣa imsaren!  
\v 19 Seř, \add a\add* tammurt, xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ řɣar \add d ameqqran\add* x řgens-a, řɣiǧet n inwayen nsen tiɛeffanin, maɣar nitni war xezzaren ca ɣar wawařen inu u nḍaren Ccariɛa inu.  
\v 20 Mayemmi d ayi dd ɣa yawyen jjawi zi Caba d uɣanim uḥemmum ittfuḥen zi temmurt yiggʷejen? Tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ nwem war d ayi dd-usint i řxaḍar u tiɣarṣa nwem war d ayi ɛjibent. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Ica. 1:11; 66:3; Ɛam. 5:21; Mixa 6:6-8\x*  
\v 21 S uya \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ tiɛenkrifin i řgens-a uca nitni ad daysent nnqarḍen jmiɛ ak-d ibabaten d iḥenjiren, ak-d wajjar d umɛacar nnes, \add ammu\add* i ɣa hellken.’”   
\m
\v 22 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, ad dd-yas ijj n řgens zi ccamal, ijj n řgens ameqqran ad ittwařaɣa zeg ineggura n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 6:22 \xt Irm. 50:41,42,43\x*  
\v 23 Nitni ṭṭfen řqews d weḥric, \add aqa-t d ijj n řgens\add* iwɛar, war arreḥmen. Ddriz nsen igga am zzhir n řebḥar uca nitni nyin x yeysan. Am weryaz n umenɣi ammu i issbedd netta ixef nnes ḍidd nnem, \add a\add* yeǧis n Ṣihyun!”   
\m
\v 24 “Neccin nesřa xas řexbar, arxun aneɣ ifassen nneɣ, iřqef aneɣ unedqef, řeḥriq am n temɣart ittarwen. \x ◘ \xo 6:24 \xt Irm. 4:31; 49:24; 50:43\x*  
\v 25 War tteffɣem ɣar barra ɣar yeyyar, war ggurem deg webrid, maɣar \add aqa din\add* ssif n řeɛdu, tiggʷudi aqa-tt mani ma!  
\v 26 \add A\add* yeǧis n řgens inu, beyset ixef nnem s txancet \add n wecḍan\add*, zuzzar xam \add iɣɣeḍ\add*, ceḍnet am x uyenni n mmis nnem, sɣuyy s tɣuyyit tamerzagt, maɣar deɣya ad xaneɣ dd-yas umteḥḥay.” \x ◘ \xo 6:26 \xt Irm. 4:8\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 27 “Necc ggiɣ cek d ṣṣumɛet n tɛessast di řgens inu, d ict n lqelɛa, ḥima ad tessned abrid nsen, ad dayes tarzud.”   
\b  
\m
\v 28 “Nitni marra d inni iḥeyyden x webrid zi markat iwɛaren qaɛ, gguren ttennḍen di temmurt ttceqqafen, nitni am nnḥas d wuzzař, marra idsen d ayt n bu-imurḍas. \x ◘ \xo 6:28 \xt Ḥiz. 22:18\x*  
\v 29 Arrabuz icmeḍ, řexfif tecca t tmessi, \add maca\add* di řbaṭeř issefsi ufessay ammu s wecḍar, iɛeffanen war zemmaren ad ttwafarzen.  
\v 30 Qqaren as: ‘Nnuqart immenḍaren!’, maɣar inḍar i-ten SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 6:30 \xt Ica. 1:22\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Awař n Irmiya di Zzawect Tameqqrant  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 2 “Bedd di tewwart n Taddart n SIDI uca řaɣa dinni awař-a, ini: ‘Sřem awař n SIDI, \add a\add* Yahuda marra, kenniw inni ittadfen zi tewwura-ya ḥima ad tbendqem zzat i SIDI.  
\v 3 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Ɛedřem ibriden nnem d tmegga nwem, \add xenni\add* Necc ad kenniw sszedɣeɣ deg wemcan-a. \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Irm. 7:3; 18:11; 26:13\x*  
\v 4 War ttcařem x wawařen n ixarriqen am teqqarem: Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI, aqa-tt d ta zeɛma!  
\v 5 Maɣar \add mɣir\add* mařa tɛedřem ibriden nwem d tmegga nwem nican, mařa s tidett tᵉtteggem s řḥeqq jar weryaz d umeddukkeř nnes, \x ◘ \xo 7:5 \xt Irm. 5:28\x*  
\v 6 war ḥeṣṣarem abarrani, ayujiř d tajjač, u war ssizziřem idammen imezdagen deg wemcan-a u war ḍeffarem irebbiten nneɣni i uḍeyyeɛ nwem, \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Ica. 10:1, 2; 59:7\x*  
\v 7 \add xenni\add* Necc ad kenniw sszedɣeɣ deg wemcan-a, di temmurt i wciɣ i řejdud nwem, zi řebda ař řebda.  
\v 8 Xzar, kenniw tᵉttcařam x ixarriqen nni war ineffɛen di walu.  
\v 9 Tᵉttacarem, tneqqem, tzennam, tᵉttjaǧam ẓur, tᵉttqeddamem tiwhibin n řebxur i Baɛl u tḍeffaram irebbiten nneɣni nni war tessinem,  
\v 10 uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-tasem tbeddem zzat i wudem inu di Taddart-a min xef ittwabarreḥ s Yisem inu, uca \add xenni\add* tzeɛmem \add ɛad\add* ad teqqarem: ‘Neccin nettwassenjem!’, uca \add xenni\add* tᵉttɛawadem tᵉtteggem marra jjɛayef-a!  
\v 11 Ma tedweř Taddart-a min xef ittwabarreḥ Isem inu d ifri n ixewwanen di tiṭṭawin nwem? Xzar, \bd Necc\bd* ẓriɣ t mliḥ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 7:11 \xt Mt. 21:13; Mk. 11:17; Lk. 19:46\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “Waxxa, uyurem ɣar wemcan n Tzeddiɣt inu di Cilu mani tuɣa sszedɣeɣ Isem inu deg umezwaru. Xzarem min zzayes ggiɣ zi ssibbet n řɣar n řgens inu Israil. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 4:11; Izhd. 78:60\x*  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, minzi kenniw teggim marra timegga-ya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, u Necc ssiwřeɣ akidwem zeg umezwaru, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim ca, u Necc řaɣiɣ-dd xawem, \add maca\add* kenniw war dd-tarrim, \f ◼ \fr 7:13 \ft \+fk zeg umezwaru\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ssiwřeɣ akidwem umi tuɣa-yi ttfaqeɣ’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt 2 Im. 36:15; Awřn. 1:24; Ica. 65:12; 66:4; Irm. 7:21-28\x*  
\v 14 \add s uyenni\add* Necc ad ggeɣ ak-d Taddart-a min xef ittwabarreḥ Isem inu, min xef tᵉttcařam, u ak-d wemcan-a nni wciɣ i kenniw d řejdud nwem, am mammec ggiɣ ak-d Cilu.  
\v 15 Necc ad kenniw nḍareɣ zi zzat n wudem inu, am mammec nḍareɣ marra aytmatwem, marra zzariɛet n Ifrayim.”   
\b  
\m
\v 16 “A cek, war ttẓaǧ i řgens-a u war sgeɛɛed \add tmijja nnec\add* ḥima ad trud niɣ ad teẓẓaǧed u war ttɣimi tᵉttrud-dd ɣari, maɣar Necc war ɣarek dd-ttesřiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Uf. 32:10; Irm. 11:14; 14:11\x*  
\v 17 Ma war tᵉttwiřid min tteggen nitni di tneddam n Yahuda u deg ibriden n Urcalim?  
\v 18 Iḥenjiren ssmunam akeccuḍ, ibabaten \add nsen\add* ssraqqan timessi, u timɣarin tteggwent arecti ḥima ad sswejdent tifḍiřin i tjeǧidt n ujenna u ḥima ad farrɣent tiwhibin n useyyeb zzat i irebbiten nneɣni maḥend ad ayi sɛaren. \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt Ica. 65:11; Irm. 8:2; 19:13; 44:19; Irm. 44:19\x*  
\v 19 Ma sɛaren ayi, iqqar SIDI? Ma war t tteggen i yixef nsen i řefḍiḥet n simant nsen?  
\v 20 S uya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, ad ittwafarreɣ weɣḍab inu d wesɛar inu x wemcan-a: x iwdan, x imuddaren, x tcejjura deg iyyar u x řɣiǧet n wudem n temmurt. Ad yareqq \add wah,\add* u war \add izemmar\add* ad ittwassexsi.”   
\b  
\m
\v 21 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Smunem tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ nwem ak-d tɣarṣa nwem uca ccem aysum \add nsent\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:21 \xt Ica. 1:11; Irm. 6:20; Ɛam. 5:21\x*  
\v 22 Maɣar deg wass nni di ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra, war ssiwřeɣ ak-d řejdud nwem maḥend ad asen weṣṣiɣ x tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣi.  
\v 23 Maca Necc umureɣ tamesřact-a umi nniɣ: ‘Sřem-dd ɣar tmijja inu, \add xenni\add* Necc ad awem iřiɣ d AREBBI u kenniw ad ayi tiřim d řgens u ad tuyurem di abrid marra nni d awem i ɣa umureɣ maḥend ad tiřim mliḥ!’ \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt Uf. 19:5; Lawi 26:12; Aɛwd. 6:3\x*  
\v 24 \add Maca\add* nitni war sřin, war d ayi wcin umezzuɣ, nitni ḍfaren ixarriṣen d řeqsaḥet n wuř aɛeffan nsen, u nitni dewřen ɣar ḍeffar, war iǧi ɣar zzat. \x ◘ \xo 7:24 \xt Irm. 2:27; 3:17; 16:12; 32:33\x*  
\v 25 Zeg wass nni di ffɣen řejdud nwem zi Miṣra ař ass-a, ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarwem marra imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen, zeg wussan n wecḥař uya.  
\v 26 Nitni war ɣari sřin u war d ayi wcin amezzuɣ. Nitni arnin di řeqsaḥet mahu řejdud nsen. \x ◘ \xo 7:26 \xt Naḥ. 9:17, 29; Irm. 17:23; 19:15\x*  
\v 27 Ad kidsen tessawařed marra awařen-a, \add maca\add* nitni war d ak ttesřin ca. Cek ad asen třaɣid, \add maca\add* war xak dd-ttarrin.  
\v 28 S uya ini asen: ‘Wa d řgens i war ittesřin ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, u war ittejjin ixef nnes ad ittwawebbex. Aqa tidett tᵉttwareddeǧ u tᵉttwaqess zeg uqemmum nsen!’” \x ◘ \xo 7:28 \xt Irm. 5:1, 3\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 29 “Ḥeff tajj nnec \add n weɛzař\add* uca nḍar i-t, wwet s igejduren x řegɛudi \add mani ttwehhbent ddbayeḥ\add*, maɣar SIDI inḍar jjiř min xef idduqqez \add ufugem nnes\add*, uca ijja i-t. \x ◘ \xo 7:29 \xt Ayub 1:20; Ica. 15:2; Irm. 16:6\x*  
\v 30 Maɣar iḥenjiren n Yahuda ggin min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Nitni ssbedden nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam di Taddart min xef ittwařaɣa s Yisem inu maḥend ad tt ssxemmjen.  
\v 31 Nitni ssbedden řegɛudi n Tufat \add mani ttwehhbent ddbayeḥ,\add* \add d tinni iǧan\add* di Teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum, ḥima ad sscemḍen iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin nsen di tmessi, min ɛemmarṣ war d asen umureɣ d min ɛemmarṣ war d ayi dd-iddaren ɣar řbař.” \f ◼ \fr 7:31 \ft \+fk ɣar řbař\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar wuř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:31 \xt 2 Ij. 23:10; Irm. 2:23; 19:5, 6\x*   
\m
\v 32 “S uya, xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, war d as ttřaɣan ɛad ‘Tufat’ niɣ ‘Taɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum’, maca ‘Taɣzurt n Wenɣay’, uca di Tufat ad neḍřen \add imettan\add*, minzi mani nneɣni war din amcan.  
\v 33 Řxecbat n řgens-a ad dewřent d macca i ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i řmař n yeyyar uca uřa d ijj war ten issiggʷid. \x ◘ \xo 7:33 \xt Aɛwd. 28:26; Irm. 34:20\x*  
\v 34 Zi tneddam n Yahuda u zeg ibriden n Urcalim ad ssbeddeɣ tmijja n usřiwřew d tmijja n řefraḥet, tmijja n muřay d tmijja n tesřit, maɣar tammurt ad tedweř d řxarbet.”\x ◘ \xo 7:34 \xt Ica. 24:7; Irm. 16:9; 25:10; Ḥiz. 26:13; Ḥuc. 2:13\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\m
\v 1 “Di řweqt nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad ssuffɣen iɣsan n ijeǧiden n Yahuda, iɣsan n řḥukkam nsen, iɣsan n ikehhanen nsen, iɣsan n inabiyyen nsen d yeɣsan n imezdaɣ n Urcalim zeg imeḍřan nsen.  
\v 2 Ad bezzɛen \add ixsan\add* i tfuct d tziri u i marra itran n ujenna, inni tuɣa ttexsen, inni umi tuɣa ɛebbden, inni tuɣa ḍeffaran d yinni tuɣa zzaysen arezzun ccwar d yinni umi tuɣa sejjaden. War ten dd-yarrwen, war ten neṭṭřen, \add maca\add* ad iřin d řeɣbar x wudem n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Irm. 7:18; 19:13\x*  
\v 3 Nitni ad xsen řmewt x tudart jar marra inni iqqimen zeg yinni iqqimen n teqbič n řgens-a taɛeffant, di marra imucan mani \add ǧan\add* inni \add ɛad\add* iqqimen, mani xasen uẓẓřeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Ma ad wḍan ař ɣa qqimen war ttekkaran \add ɛad\add*? Ma ad \add xafi\add* ḥeyyden u war dd-ttɛiqqiben?  
\v 5 Mayemmi iḥeyyed řgens-a, Urcalim \add tanita\add*, řebda \add zzayi\add*? Nitni cebbaren deg wecmat, ugin ad ɣari dd-dewřen.  
\v 6 Necc ssḥesseɣ, sřiɣ: min ssawařen, war t tteggen, uřa d ijjen war indim x řɣar nnes, ad yini: Min ggiɣ? Kuř ijj iqqim ittazzeř am uyis ittazzřen ɣar umenɣi.  
\v 7 Uřa d abellarj deg ujenna issen řewqat ittwaggen nnes. Tajlilleḥt d tfařǧest nni iṭṭawen deg wenneḍ, ḥḍant řweqt n wuffuɣ nsent, řgens inu \add maca\add* war issin řḥeqq n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt Irm. 5:4, 5\x*  
\v 8 Mammec teqqarem: Neccin d imiɣisen d Ccariɛa n SIDI aqa-tt akidneɣ! S tidett, xzar, řeqřem n ixarriqen n imariren igga \add Ccariɛa\add* d axarriq.  
\v 9 Imiɣisen ttseḍḥan, tteggʷeden uca ttwaḥebbsen. Xzar, nḍaren awař n SIDI, \add xenni\add* mammec i teǧa tiɣit i ɣarsen?”   
\m
\v 10 “S uya ad wceɣ timɣarin nsen i inneɣni, iyyaren nsen i yinni i ɣa iḥewwsen \add tammurt\add*, maɣar zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran arezzun marra nitni tizi nsen, zeg unabi ař akehhan marra tcemmet. \x ◘ \xo 8:10 \xt Ica. 56:11; Irm. 6:12, 13, 14, 15\x*  
\v 11 Tareẓẓit n řgens inu xsen ad tt ssgenfan s řehwen am qqaren: ‘Řehna, řehna!’, maca war din iǧi řehna.  
\v 12 Ma ad seḍḥan nitni, minzi tteggen jjɛifect? Nitni war ttseḍḥin ca, řeḥya war t ssinen. S uya ad wḍan jar inni iweṭṭan. Di řweqt meřmi zzaysen i ɣa xeřfeɣ ad nnqarḍen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”  
\v 13 “Necc ad ten řeqḍeɣ qaɛ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. War iqqim \add ɛad\add* uḍiř ɣar tzayart u war teqqim \add ɛad\add* tazart ɣar tcejjart n wartu, \add ɛad\add* tifray wḍant. Necc ad ɣarsen awyeɣ inni xasen i ɣa iɛefsen.” \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Ica. 5:1-7; Mt. 21:19; Lk. 13:6-9\x*   
\m
\v 14 “Mayemmi da narni deg uɣimi? Ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad nmun, ad nadef ɣar tneddam ifaryen, uca ad din nesqar. Aqa SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, yarra aneɣ ad nesqar uca iwca aneɣ aman ismumen, maɣar nexḍa x SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Irm. 4:5; 9:15; 23:15\x*  
\v 15 Nessittim di řehna, \add maca\add* war din min iṣebḥen, di řweqt n usgenfi, \add maca\add* xzar, \add mɣir\add* asnexřiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Irm. 14:19\x*  
\v 16 Zi Dan ittwaseř usaḥart n yeysan nnes, zeg wesneḥneḥ n \add yeysan\add* ijehden nnes tenhezza marra tammurt. Nitni ad dd-asen ad ccen tammurt d řɣiǧet nnes, tandint ak-d imezdaɣ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt Irm. 4:15\x*  
\v 17 Maɣar xzar, Necc ad ssekkeɣ jar awem ifiɣran, ifiɣran n arrhaj, akidsen war ineffeɛ uɛezzem. Ina ad kenniw zeɛfen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Izhd. 58:5, 6\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řeḥřiq deg wuř n Irmiya  
\m
\v 18 “Amḥad inu aqa idweř d acḍan, uř inu yuḥeř aṭṭas deg ixef inu.  
\v 19 Xzar, řḥess n iɣuyyan n yeǧis n řgens inu zi temmurt tiggʷej: ‘Ma SIDI war iǧi di Ṣihyun, ma war dayes iǧi ujeǧid nnes?’”  
\b  
\m “Mayemmi d ayi sɛaren s řexyařat nsen ineqcen, s \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen n ibarraniyyen?”   
\b  
\m
\v 20 “Teɛdu tmeyra, iffeɣ unebdu, \add u\add* neccin ɛad war nenjim.  
\v 21 Necc ttwarẓiɣ zi ssibbet n tareẓẓit n yessis n řgens inu. Necc arḍeɣ arruḍ d abarcan, icebbar dayi unexřiɛ. \f ◼ \fr 8:21 \ft \+fk tareẓẓit\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘ayezzim yarezmen’ wenni dd-yusin ak-d ddnub n řgens n Israil d Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim, minzi war xsen ad dewřen ɣar Arebbi. Xzar ɛawed Ica. 1. S wawař ‘tareẓẓit’ iceyyar unabi Irmiya ɛawed ɣar uweṭṭu i dd-yusin ɣar Urcalim s ufus n ujeǧid n Babil i x issawař Irmiya deg wudem-a n řectab n Irmiya.\f*  
\v 22 Ma war din iǧi balsam di Jilɛad? Ma war dinni iǧi umesgenfu? Mayemmi war inniḍ uyezzim n yeǧis n řgens inu? \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Amz. 37:24; Irm. 46:11; 51:8\x*  
\v 23 Ax, mři azeǧif inu d aman, tiṭṭ inu d řɛunṣar n imeṭṭawen, \add xenni\add* aziř d ǧiřet iři ruɣ x yinni ittwanɣen n yeǧis n řgens inu.” \x ◘ \xo 8:23 \xt Ica. 22:4; Irm. 4:19\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Acetci n SIDI AREBBI  
\m
\v 1 “Ax, mři ɣari tazeddiɣt di řexřa i imsebriden, \add xenni\add* iři semḥeɣ di řgens inu, uyureɣ, maɣar nitni marra d izennayen, amuni n iɣeddaren. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Irm. 5:7, 8\x*  
\v 2 Nitni ssqeḍɛen iřes nsen, řqews \add iccur s\add* ixarriqen. Nitni war dwiřen d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt di temmurt s řmanet, maɣar nitni uyuren zi tɛeffant ɣar učmas umi war d ayi ssinen ca, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Ica. 59:4, 13, 15; Irm. 6:7\x*  
\v 3 Ejj kuř ijj ad iḥḍa ixef nnes zeg umeddukkeř nnes, war ttciřem uřa x tawmat, maɣar kuř tawmat tᵉttegg mɣir acmat u kuř ameddukkeř ittenneḍ am ittceqqaf s řhard nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Irm. 6:28\x*  
\v 4 Kuř ijj ittɣarra ameddukkeř nnes, war qqaren ca tidett. Nitni sseřmaden i yiřes nsen ad issxarreq, nitni ssaḥařen ixef nsen s min war iseggden.  
\v 5 Tazeddiɣt nnec tbedd di řwesṭ n wecmat. S wecmat \add nsen\add* ɛewwřen ad ayi ssnen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 6 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ten ssfesyeɣ u ad ten jarrbeɣ, maɣar mammec ɣa ggeɣ ad kkareɣ \add xenni\add* ak-d yeǧis n řgens inu?  
\v 7 Iřes nsen am fřitca n řqews ineqqen, aqa issawař s wecmat. S uqemmum nnes kuř ijj issawař x řehna ak-d umeddukkeř nnes, \add maca\add* deg wuř nnes issewjad as ijj n řfex. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Izhd. 12:3; 28:3; 120:4; Awřn. 30:14\x*  
\v 8 Ma war zzaysen xeǧfeɣ zi man aya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Ma war ixeǧef řeɛmar inu zi řgens am wa?” \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Irm. 5:9, 29\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Necc ad ruɣ, ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ tɣuyyit n uweḥweḥ x idurar d yezři n wecḍan x ddmani n tarewsa, maɣar ttwacemḍen ařami uřa d ijj war ssenni dd-ittekk u war ttesřin řḥess n tḥimriwin ɛad. Zeg ijḍaḍ n ujenna ař řmař \add marra\add* arewřen, kkaren uyuren.”   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “Ad arreɣ Urcalim d izellijen n weẓru, d amcan n udurri i wuccanen n řexřa, uca tineddam n Yahuda ad tent ggeɣ d tammurt ittwareddǧen nni di war izeddeɣ uřa d ijj.” \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Irm. 10:22\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Wi iǧan d aryaz amiɣis, aqa ad iḥaka deg uya, u wi ɣar issiweř uqemmum n SIDI? Ejj i-t ad \add zzayes\add* ibarreḥ \add xenni\add*! Mayemmi tᵉttwaxarreb tammurt, tᵉttwassecmeḍ am řexřa ařami uřa d ijj war tt ittcuqi?”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “SIDI inna: ‘Řami arxun nitni zi Ccariɛa inu tenni d asen wciɣ zzat i uɣembub nsen, u war sřin ɣar tmijja inu u war tt ḍfaren,  
\v 13 maca ḍfaren řeqsaḥet n wuř \add n yixef\add* nsen uřa d ‘Ibaɛlen’ am mammec i d asen sseřmaden řejdud nsen,  
\v 14 s uya, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad wceɣ cciḥ i řgens-a ḥima ad t ccen uřa d aman n arrhaj ḥima ad ten swen. \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Irm. 8:14; 23:15\x*  
\v 15 Necc ad ten zuzzareɣ jar řegnus nni war ssinen, war iǧi nitni uřa d řejdud nsen, u Necc ad xasen ssekkeɣ ssif ař ten qḍiɣ.’ \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Lawi 26:33\x*  
\v 16 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Ḥḍam, řaɣam-dd i temɣarin i wecḍan maḥend ad dd-asent, uca jjem uřa d timɣarin timiɣisin ad dd-asent!’”   
\m
\v 17 “\add Necc nniɣ, wah,\add* jjem tent ad deɣyant u ad ssgeɛɛdent tɣuyyit n wecḍan xaneɣ ař dd-azzřent tiṭṭawin nneɣ s imeṭṭawen u waman ad dd-hwan x wabřiwen.  
\v 18 Maɣar tɣuyyit n wecḍan sřin as-dd zi Ṣihyun: ‘Ax, mammec nettwareddeǧ, neccin nseḍḥa aṭṭas maɣar tuɣa xaneɣ ad nekkar ad nesmeḥ di temmurt nneɣ, maɣar tizeddiɣin nneɣ hedmen tent.’  
\v 19 Sřent xenni i wawař n SIDI, \add a\add* timɣarin, ejj amezzuɣ nkent ad iksi awař zeg uqemmum nnes. Sřemdent yessitkent ad ceḍnent uca ad tᵉsseřmed kuř tamɣart ict n wezři n wecḍan i tmeddukkečt nnes.  
\v 20 Minzi řmewt tgeɛɛed-dd zi řekwazi nneɣ, yudef-dd ɣar řeqṣur nneɣ maḥend ad iqḍeɛ iḥenjiren imeẓyanen zi zznaqi d iḥudriyyen zeg wazzayen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 21 “Siweř, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI:  
\m \qt ‘Řxecbet n bnadem ad tewḍa\qt*  
\m \qt am řeɣbar x yeyyar,\qt*  
\m \qt u am tqebbiḍt \+tl n imendi\+tl*\qt*  
\m \qt awarni i wenni imejjaren\qt*  
\m \qt nni war t i ɣa ijarwen uřa d ijj.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Irm. 7:33\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War ittfeyyic umiɣis s tiɣit \add n yixef nnes\add* uřa d bu-teɣruḍt war ittfeyyic s jjhed nnes, bu-wagřa war ittfeyyic s wagřa nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt 1 Kur. 1:31; 2 Kur. 10:17\x*  
\v 23 Maca wenni ittfeyyacen, ejj i-t ad issemɣar, belli netta ɣares řefhamet u issen ayi, belli Necc d SIDI nni itteggen s tmexsiwt icewwaren d řḥeqq d tsegda di temmurt, maɣar timesřayin-a tteɛjibent ayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 24 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, aqa Necc ad xeřfeɣ zi marra inni ixetnen, \add maca waxxa amenni\add* ɣarsen \add ɛad\add* řeɛdařyet,  
\v 25 zi Miṣra d Yahuda d Idum d ayt n Ɛammun d Mu’ab d marra inni ittḥeffan \add acuwwaf\add* ɣar ṭṭrufa, inni izeddɣen di řexřa, maɣar marra řegnus war ttwaxetnen, maca marra taddart n Israil aqa ɣarsen řeɛdařyet x wuř.” \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt Lawi 19:27; 21:5; 26:41; Irm. 9:25; 25:23; 49:32; Rum. 2:28, 29 \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\m
\v 1 “Sřem awař i zi ɣarwem dd-issawař SIDI, \add a\add* taddart n Israil!  
\v 2 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War řemmdem abrid n řegnus i yixef nnem u war ttnexřiɛem zi řeɛřamat n ujenna, waxxa řegnus ttnexřaɛen zzaysent.  
\v 3 Maɣar min ḥessben řegnus d řḥeqq aqa-t di řbaṭeř, minzi aqa aya d akeccuḍ nni dd-qessen zeg wezɣar, d řxedmet n ifassen n bu-ṣṣenɛet nni igga s imeydi n wemziř. \f ◼ \fr 10:3 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:3 \xt Ica. 44:14-17\x*  
\v 4 Zewwqen tt s nnuqart d wureɣ, s imesmiren d ifḍisen ssmetnen tt \add ařami\add* war teqqim tᵉttenxuxuř. \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Ica. 41:7\x*  
\v 5 Aqa atent am yict n tcejjart issawařen i \add din\add* ibedden, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad ssiwřen, \add ittxeṣṣa\add* ad tent arbun, minzi war zemmarent ad uyurent. War zzaysent teggʷedem ca, maɣar nitenti war zemmarent ad ggent min iɛeffnen, u \add war zemmarent\add* ad ggent min iṣebḥen.’” \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Izhd. 115:5; Ica. 41:23; 46:1, 7\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Uřa d ijj ma am Cek, \add a\add* SIDI! Cek d ameqqran u Isem nnec d ameqqran s jjehd. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Izhd. 86:8, 10\x*  
\v 7 Man wen war Cek itteggʷiden, \add Cek\add*, \add a\add* Ajeǧid n řegnus? Minzi aya yusa-dd xak, maɣar jar marra imiɣisen n řegnus u di marra tageldit nsen uřa d ijj am Cek.” \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Asa. 15:4\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 “Aqa-ten \add jmiɛ\add* d ifɣar d ibuhařiyyen, \add minzi\add* ttarbiyyet n \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen \add teffeɣ-dd\add* zeg ukeccuḍ \add waha\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Ica. 41:29; Ḥab. 2:18; Zak. 10:2\x*  
\v 9 Iwyen-dd nnuqart ittwabezzɛen zi Tarcic d wureɣ zi Ufaz, aqa-tt d řxedmet n uḥrayfi uřa n ifassen n wemziř n wureɣ. Arruḍ nsen \add n ifiřan\add* idehmaniyyen d arjuwaniyyen, marra \add řexyařat\add* ggin tent yeryazen inni ɣarsen tizemmar.”   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “SIDI AREBBI d Tidett, Netta d AREBBI iddaren, d Ajeǧid n řebda. Tammurt tᵉttenhezza s uduqqez n weɣḍab nnes uca řegnus war zemmaren \add ad ksen\add* asxeḍ nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “D man aya d asen i ɣa tinim: ‘Irebbiten nni war iggin ajenna uřa d tammurt, nitni ad ttwaqḍan zi temmurt d sadu ajenna.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “\add Maca\add* Netta igga tammurt s jjhed nnes, igga ddunect zi tiɣit u s řefhamet nnes ibezzeɛ ajenna. \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Amz. 1:1; Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2; Ica. 40:22; 44:24; 51:13; Irm. 51:15\x*  
\v 13 Řami ittejja tmijja nnes ad tt sřen, \add xenni tegga\add* am ucarcur n waman deg ujenna. Iseynuten issgeɛɛad i-ten zeg ineggura n ddunect, ittegg assamen ak-d wenẓar u issekka-dd asemmiḍ zeg ixxamen nnes n txubay.” \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Izhd. 135:7; Irm. 51:16; Asa. 14:3\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Kuř bnadem d agarruḍ, břa tussna, kuř amziř n wureɣ ittseḍḥa zi ssibbet n řexyař ineqcen \add i igga\add*, maɣar řexyař nnes ifesyen d ixarriqen, war dayes \add iǧi\add* buḥbeř. \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt Irm. 51:17, 18\x*  
\v 15 Aqa tent d \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen, aqa atent d timesřayin n tseḍḥact. Di řweqt mani tent i ɣa ɛaqben, ad fnant.  
\v 16 Tasɣart n Yaɛqub war teǧi am \add tesɣart\add* nsent, minzi Netta d Wenni iggin marra, uca Israil d taqbič n tesɣart nnes, aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Izhd. 74:2; Irm. 51:19\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Abarreḥ s tmeḥbast n Yahuda  
\m
\v 17 “Seggwej sseřɛet zi temmurt nnem, \add a cem\add* tamɣart nni izeddɣen di lqelɛa!  
\v 18 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, twařa-ya ad nḍareɣ imezdaɣ n temmurt ɣar řaggʷaj uca ad asen dd-awyeɣ di řeḥṣaret, ḥima ad ttwaṭṭfen!’ \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Irm. 6:24\x*  
\v 19 Uct inu zi ssibbet n treẓẓit inu, ayezzim inu itteqqes ayi aṭṭas. Waxxa necc nniɣ: Aya d ijj n řehřac u necc ad t ksiɣ!  
\v 20 Ittwaxarreb Uqiḍun inu, marra imurar \add n uqiḍun\add* qeṭṭsen, iḥenjiren inu uyuren xafi u war da ǧin ɛad. War din wi ɣa issbedden Aqidun inu uca ad xas yayeř tijartiřin nnes.  
\v 21 Maɣar imeksawen tuɣa qejḥen, SIDI war xas arzun. X uya war ttgeɛɛaden u marra \add taḥimart n\add* ddmani nsen tᵉttwazuzzar. \f ◼ \fr 10:21 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 22 Řeḥweř d ameqqran, aqa da, ddriz zi temmurt di ccamal, ḥima ad areddǧen tineddam n Yahuda, \add maḥend ad tt arren d tammurt n\add* tzeddiɣt i wuccanen n řexřa.” \x ◘ \xo 10:22 \xt Irm. 1:14; 4:6; 9:11\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 “Necc ssneɣ, \add a\add* SIDI, aqa war dd-teqqim ɣar bnadem ad ixḍar abrid nnes, uřa i weryaz iggur, maḥend ad indeh iṣuraf nnes. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt Awřn. 16:1; 20:24\x*  
\v 24 Seggem ayi, SIDI, maca s řḥeqq, war iǧi deg weɣḍab nnec, ḥima war d ayi tarrid d walu. \x ◘ \xo 10:24 \xt Izhd. 6:2; 38:2; Irm. 30:11; 46:28\x*  
\v 25 Zeǧeɛ asɛar nnec x řegnus nni war Cek issinen, u x tqebbař nni war ittřiɣin Isem nnec, minzi nitni ṣarḍen Yaɛqub, ṣarḍen t uca qḍan xas, hedmen amcan n tzeddiɣt nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 10:25 \xt Izhd. 79:6; Irm. 8:16; 9:16\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Řgens yarẓa Řɛahd ak-d SIDI  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 2 “Sřem i wawařen n Řɛahd-a uca siweř ak-d yeryazen n Yahuda u ak-d imezdaɣ n Urcalim,  
\v 3 ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Ittwanɛeř weryaz nni war isřin i wawařen n Řɛahd-a, \x ◘ \xo 11:3 \xt Aɛwd. 27:26; Gal. 3:10. \x*  
\v 4 wenni weṣṣiɣ i řejdud nwem deg wass umi ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra, zeg ufarran n wuzzař, \add řami\add* nniɣ: Sřem i tmijja inu uca ggem am mammec i kenniw weṣṣiɣ marra, \add xenni\add* ad ayi tiřim d řgens inu uca Necc ad awem iřiɣ d AREBBI nwem, \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt Lawi 26:3, 12; Aɛwd. 4:20\x*  
\v 5 ḥima ad menɛeɣ di tjaǧit nni jjuǧeɣ di ṭṭweɛ n řejdud nwem, maḥend ad asen wceɣ ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.’” \add Xenni\add* necc arriɣ-dd, nniɣ: “Amin, SIDI!” \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Aɛwd. 7:12\x*   
\m
\v 6 Inna ayi SIDI: “Barreḥ s marra awařen-a di tneddam n Yahuda u di dcurat n Urcalim, ini: ‘Sřem i wawařen n Řɛahd-a, ggem zzaysen,  
\v 7 maɣar Necc ɛeřmeɣ s jjehd i řejdud nwem deg wass umi ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra, zeg umezwaru ař ass-a, \add wah,\add* cehdeɣ nniɣ: Sřem ɣar tmijja inu’ \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt Irm. 7:13, 25\x*  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* nitni war sřin u war d ayi wcin amezzuɣ nsen, maca nitni ḍfaren marra idsen řeqsaḥet n wuř nsen aɛeffan. S uyenni ssiwḍeɣ xasen marra awařen n Řɛahd-a, inni x ten weṣṣiɣ maḥend ad zzaysen ggen, \add maca\add* war zzaysen ggin.’” \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Irm. 3:17; 7:24, 26; 9:14\x*   
\m
\v 9 Inna ayi SIDI: “Aqa tᵉttwaɛarra ict n tmeɛmuč jar iryazen n Yahuda u jar imezdaɣ n Urcalim.  
\v 10 Nitni dewřen-dd ɣar řmuɛṣiyyet n řejdud nsen nni yugin ad sřen ɣar wawařen inu. Nitni ruḥen ḍeffaran irebbiten nneɣni maḥend ad asen sexxaren. Taddart n Israil d taddart n Yahuda arẓin Řɛahd inu nni ggiɣ ak-d řejdud nsen.”   
\m
\v 11 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad xasen nḍareɣ ijj n řɣar i zi war zemmaren ad nejmen. \add Mařa\add* řaɣan ayi-dd \add xenni\add*, Necc war dd ɣarsen ttesřiɣ ca. \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Awřn. 1:28; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 14:12; Ḥiz. 8:18; Mixa 3:4\x*  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ad ffɣen tineddam n Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ad řaɣan ɣar irebbiten i yinni umi qeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur, \add maca\add* yina war zemmaren ad asen wcen afus di řweqt umi ten iřqef řɣar.  
\v 13 Maɣar irebbiten nnec deg waṭṭas anect n tneddam nnec, \add a\add* Yahuda, u iɛaltaren i tessbeddem i nnɛi \add n ṣṣanam\add* nni deg waṭṭas anect n ibriden n Urcalim, iɛalṭaren maḥend ad xasen wehhben tiwhibin n řebxur i Baɛl.’” \x ◘ \xo 11:13 \xt Irm. 2:28\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Cek \add xenni\add* war tᵉttar i řgens-a, war ttekkared ad asen trud niɣ ad asen tedɛid, maɣar Necc war ttesřiɣ di řweqt nni xafi dd ɣa řaɣan zi ssibbet n řɣar i ten iřeqfen.” \x ◘ \xo 11:14 \xt Irm. 7:16; 14:11\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “Min i teggid, \add a\add* tamɛizt inu, di Taddart inu, umi teǧa řefḍiḥet nnes \add d ta\add*: aqa aṭṭas ttaggʷejen xam ak-d weysum iqeddsen. Maɣar s tuɛeffna i teggid, ma tzemmared ad tnegzed s řefraḥet?  
\v 16 ‘Tazitunt tazeyzawt, \add a cem,\add* řemřaḥet, s řɣiǧet icnan di řewṣifet!’, \add ammu i\add* tuɣa igga SIDI isem nnem, \add maca\add* \add řexxu\add* iqqed as timessi am ittwaseř řḥess n ijj n zzhir d ameqqran uca ttwarẓen řefruɛ nnes.  
\v 17 SIDI n řɛeskarat, d wenni cem iẓẓun, igga xam ijj n řɣar zi ssibbet n řɣar i tegga taddart n Israil d taddart n Yahuda, \add řɣar i\add* ggint i yixef nsent umi d ayi sɛarent s tewhibin n řebxur i Baɛl.” \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Irm. 2:21\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tudart n unabi Irmiya di lxaṭař  
\m
\v 18 “SIDI isscen t ayi uca \add řexxu\add* ssneɣ, řami tessecned ayi timegga nsen.  
\v 19 Necc simant inu tuɣa ayi am yijj n yezmar aynaw n taddart, neddhen t i tɣarṣt, maɣar tuɣa war ssineɣ aqa nitni ggin ayi ijj n řfex \add umi qqaren\add*: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad nḍeyyeɛ tacejjart ak-d řɣiǧet nnes u ad tt nteḥḥa zi temmurt n yinni iddaren maḥend isem nnes war t ttidaren ɛad.’” \f ◼ \fr 11:19 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*   
\m
\v 20 “SIDI n řɛeskarat, \add a Cek\add* Řqaḍi iseggden nni ittjarraben tiẓẓař d wuř, scen ayi nneqmet nnec, maɣar necc sellmeɣ ddeɛwet inu deg ifassen nnec.” \f ◼ \fr 11:20 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:20 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:7; 1 Im. 28:9; Izhd. 7:10; 26:2; Asa. 2:23\x*   
\m
\v 21 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x yeryazen n Ɛanatut, inni yarezzun řeɛmar nnec, qqaren: ‘War ttnab s Yisem n SIDI ařami war tmettid s ufus nneɣ.’  
\v 22 S uya, \add ammu\add* i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ten xeǧṣeɣ: iḥudriyyen ad mmten s ssif, iḥenjiren d yessitsen ad mmten s řaẓ.  
\v 23 War ittɣimi min iqqimen zzaysen, maɣar Necc ad xasen dd-ssiwḍeɣ ijj n řɣar d aɛeffan x yeryazen n Ɛanatut deg useggʷas nni di ten i ɣa xeǧṣeɣ.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Acetci n Irmiya  
\m
\v 1 “Mařa ggiɣ ad carrɛeɣ akidek, \add a\add* SIDI, Cek \add ad tbaned\add* d amsegged. Qaɛ amenni ttexseɣ ad siwřeɣ akidek x ibriden n řḥeqq: Mayemmi abrid n iɛeffanen iseggem, \add u\add* mayemmi iɣeddaren řebda di arraḥet? \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt Ayub 21:7; Izhd. 73:11, 12; Ḥab. 1:3\x*  
\v 2 Cek teẓẓud ten u nitni wtin iẓewran, nitni ɣemyen-dd u iwyen-dd řɣiǧet. Cek aqa tudsed aqemmum nsen, maca tiggʷejed x tiẓẓař nsen.” \f ◼ \fr 12:2 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘uř’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Ica. 29:13\x*   
\m
\v 3 “Cek, \add a\add* SIDI, tessned ayi, tᵉttwarid ayi u tqeǧbed uř inu, \add ma\add* aqa-t akidek. Jbed i-ten am wuǧi i tɣarṣt u ɛzeř i-ten i wass n wenɣay. \f ◼ \fr 12:3 \ft \+fk ɛzeř i-ten\ft  - s lḥarf: ‘qeddes i-ten’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Izhd. 17:3; 139:1; Irm. 11:20\x*  
\v 4 Mecḥař ɛad i ɣa tekk temmurt tecḍen u afsu \add aziza\add* ad yaẓeɣ deg iyyar marra? S tuɛeffna n yinni din izeddɣen ḍeyyɛen řmař d yejḍaḍ, maɣar nitni qqaren: ‘Netta war ittwiři aneggar nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Irm. 4:25; 7:20; 9:10\x*   
\m
\v 5 “Mařa tuzzřed ak-d inni ittazzřen x iḍaren, nitni ssaḥařen cek, mammec texsed ad tegged \add xenni\add* ḥamat ak-d iysan? Mařa tᵉttacid aqa cek di řaman mɣir di temmurt n řehna, mammec ɣa tegged \add xenni\add* di cbarq iqqnen n \add yeɣzar n\add* L’Urdun?  
\v 6 Maɣar uřa d aytmac d taddart n babac, uřa d nitni ɣeddaren cek, uřa d nitni sɣuyyun s jjhed awarni ac. War ten ttiqqem, waxxa ssawařen akidek mliḥ.” \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Awřn. 26:25\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Acetci n SIDI x Yahuda u x řegnus i d as dd-innḍen  
\m
\v 7 “Necc semḥeɣ di taddart inu, Necc nḍareɣ tasɣart inu. Tenni issɛizz řeɛmar inu sellmeɣ tt deg ufus n řɛedyan nnes.  
\v 8 Tasɣart inu tedweř-dd akidi am yijj n wayrad deg wezɣar. Tessgeɛɛed-dd akidi tmijja nnes, x uya Necc dewřeɣ carrheɣ tt. \f ◼ \fr 12:8 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 9 Tasɣart inu i Necc \add am\add* ujḍiḍ ibeqqḍen ittkeccaḍen. Ttennḍen as ijḍaḍ ikeccḍen. Kkarem, smunem-dd marra řmař n yeyyar, ejj i-ten ad dd-asen ḥima ad ccen!” \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt Irm. 7:33\x*   
\m
\v 10 “Imeksawen aṭṭas xarrben amarjeɛ inu n uḍiř, ɛefsen x yeyyar inu, aqa arrin iyyar iɛizzen inu d ijj n řexřa ixwa. \f ◼ \fr 12:10 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ: ‘iničan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt Irm. 6:3\x*  
\v 11 Arrin \add iyyar\add* d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen, aqa ittwaxarreb \add yeyyar\add*, izzeř zzati icḍen. Marra tammurt txarreb minzi uřa d ijj war d as yecqi.  
\v 12 X marra tiwririn iqeccaren di řexřa usin-dd imteḥḥayyen, maɣar ssif isarḍ zi ṭṭarf n temmurt ař ṭṭarf \add nneɣni\add* n temmurt. War din iqqim řehna i marra ddat.  
\v 13 Nitni zarɛen irden, \add maca\add* mjaren isennanen, nitni uḥřen, maca břa nnfaɛ. Nitni ad seḍḥan x ṣṣabet nwem zi ssibbet n řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt Lawi 26:16; Aɛwd. 28:38\x*   
\m
\v 14 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Marra ajjaren inu iɛeffanen nni ittḥadan tasɣart inu i wciɣ i řgens inu Israil d tasɣart, xzar, Necc ad ten qeřɛeɣ zi temmurt, \add maca\add* taddart n Yahuda ad tt qeřɛeɣ zi řwesṭ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Aɛwd. 30:3; Irm. 32:37\x*  
\v 15 Awarni řami ten qeřɛeɣ, ad dd-dewřeɣ u ad xasen ḥinneɣ uca Necc ad ten arreɣ ad ɛeqben, kuř ijj ɣar tesɣart nnes u kuř ijj ɣar temmurt nnes.  
\v 16 Xmi ɣa řemden s tidett ibriden n řgens inu maḥend ad jjaǧen ɣar Yisem inu: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI!’, am mammec nitni ssřemden řgens inu maḥend ad jjaǧen ɣar Baɛl, \add xenni\add* ad ttwassbedden nitni di řwesṭ n řgens inu.  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* mařa nitni war ttexsen ad sřen, \add xenni\add* Necc ad qeřɛeɣ řgens nni uca ad ten areddǧeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt Ica. 60:12\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Abyas n řeqṭen  
\m
\v 1 “Ammu i d ayi inna SIDI: ‘Uyur, seɣ i yixef nnec ijj n webyas n řeqṭen uca beys i-t x tejɛinnatin nnec, \add maca\add* war t tejji ad yadef deg waman!’  
\v 2 Necc sɣiɣ ijj n webyas ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI uca beyseɣ t x tejɛinnatin inu.  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI i twařa wiss tnayen, inna:  
\v 4 ‘Ksi abyas i tesɣid, nni tbeysed x tejɛinnatin nnec uca kkar, uyur ɣar \add yeɣẓar n\add* Lfuraṭ uca ffar i-t dinni di tazzect n jjarf.’  
\v 5 Necc uyureɣ uca ffareɣ t ɣar Lfuraṭ, am mammec tuɣa d ayi yumur SIDI.”   
\m
\v 6 “Awarni i waṭṭas n wussan inna ayi SIDI: ‘Kkar, uyur ɣar Lfuraṭ uca ksi ssenni abyas nni d ac umureɣ maḥend ad t teffared dinni.’  
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* uyureɣ ɣar Lfuraṭ uca ɣziɣ u kkseɣ-dd abyas zeg wemcan mani t tuɣa ffareɣ. Xzar, abyas iḍeyyeɛ, war iǧi min umi ɣa infiɛ ɛad.   
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 9 ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ammu i ɣa ssḍeyyɛeɣ nnfaxet n Yahuda uřa d nnfaxet tameqqrant n Urcalim.  
\v 10 Řgens-a aɛeffan nni yugin ad iseř ɣar wawařen inu, nni iḍeffaren řeqsaḥet n wuř nnes uca yareddef irebbiten nneɣni maḥend ad ten iɛbed u ad asen ibendeq, \add řgens-a\add* ad idweř am webyas-a i war ineffɛen i walu ɛad.  
\v 11 Maɣar mammec iqqen webyas i tejɛinnatin n weryaz, ammu i arriɣ marra taddart n Israil d marra taddart n Yahuda ad ɣari qqnent, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maḥend ad iřint d řgens inu d Yisem inu d ccan inu d uɛuǧi inu, \add maca\add* nitni war sřin ca.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Iqedduḥen iccuren s binu  
\m
\v 12 “Cek ad asen tinid awař-a: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Qaɛ aɣarraf ad ittwaccur s binu.’ \add Xenni\add* ad ac inin nitni: ‘Ma \add zeɛma\add* neccin war nessin simant nneɣ nican, aqa qaɛ aɣarraf ad ittwaccur s binu?’  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* ad d asen tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad arreɣ ad scaren marra imezdaɣ n temmurt-a, ijeǧiden nni iqqimen x řɛarc n Dawud, ikehhanen, inabiyyen d marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim.  
\v 14 Necc ad ten wteɣ d iwetwiten, ijj ak-d wenneɣni, ibabaten munen ak-d iḥenjiren, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Necc war ttḥinniɣ, war ssɛizziɣ u war areḥḥmeɣ maḥend war ten ttḍeyyiɛeɣ.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 SIDI issawař s imedya nneɣni  
\m
\v 15 “Sřem u wcem amezzuɣ, war ttnefxem, maɣar SIDI issiweř.  
\v 16 Wcem ccan i SIDI, AREBBI nwem, qbeř i dd ɣa tas taǧest u qbeř i ɣa nqarḍen iḍaren nwem x idurar ibbubsen, \add am\add* tᵉttrajam tafawt, \add maca\add* Netta ad tt yarr d tiři n unuri uřa d aseynu ibbumbes. \x ◘ \xo 13:16 \xt Izhd. 44:20\x*  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* mařa kenniw war tᵉttexsem ad tesřem, \add xenni\add* ad iru řeɛmar inu di tnuffra x nnfaxet \add nwem\add*, ad iksi deg imeṭṭawen, uca ad dd-ssehwan imeṭṭawen zi tiṭṭawin inu, maɣar taḥimart n SIDI aqa tᵉttwandeh di tmeḥbast.” \x ◘ \xo 13:17 \xt Igjd. 1:2, 16\x*   
\m
\v 18 “Ini i ujeǧid d yemmas n ujeǧid: ‘Swaḍɛem ixef nwem, qqimem deg wemcan ihwa, maɣar ttaj nwem icuwwaren tewḍa awem-dd x uzeǧif.’  
\v 19 Ttwabellɛent tneddam n \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub, uca uřa d ijj war tent yarezzem. Aqa ittwandeh marra \add řgens n\add* Yahuda ittwandeh imun.  
\v 20 Sgeɛɛdem tiṭṭawin nwem, u xzarem, man wen i dd-yusin zi ccamal! Mani teǧa tḥimart i d am immewcen, uǧi nnem icewwaren? \f ◼ \fr 13:20 \ft \+fk i d am immewcen\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘i immewcen i yeǧis n Ṣihyun’.\f*  
\v 21 Min ɣa tinid mařa Netta igga d azeǧif xam inni i tessřemded maḥend ad iřin d imeddukkař nnem iɛizzen? Ma war cem dd-mennɛen řewjeɛ am yict n temɣart ittarwen?”   
\m
\v 22 “Xmi ɣa tinid deg wuř nnem: ‘Mayemmi d ayi iřqef \add marra\add* aya?’, \add ssen aqa:\add* ‘X ubarru n řmuɛṣiyyet nnem ttwassgeɛɛdent xam timmawin \add n warruḍ\add*, ttwadeǧen inirzen nnem’. \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt Ica. 47:2, 3; Irm. 5:19; 16:10\x*  
\v 23 Ma izemmar ijj \add n weryaz\add* zi \add temmurt n\add* Kuc ad ibeddeř smex n teřmect nnes? Niɣ aɣiřas areqqiɛen nnes? Ma tzemmarem uřa d kenniw \add xenni\add* ad tɛedřem, \add kenniw\add* inni innumen tuɛeffna.  
\v 24 S uyenni Necc ad ten zuzzareɣ am uřum nni iṭṭawen s usuḍi n usemmiḍ n řexřa.  
\v 25 Wa ad yiři d zzhar nnem i d am dd-ikkaren zzayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, minzi cem tᵉttud ayi u tᵉttecřed x ixarriqen.  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* uřa d Necc ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ ibeḥruren \add n warruḍ\add* nnem ař tiwa aɣembub nnem uca ad ẓaren řefḍiḥet nnem:  
\v 27 zzina nnem d usneḥneḥ inezren nnem, farq-ccɣeř nnem infeḍḥen. X tewririn u deg iyyar ẓriɣ nnɛawat nnem n l’aṣnam. Uct xam, \add a\add* Urcalim, ař meřmi war tᵉttwassizdiged ca ɛad \add zzaysent\add*?”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Awař n SIDI x řaẓaɣ ameqqran  
\m
\v 1 Awař n SIDI i dd-yusin ɣar Irmiya x řaẓaɣ ameqqran.   
\m
\v 2 “\add Tammurt n\add* Yahuda tecḍen uca tiwwura nnes heyyfent. Qqimen nitni x temmurt \add s werruḍ\add* d abarcan, uca tɣuyyit n ucetci n Urcalim tgeɛɛed ɣar ujenna.  
\v 3 Ayt n jjehd sekken ixemmasen nsen imuqřiřen maḥend ad aymen aman. Řami dd-usin nitni ɣar wanuten n wenẓar, war daysen ufin aman. Nitni ɛeqben-dd s ibuqaren nsen xwan, seḍḥan, ucin s ubarreq uca řeḥḥfen i uzeǧif nsen,  
\v 4 minzi tᵉttwacarreg temmurt, maɣar war din anẓar di temmurt. Ifeǧaḥen ttseḍḥan, ttřeḥḥafen i uzeǧif nsen.  
\v 5 Wah, uřa d tudadt deg iyyar turuw-dd mmis, \add maca xenni\add* tesmeḥ dayes, minzi war din iqqim arbiɛ ɛad.  
\v 6 Iɣyař n řexřa bedden x tewririn iquccaren, ssɣatan ɣar řeɛwin am wuccanen n řexřa. Tiṭṭawin nsen xesyent maɣar war iqqim wefsu \add aziza\add* ɛad.” \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Irm. 12:4\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Waxxa cehhdent xaneɣ řmuɛṣiyyat nneɣ, \add a\add* SIDI, egg i-t di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnec, maɣar aweddar nneɣ deg waṭṭas, aqa nexḍa akidek.  
\v 8 \add Cek\add* d řayas n Israil, \add Cek\add* d Amsenjem nnes di řweqt n řeḥṣaret, mayemmi ɣa tiřid am yijj n ubarrani di temmurt, am yijj n umsebrid ittnusan ǧiřet waha?  
\v 9 Mayemmi teǧid am yijj n weryaz iweddaren, am yijj n bu-teɣruḍt i war izemmaren ad ifekk? Aqa Cek di řwesṭ nneɣ, \add a\add* SIDI, Isem nnec ittwabarreḥ xaneɣ, war dayneɣ semmeḥ!”   
\m
\v 10 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI x řgens-a: ‘Tuɣa iɛjeb asen ad telɛen, war ssɛizzen x iḍaren nsen. S uyenni SIDI war xasen yarḍa. Řexxu ad yidar Netta řmuɛṣiyyet nsen uca ad ixeǧeṣ ddnub nsen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Inna ayi SIDI: “War tᵉttar i řgens-a maḥend ad yiři mliḥ! \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Uf. 32:10; Irm. 7:16; 11:14\x*  
\v 12 Waxxa ẓummen, Necc war ttesřiɣ ca ɣar tɣuyyit nsen, \add waxxa\add* nitni iwyen ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, Necc war xasen arḍiɣ ca, maɣar Necc ad ten qḍiɣ s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun.”\x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt Awřn. 1:28; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 6:20; 7:21, 22; 11:11; Ḥiz. 8:18; Mixa 3:4\x*   
\m
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* nniɣ necc: “Wayyaw, a Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, inabiyyen qqaren asen: ‘Kenniw war tẓarrem ssif, war ittiři řaẓ, maɣar Necc ad awem wceɣ řehna d tidett deg wemcan-a’”  
\v 14 Inna ayi SIDI: “Inabiyyen ttnebban s ixarriqen s Yisem inu. Necc war ten dd-ssekkeɣ, war ten umureɣ u war kidsen ssiwřeɣ. Nitni ttnabben ijj n řewḥiy war iǧin i kenniw, aɛezzem, min ibeḍřen d wecmat n wuř \add n yixef\add* nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 14:14 \xt Irm. 23:21; 27:15; 29:8, 9\x*   
\m
\v 15 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: “X inabiyyen nni ittnebban s Yisem inu, waxxa Necc war ten dd-ssekkeɣ ca, uca qqaren: ‘War ittiři ssif uřa d řaẓ di temmurt-a!’, aqa inabiyyen nni ad ttwaqḍan s ssif d řaẓ.  
\v 16 Řgens umi nebban, ad immenḍar deg ibriden n Urcalim zi ssibbet n řaẓ d ssif, uca war ittiři wi ten i ɣa ineḍřen: nitni, timɣarin nsen, iḥenjiren nsen d tḥenjirin nsen. Ammu d xasen i ɣa zeǧɛeɣ řɣar \add n yixef\add* nsen.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Acḍan n unabi  
\m
\v 17 “S uyenni ad asen tinid awař-a: ‘Imeṭṭawen ad dd-ssefyent zi tiṭṭawin inu ad dd-hwant, ǧiřet d wass, břa qeṭṭu!’ Maɣar tᵉttwarẓ teɛzarect, iǧis n řgens inu, s tareẓẓit d tameqqrant, s uyezzim itteqqes aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 14:17 \xt Irm. 13:17; Igjd. 1:16; 2:18\x*  
\v 18 Xmi ɣa ffɣeɣ, ɣar yeyyar, aqa da inni ittwassnuqqben s ssif, u xmi ɣa adfeɣ ɣar tendint, xzar, inni iheřcen s řaẓ! Wah, inabiyyen d ikehhanen tᵉttliɛen deg ict n temmurt i war ssinen.  
\v 19 Ma tenḍared Cek Yahuda marra? Ma icarreh řeɛmar nnec Ṣihyun? Mayemmi d aneɣ tewtid ammu ařami war d aneɣ iqqim bu ugenfu? Sittimen ad yiři řehna, maca war din amcan i řxar, sittimen deg ijj n řweqt n ugenfi, \add maca\add* xzar, \add mɣir\add* asnexřiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:19 \xt Irm. 8:15\x*  
\v 20 \add A\add* SIDI, neccin war nessin řɣar nneɣ d řmuɛṣiyyet n řejdud nneɣ, maɣar neccin nexḍa akidek. \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Izhd. 106:6; Dan. 9:8\x*  
\v 21 War d aneɣ sseḥqara ca di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnec, war sseḥqara řɛarc n uɛuǧi nnec. Idar aneɣ, war tareẓẓa Řɛahd i kidneɣ teggid!  
\v 22 Ma aqa din jar \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen n řegnus \add l’aṣnam\add* nni izemmaren ad wcen anẓar, niɣ ccaten ijenwan s wenẓar s simant nsen? Ma war iǧi d Cek, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ? S uyenni ad Cek nraja, maɣar Cek i itteggen marra aya.” \x ◘ \xo 14:22 \xt Izhd. 135:7; 147:8; Ica. 30:23; Irm. 5:24; 10:13\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Tamwarrit n SIDI  
\m
\v 1 Inna ayi SIDI: “Waxxa mařa ibedd Musa d Camwil zzat i wudem inu, ɛad war ittiři řeɛmar inu ak-d řgens-a. Siggʷej i-ten zi zzat n wudem inu, ejj i-ten ad uyuren. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt Uf. 32:14; 1 Ṣm. 7:9; Ḥiz. 14:14, 20\x*  
\v 2 Xmi d ac i ɣa inin: ‘Mani ɣa nuyur?’, \add xenni\add* ad asen tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Wi \add iǧan\add* i řmewt, ɣar řmewt, wi \add iǧan\add* i ssif, ɣar ssif, wi \add iǧan\add* i řaẓ, ɣar řaẓ u wi \add iǧan\add* i řeḥbes, ɣar řeḥbes!’\x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Zak. 11:9; Asa. 13:10\x*  
\v 3 Ad ten xeǧṣeɣ s arebɛa n webriden, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: s ssif ařami ɣa ttwanɣen, s yiṭan ařami \add ten\add* jarren zeg webrid, s ijḍaḍ n ujenna d řewḥuc n temmurt ař ɣa ttwaṣarḍen u ad ttwareddǧen. \x ◘ \xo 15:3 \xt Lawi 26:16; Irm. 7:33\x*  
\v 4 Necc ad ten arreɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect zi ssibbet n Manassa, mmis n Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d axřaf zi min igga di Urcalim.” \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt Aɛwd. 28:25\x*   
\m
\v 5 “Maɣar man wen umi ɣa tezziǧed, \add a\add* Urcalim? Wi d am i ɣa issḥissfen niɣ wi dd ɣa iffɣen zeg webrid maḥend ad xam isseqsa x umeddur nnem? \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Ica. 51:19\x*  
\v 6 Cem tsemḥed dayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, tdewřed ɣar ḍeffar. S uyenni i ɣa sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnem uca ad cem areddǧeɣ. Necc uḥreɣ s uḥinni xawem.” \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Irm. 5:7\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Necc ad ten zuzzareɣ s ǧuḥ di tewwura n temmurt. Necc keccḍeɣ iḥenjiren zi řgens inu uca sshellkeɣ \add ten\add*. Nitni war dd-dwiřen ca zeg ibriden nsen \add iɛeffanen\add*.\x ◘ \xo 15:7 \xt Irm. 4:11\x*  
\v 8 Tijjař nsen ad iřint wesɛent x yejdi n řebḥurat. Di ṭṭya n wass ad xasen ssiwḍeɣ ijj n umteḥḥay, x yemmas d uḥudri. Deɣya ad xas wḍiɣ Necc s tiggʷudi d inexřiɛen. \f ◼ \fr 15:8 \ft \+fk x yemmas n uḥuḍri\ft  - xzar ɛawed Irm. 15:9.\f*  
\v 9 Tenni i dd-yurwen sebɛa n iḥenjiren, texsi. Nettat tedřeq i buḥbeř nnes, teɣři tfuct nnes am iǧa ɛad d wass. Nettat tᵉttseḍḥa uca tᵉtteṭṭef i-tt i-dd řefḍiḥet. Min iqqimen zzaysen ad t wceɣ i ssif zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 15:9 \xt Ɛam. 8:9\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amenɣi deg wuř n Irmiya  
\m
\v 10 “Uct xafi, yemma, aqa cem turwed ayi-dd: ijj n weryaz n umcubbec, ijj n weryaz n umenɣi i marra tammurt. Necc war d asent arḍřeɣ uca nitni war d ayi ttᵉttursen, waxxa amenni marra neɛɛřen ayi.” \f ◼ \fr 15:10 \ft \+bd afessar\+bd* - anabi Irmiya issawař.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Ayub 3; Irm. 20:14-18\x*  
\v 11 Inna SIDI: “\add Ah\add*, mařa Necc war teggeɣ s tcuni akidek, mařa Necc war ggiɣ ad cek iḥcem řeɛdu di řweqt n tecti taɛeffant u di řweqt n řeḥṣaret.”  
\v 12 Ma izemmar bnadem ad yarẓ uzzař, uzzař i dd-yusin zi ccamal, niɣ nnḥas? \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Irm. 6:28\x*  
\v 13 Agřa nnec d řeknuz nnec ad ten wceɣ d takeccaḍt i řegnus, břa ttaman, zi ssibbet n marra ddnub nnec uca \add aya\add* di marra tammurt nnec. \x ◘ \xo 15:13 \xt Irm. 17:3\x*  
\v 14 Necc ad \add cek\add* sseɛduɣ ak-d řeɛdu nnec ɣar ict n temmurt nni war tessined ca, maɣar s weɣḍab inu tarɣa tmessi nni i ɣa iqqimen tcemmeḍ ḍidd nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 15:14 \xt Aɛwd. 32:22\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “\add A\add* SIDI, Cek tessned tt, idar ayi uca řha-dd akidi! Ntaqem ayi zeg yinni d ayi iḍeffaren! War d ayi ttekkes, minzi ɣarek ttasiɛ n řxaḍar aṭṭas. Ssen aqa necc ad xak ksiɣ řɛar di ṭṭweɛ nnec. \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Irm. 11:20\x*  
\v 16 Umi ttwafen wawařen nnec, cciɣ ten deɣya. Awař nnec tuɣa-t i necc d arcuq d řefraḥet i wuř inu maɣar ittwabarreḥ Isem nnec di tiwa inu, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat.   
\m
\v 17 Necc war ttɣimiɣ ca deg wegraw n yinni istehzan, war neggzeɣ s řefraḥet. Zi ssibbet n ufus nnec ttɣimiɣ weḥḥdi, maɣar teccured ayi s wesxeḍ nnec. \x ◘ \xo 15:17 \xt Izhd. 1:1\x*  
\v 18 Mayemmi řeḥriq inu iddar řebda u mayemmi war izemmar uyezzim inu ɛemmarṣ ad iggenfa, ma netta yugi ad iggenfa? Ma s tidett aqa Cek am waman inhewřen inni war di iǧi řaman?” \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt Ayub 6:15-30; Irm. 30:15\x*   
\m
\v 19 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Mařa cek tdewřed-dd, Necc ad cek arreɣ ad dd-tdewřed u ad tbedded zzat i wudem inu. Mařa tessiwřed min iɣřan deg wemcan n min war isekkwin walu, \add xenni\add* ad tiřid am uqemmum inu. Ejj i-ten ad ɣarek dd-dewřen, maca cek war tzemmared ad ɣarsen dd-tdewřed.  
\v 20 Maɣar Necc ad cek ggeɣ i řgens-a d řḥiḍ imetnen n nnḥas. Ad kidek mmenɣen, \add maca\add* nitni war zemmaren ad cek arenyen, maɣar Necc akidek ḥima ad cek ssnejmeɣ u ḥima ad cek fekkeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.\x ◘ \xo 15:20 \xt Irm. 1:18\x*  
\v 21 Necc ad cek fekkeɣ zeg ufus n iɛeffanen u Necc ad cek fdiɣ zeg wemnaɛ n ayt n bu-řexcunet.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 SIDI issawař ak-d Irmiya  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “War ttawi tamɣart i yixef nnec u war ɣarek ttiřin iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin deg wemcan-a,  
\v 3 maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI x iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin i dd ɣa ittwurwen deg wemcan-a u x yemmatsen i ten dd-yurwen u x babatsen i ten dd-ijjin di temmurt-a:  
\v 4 ‘Nitni ad mmten s ibriden iwɛaren aṭṭas, war xasen ceṭṭen u war ten neṭṭřen, nitni ad dewřen d řeɣbar i wudem n temmurt uca ad ttwaɣezzen s ssif d řaẓ, u řxecbat nsen ad dewřent d macca i ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i řewḥuc n řexřa.’” \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt Irm. 7:33; 9:22; 14:16; 15:2, 3; 25:33; 34:20\x*   
\m
\v 5 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War ttadef ɣar ict n taddart n wecḍan u war ccat agejdur, war areḥḥem, maɣar Necc kkseɣ řehna inu x řgens-a, tamexsiwt inu icewwaren d arreḥmet, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’  
\v 6 Imeqqranen d imeẓyanen ad mmten di temmurt-a. War ten neṭṭřen, war xasen ccaten agejdur, war xebbcen ixef nsen niɣ ad ssquccaren ixef nsen di ṭṭweɛ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 16:6 \xt Lawi 19:28; Aɛwd. 14:1\x*  
\v 7 War d asen ittwarẓ weɣrum zi ssibbet n wecḍan ḥima ad ɛezzan ca n yijjen x ijj n umetti, u war d asen tticen ad swen zeg uɣarraf n uɛezzi x babas niɣ yemmas. \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt Mt. 26:26-28; Mk. 14:22-24; Lk. 22:19-20\x*  
\v 8 War ttadef ɣar taddart mani tteggen zzardet maḥend ad teqqimed ɣarsen i macca d tsessit.  
\v 9 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad ssbeddeɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem deg wemcan-a tmijja n warcaq d tmijja n řefraḥet, tmijja n muřay d tmijja n tesřit.” \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Ica. 24:7, 8; Irm. 7:34; 25:10; Ḥiz. 26:13\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “Xmi ɣa tbarrḥed marra awařen-a i řgens-a uca nitni ad sseqsan: ‘Mayemmi iqqar SIDI marra řɣar-a ameqqran xaneɣ u min \add iǧan\add* d ljarima nneɣ u min iǧan d ddenb nneɣ i negga neccin ak-d SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ?’, \x ◘ \xo 16:10 \xt Irm. 5:19\x*  
\v 11 \add xenni\add* ad asen tinid: ‘Maɣar řejdud nwem semḥen dayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, uca uyuren awarni i irebbiten nneɣni uca ɛebden u sejden asen, \add maca\add* semḥen dayi u war ḥḍin Ccariɛa inu.  
\v 12 U kenniw simant nwem teggim mahu x řejdud nwem, minzi xzar, kuř ijj zzaywem iḍaffar řeqsaḥet n wuř nnes aɛeffan, ařami kenniw war dd ɣari tesřim \add qaɛ\add*. \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Irm. 3:17; 7:26; 9:14; 11:10; 13:10; 17:23\x*  
\v 13 S uyenni ad kenniw ḥejjareɣ ɣar barra zi temmurt-a ɣar ict n temmurt i war tessinem kenniw uřa d řejdud nwem, uca dinni i ɣa tɛebdem irebbiten nneɣni, ass d ǧiřet, minzi Necc war ɣarwem dd-ttarzifeɣ ɛad s ca n řxaḍar.’” \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Aɛwd. 4:27; 28:64, 65\x*   
\m
\v 14 “S uya, xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, nni di war qqaren ɛad: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI i dd issuffɣen ayt n Israil zi Miṣra!’ \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt Irm. 23:7, 8\x*  
\v 15 maca: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI wenni dd-issuffɣen ayt n Israil zi temmurt n ccamal u zi marra timmura mani xasen yuẓẓeř!’ Minzi Necc ad ten arreɣ ɣar temmurt nni wciɣ i řejdud nsen.  
\v 16 Xzar, Necc ad ssekkeɣ aṭṭas n ineymaren n iseřman, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, inni ten i ɣa ymaren, u xenni ad ssekkeɣ aṭṭas n ineymaren nni xasen i ɣa yaẓẓřen zi mkuř adrar u zi mkuř tawrirt u zeg ifeǧiqen jar řejruf.  
\v 17 Maɣar tiṭṭawin inu ttwařant marra ibriden nsen, nitni war zemmaren ad zzayi nnuffaren uca řmuɛṣiyyet nsen war tzemmar ad tennuffar zzat i tiṭṭawin inu. \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt Ayub 34:21; Awřn. 5:21; Irm. 32:19\x*  
\v 18 Amezwar ad xeřfeɣ s uḍeffus \add marra\add* řmuɛṣiyyet nsen d marra ddnub nsen, minzi nitni ssɛiǧten tammurt inu. Nitni ccuren tasɣart inu s řxecbat n nnɛawat n l’aṣnam nsen u s jjɛayef nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Irm. 3:2; Ḥiz. 43:7\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “\add A\add* SIDI, Cek d Jjehd inu d Lburj inu d amcan inu n tarewřa deg wass n řeḥṣaret. Ad ɣarek dd-asen řegnus zeg ineggura n ddunect, ad inin: ‘Tasɣart nni ṭṭfen řejdud nneɣ, \add dayes mɣir\add* acmat d \add aɛbed n l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭiřen, timesřayin i war ineffɛen.’  
\v 20 Ma izemmar bnadem ad igg irebbiten i yixef nnes? Nitni war ǧin d irebbiten.  
\v 21 S uya, xzar, twařa-ya Necc ad ten arreɣ ad cehden, ad ten arreɣ ad ssnen afus inu d jjehd inu, uca \add xenni\add* ad ssnen belli Isem inu ‘SIDI’.” \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Irm. 33:2\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Ddnub n Yahuda  
\m
\v 1 “Ittwaxbec ddenb n Yahuda s pluma n wuzzař, s txeft n ijj n umesmir di teřwiḥt n wuř nsen u deg waccawen n iɛalṭaren nnec. \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Irm. 11:13\x*  
\v 2 Am mammec ttidaren tarwa nsen, ttidaren nitni uřa d iɛalṭaren nsen d trebbin nsen n cwarti ɣar tcejjura tizizawin x tewririn yuɛřan. \x ◘ \xo 17:2 \xt Irm. 2:20\x*  
\v 3 Adrar inu deg iyyar d wagřa nnec d marra řeknuz nnec ad ten wceɣ d takeccaḍt, uřa d řegɛudi nnec \add mani tᵉttwehhbed ddbayeḥ\add*, zi ssibbet n ddnub di marra tammurt nnec. \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt Irm. 15:13\x*  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad tarxud zi tesɣart nnec nni d ac wciɣ u man aya zi ssibbet n \add ddnub n\add* yixef nnec. Necc ad cek ggeɣ d ismeɣ n řɛedyan nnec deg ict n temmurt i war tessined ca, maɣar kenniw tarrim ict n tmessi ad tsareɣ weɣḍab inu nni i ɣa iqqimen icemmeḍ i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 17:4 \xt Aɛwd. 28:68; Irm. 15:14; 16:13\x*   
\m
\v 5 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ad ittwanɛeř weryaz nni ittcařen x bnadem uca igga ddat d uɣiř nnes \add i xef ittɛemmed\add*, u wenni uř nnes iḥeyyed x SIDI.  
\v 6 S minzi ad yiři d řɛerɛar di řexřa, wenni war ittacan x minni dd ɣa yas min icnan, d wenni i ɣa iqqimen deg imucan ittwacemḍen s řeḥmu di řexřa, deg ict temmurt tameǧaḥt war izdiɣen.  
\v 7 Ad ittwabarek weryaz nni ittcařen x SIDI d wenni iggin SIDI d řaman nnes. \x ◘ \xo 17:7 \xt Izhd. 2:12; 34:9; Awřn. 16:20; Ica. 30:18\x*  
\v 8 Ad yiři am tcejjart i ittwaẓẓun ɣar tiɣezratin n waman, tenni iwtin iẓewran nnes ɣar teɣzart. War tessin ca meřmi dd ɣa yas řehmu u tifray nnes ad qqiment d tiziyzawin. Deg ijj n useggʷas n řaẓaɣ war tᵉttisřiw ca uca war tᵉttbeddi ad teksi řɣiǧet nnes.’” \f ◼ \fr 17:8 \ft \+fk tacejjart\ft  - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:8 \xt Izhd. 1:3\x*   
\m
\v 9 “Uř d aɣeddar sennej x kuřci, war izemmar ad iggenfa, wi izemmaren ad t issen?  
\v 10 Necc, SIDI, arezzuɣ deg wuř u ttjarrabeɣ tiẓẓař, ḥima ad xeǧṣeɣ kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab tibridin nnes, ɛlaḥsab řɣiǧet n tmegga nnes. \f ◼ \fr 17:10 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:10 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:7; Izhd. 7:10\x*  
\v 11 Am ict n tsekkurt i issguṭṭyen x \add tmeǧařin\add* nni war dd-turuw, ammu i iǧa wenni iggin agřa, \add maca\add* war iǧi s řḥeqq. Di řwesṭ n wussan nnes ittxeṣṣa ad daysen ismeḥ u ɣar uneggaru nnes ad idweř d abuhaři.”   
\b  
\m
\v 12 “Ijj n řɛarc igdaren s uɛuǧi, yuɛřan aṭṭas zeg umezwaru, \add ammu i yeǧa\add* amcan n Zzawect nneɣ Iqeddsen.  
\v 13 \add Cek\add* d Řayas n Israil, \add a\add* SIDI, marra inni xak iḥeyyden, ad nfeḍḥen. Inni xafi iḥeyyden, ad twarin \add ismawen nsen\add* deg ucař, maɣar nitni semḥen di SIDI, řɛunṣar n waman iddaren. \x ◘ \xo 17:13 \xt Izhd. 73:27; Ica. 1:28; Irm. 2:13; Yḥ. 8:8\x*  
\v 14 Sgenfa ayi, SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad ggenfiɣ, senjem ayi, \add xenni\add* ad ttwassnejmeɣ, maɣar Cek d izři n uṣebbeḥ inu.  
\v 15 Xzar, nitni qqaren ayi: ‘Mani iǧa wawař n SIDI? Ejj i-t ad dd-ixecc!’ \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt Ica. 5:19; 2 Bṭ. 3:4\x*  
\v 16 Necc ɛemmarṣ war ḥṣareɣ ixef inu maḥend ad iřiɣ d ameksaw awarni ac, war meẓriɣ ɣar wass n arẓiyyet. Cek tessned t: min i d ayi dd-yusin x iyencicen inu, iffeɣ-dd zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec.  
\v 17 War d ayi snexřiɛ ca, Cek d adurri inu deg wass n řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 17:17 \xt Irm. 16:19\x*  
\v 18 Ejj inni d ayi iḍaffaren ad nfeḍḥen, maca war d ayi ttejji ad nfeḍḥeɣ, ejj i-ten ad nxeřɛen, maca war d ayi ttejji ad nxeřɛeɣ. Siweḍ-dd xasen ass n řɣar uca arẓ i-ten s ict n tareẓẓit s weḍfas.” \x ◘ \xo 17:18 \xt Izhd. 35:4; 40:15; Irm. 15:15\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “Ammu i ɣari dd-issiweř SIDI: ‘Uyur uca bedd di tewwart n iḥenjiren n řgens, \add tawwurt\add* i zi ttadfen ijeǧiden n Yahuda u i zi dd-tteffɣen nitnu, u \add egg ammu uřa\add* di marra tiwwura n \add tendint\add* Urcalim  
\v 20 uca ini asen: Sřem i wawař n SIDI, kenniw ijeǧiden n Yahuda d marra Yahuda d marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim inni ittadfen zi tewwura-ya.’  
\v 21 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ḥḍam x ixef nwem ad tarbum řeḥmeř deg wass n ssebt u ad t tessidfem zi tewwura n Urcalim! \x ◘ \xo 17:21 \xt Naḥ. 13:19\x*  
\v 22 Deg wass n ssebt war tessuffuɣem ca uřa d ijj n řeḥmeř zi tudrin nwem u war tᵉtteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet. Kenniw ad tessqeddsem ass n ssebt am mammec weṣṣiɣ babatwem.’ \x ◘ \xo 17:22 \xt Uf. 20:8; 23:12; 31:13; Ḥiz. 20:12\x*  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* nitni war sřin ca u war d ayi wcin amezzuɣ nsen, nitni \add maca\add* ɣennan ayi, maḥend war sřin u war ksin aweddeb.” \x ◘ \xo 17:23 \xt Irm. 11:10; 13:10; 16:12\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 24 “Mařa tesřim-dd ɣari mliḥ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad yiři řami war tessidfem řeḥmeř zi tewwura n tendint-a u řami i ɣa tessqeddsem ass n ssebt, war dayes tᵉtteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet,  
\v 25 \add xenni\add* ad adfen ijeǧiden d řḥukkam nni iqqimen x řɛarc n Dawud zi tewwura n tendint-a, am neddhen ikarruten d iysan, nitni d řḥukkam nsen, iryazen n Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim. \add Xenni\add* tandint-a ad dayes qqimen zeddɣen imezdaɣ nnes i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 17:25 \xt Irm. 22:4\x*  
\v 26 Nitni ad dd-asen zi tneddam n Yahuda u zi jjwayeh i dd-innḍen i Urcalim, u zi temmurt n Binyamin, u zi Temmurt Iwaṭan, zi Temmurt n Idurar u zi Ljanub, nitni ad awyen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d ṣṣedqet n tɣarṣt d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d jjawi uca ad awyen tawhibt n uqadi di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* mařa kenniw war ɣari tᵉttesřim ḥima ad tessqeddsem ass n ssebt u ḥima ad tadfem zi tewwura n Urcalim s ijj n řeḥmeř deg wass n ssebt, \add xenni\add* Necc ad ssarɣeɣ ict n tmessi di tewwura nnes nni i ɣa iccen řeqṣur n Urcalim u war ggur ɛemmarṣ ad texsi.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Irmiya di taddart n uqeddar  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-yusin zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Kkar, hwa ɣar taddart n bu-třaxt. Dinni i ɣa jjeɣ awařen inu ad ttwasřen.”  
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* hwiɣ ɣar taddart n bu-třaxt, uca xzar, ufiɣ t ixeddem ict n řqecɛet x iẓra \add ittennḍen\add*.  
\v 4 Mařa ixsar uɣarraf nni tuɣa ittegg zi třaxt nni iǧan deg ufus n bu-třaxt, Netta igga zzayes ɛawed ijj n uɣarraf nneɣni, am mammec d as ittɣiř d lemliḥ i bu-třaxt maḥend ad t igg.  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 6 “Ma war zemmareɣ Necc ad ggeɣ akidwem am bu-třaxt wanita, \add a\add* taddart n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Xzar, am třaxt deg ufus n bu-třaxt, ammu i teǧam deg ufus inu, \add a\add* taddart n Israil!\x ◘ \xo 18:6 \xt Ica. 45:9; 64:8; Rum. 9:20\x*  
\v 7 Ict n twařa ad ssiwřeɣ x ijj n řgens u x ict n tgeldit aqa ad \add t\add* qeřɛeɣ, ad \add t\add* hedmeɣ u ad \add t\add* teḥḥiɣ, \x ◘ \xo 18:7 \xt Irm. 1:10\x*  
\v 8 \add maca\add* mařa řgens nni ad dd-idweř zi tuɛeffna nnes i x ssiwřeɣ \add akidsen\add*, \add xenni\add* ad nedmeɣ zi řɣar i tuɣa nwiɣ ad as t ggeɣ.  
\v 9 Ict n twařa nneɣni ad ssiwřeɣ x ijj n řgens u x ict n tgeldit belli ad \add t\add* ssbeddeɣ u ad \add t\add* ẓẓuɣ,  
\v 10 \add maca\add* mařa ad yegg min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin inu umi war ttesřin ɣar tmijja inu, \add xenni\add* ad nedmeɣ x min icnan i nniɣ ad kidsen t ggeɣ.  
\v 11 Xenni řexxu, siweř ak-d iryazen n Yahuda u ak-d imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc sswejdeɣ ijj n řɣar ḍidd nwem u Necc ttxarraṣeɣ deg ijj n wenway xawem. Dewřem-dd xenni, kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan, u ɛedřem ibriden nwem d tmegga nwem.’ \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt 2 Ij. 17:13; Irm. 7:3; 25:5; 26:13; 35:15\x*  
\v 12 Maca nitni qqaren: ‘Řayas walu! Neccin ad neḍfar inwayen \add n yixef\add* nneɣ uca ad negg kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab řeqsaḥet n wuř nnes!’” \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Irm. 2:25\x*   
\m
\v 13 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Seqsam řegnus, man wen isřin \add ɛemmarṣ\add* am wa? Taɛzarect Israil tegga ijj n nnɛi d ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 18:13 \xt Irm. 2:10\x*  
\v 14 Ma ad iḥeyyed ɛemmarṣ wedfeř n Lubnan zeg ict n teṣḍart deg iyyar? Ma ad aẓɣen \add ɛemmarṣ\add* waman ittbuqbuqen, isemmaḍen ittazzřen?  
\v 15 Maca waxxa amenni ittu ayi řgens inu. Nitni ttawyen tiwhibin n řebxur i \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen inni ten ijjin ad nnqarḍen deg ibriden nsen, di jjurat n wecḥař uya, maḥend ad uyuren deg izubaq n ijj n webrid war iwiṭin, \x ◘ \xo 18:15 \xt Irm. 2:32; 3:21; 6:16; 13:25\x*  
\v 16 maḥend ad arren tammurt nsen d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d tseḍḥact i řebda. Qaɛ wenni ssenni i ɣa ikken, ad innexřeɛ, ad ihezz azeǧif nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Irm. 12:11; 19:8; 49:13; 50:13\x*  
\v 17 Am usemmiḍ n manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct ad ten zuzzareɣ zzat i řeɛdu. Necc ad asen ssecneɣ aɛrur, war iǧi udem \add inu\add*, deg wass n uhellek nsen.’”\x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Ica. 27:8; 29:6; Irm. 4:11, 12, 13; 13:24\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 “Nitni \add maca\add* nnan: ‘Asem-dd, jjem aneɣ ad negg tameɛmuč x Irmiya, maɣar Ccariɛa ɛemmarṣ ad iqḍa ɣar ukehhan, ccwar ɣar umiɣis u awař ɣar unabi. Asem-dd, ejj aneɣ ad t newwet s \add wawařen n\add* yiřes nneɣ uca ejj aneɣ war nettic taynit i uřa d ijj zeg wawařen i iqqar.’” \x ◘ \xo 18:18 \xt Irm. 9:7; Mal. 2:7\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Irmiya di řeḥṣaret  
\m
\v 19 “Ḥḍa ayi, \add a\add* SIDI, u seř-dd ɣar tmijja n yinni akidi ittmenɣan.  
\v 20 Ma \add xenni\add* ad ittwaxřef min iṣebḥen s min war iḥřin? Maɣar nitni ɣzin ayi ict n tenḍeč! Idar mammec beddeɣ zzatek ḥima ad ssiwřeɣ di řxir nsen, ḥima ad xasen ḥeyydeɣ asɛar nnec.  
\v 21 S uya, ewc iḥenjiren nsen i řaẓ uca sellem i-ten i tzemmar n ssif uca ejj timɣarin nsen ad asent acaren iḥenjiren, ad dewřent d tijjař, ejj iryazen nsent ad ttwanɣen u iḥuḍriyyen nsent ad mmten s ssif deg umenɣi. \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt Izhd. 109:10\x*  
\v 22 Ejj ad tᵉttwaseř tɣuyyit zi tudrin nsen, mařa Cek deɣya tɣeḍred-dd xasen ict n bandiyya umi ɣzin ict n tenḍeč ḥima ad ayi ṭṭfen, u ssarsen řefxux innuffaren i iḍaren inu.  
\v 23 \add A\add* SIDI, Cek tessned marra anway nsen maḥend ad ayi nɣen. War sduriy řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u war meḥḥi ddnub nsen zzat i wudem nnec, \add maca\add* ejj i-ten ad wḍan zzatek. Egg asen \add ammu\add* di řweqt n weɣḍab nnec.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Areẓẓit n Urcalim d Yahuda am ict n tqedduḥt n třaxt  
\m
\v 1 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: “Uyur uca seɣ ijj n uɣarraf n třaxt uca awi \add ca zeg\add* imɣaren n řgens u zeg imɣaren n ikehhanen \add akidek\add*.  
\v 2 Ffeɣ ɣar barra ɣar Teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum, tenni ɣar wadaf n Tewwart n Iceqfan, uca barreḥ dinni awařen nni i d ac ɣa iniɣ,  
\v 3 ini: ‘Sřem i wawař n SIDI, \add a\add* ijeǧiden n Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim! Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ ict n tecti \add tameqqrant\add* x wemcan-a, maḥend n marra nni tt ɣa isřen, ad ṭneṭnen imezzuɣen, \x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt 1 Ṣm. 3:11; 2 Ij. 21:12\x*  
\v 4 maɣar nitni ḥeyyden xafi, arrin amcan-a \add d ijj n wemcan\add* i ibarraniyyen uca qeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni nni war ssinen, war iǧi nitni uřa d ibabaten nsen d ijeǧiden n Yahuda. Nitni ɛemmaren amcan-a s idammen n imezdagen. \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt Ica. 65:11; Irm. 2:13, 17, 19; 5:7, 19; 7:6; 15:6; 17:13\x*  
\v 5 Minzi nitni ssbedden řegɛudi \add mani ttwehhbent ddbayeḥ nsen\add* i Baɛl, ḥima ad sscemḍen iḥenjiren nsen s tmessi, am tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i Baɛl, min war \add d asen\add* umureɣ d min war \add ɣarsen\add* ssiwřeɣ d min ɛemmarṣ war \add t\add* ggiɣ deg wuř inu.’”   
\m
\v 6 “S uya, xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, war daysen qqaren ɛad i wemcan-a ‘Tufat’ niɣ ‘Taɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum’, maca ‘Taɣzurt n Wenɣay’. \x ◘ \xo 19:6 \xt Irm. 7:32\x*  
\v 7 Maɣar ad ssbeṭṭřeɣ inwayen n Yahuda d Urcalim deg wemcan-a u ad ten ɣeḍřeɣ zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nsen s ssif u s ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nsen. Necc ad wceɣ řxecbat nsen d macca i ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i řmař n temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 19:7 \ft \+fk tudart nsen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar nsen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:7 \xt Irm. 15:3; 16:4\x*  
\v 8 Necc ad arreɣ tandint-a d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d tseḍḥac. Kuř ijj wenni xas dd ɣa ikken ad innexřeɛ u ad iṣeffar \add s asrubi\add* x marra jjɛayef nnes.  
\v 9 Necc ad asen ggeɣ ad ccen aysum n iḥenjiren nsen d weysum n yessitsen. Nitni ad ccen, kuř ijj aysum n jjar nnes, di \add řweqt nni di\add* ɣa quwwaren i tendint, di řeḥṣaret i zi ten i ɣa ḥṣaren řɛedyan nsen d yinni yarezzun tudart nsen.”\x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Lawi 26:29; Aɛwd. 28:53; Igjd. 4:10\x*  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ac ad tarẓed aɣarraf jar tiṭṭawin n yeryazen nni akidek yuyuren.  
\v 11 Ittxeṣṣa ad asen tinid: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Ammu i ɣa arẓeɣ řgens-a d tendint-a, am mammec ttareẓẓan ijj n uɣarraf n bu-třaxt nni war izemmaren ad t ɛedřen ɛad. Nitni ad ten neḍřen di Tufat umi war din iqqim wemcan mani ɣa neḍřen. \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Irm. 7:32\x*  
\v 12 Ammu i ɣa ggeɣ zeg wemcan-a u zeg imezdaɣ nnes, iqqar SIDI, ḥima ad arreɣ tandint-a am Tufat.  
\v 13 Tudrin n Urcalim d tudrin n ijeǧiden n Yahuda ad dewřent xemjent am wemcan n Tufat, zi ssibbet n marra tudrin i zi x tzeɣwin nsent qeddmen nitni řebxur i marra řɛeskar n ujenna d tewhibin n useyyeb i irebbiten nneɣni.’” \x ◘ \xo 19:13 \xt Irm. 7:18\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Umi dd-iɛqeb Irmiya zi Tufat, mani tuɣa t issekk SIDI maḥend ad inebba, yuyur di řemraḥ n zzat n Taddart n SIDI uca inna i řgens marra:  
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ x tendint-a u x marra tineddam nnes marra řɣar nni x ssiwřeɣ, minzi nitni menɛen taɣennant am ugin ad sřen ɣar wawařen inu.’” \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Irm. 7:26; 17:23\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Irmiya d řɛedyan nnes  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* Facḥur, mmis n Immir, akehhan nni ittwaggen d aweqqaf ameqqran x Taddart n SIDI, isřa i Irmiya ittnebba awařen-a,  
\v 2 iwta Facḥur anabi Irmiya uca iḥebbes i-t deg ukeccuḍ nni iǧan deg wexxam n sennej n Tewwart Yuɛřan n Binyamin nni \add iǧan\add* di Taddart n SIDI.   
\m
\v 3 Tiwecca nnes ijja Facḥur ad arxun i Irmiya zeg ukeccuḍ. \add Xenni\add* inna as Irmiya: “War d ac iqqar SIDI Facḥur, maca Majur-Missabib. \f ◼ \fr 20:3 \ft \+fk Facḥur\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘sřam’ niɣ ‘tiřelli’. \fk Majur-Missabib\ft  - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘anexřiɛ zi marra iɣezdisen’.\f*  
\v 4 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad cek ggeɣ d asnexřiɛ i yixef nnec u i marra inni cek ittexsen. Nitni ad wḍan s ssif n řɛedyan nsen, am t ttwařant tiṭṭawin nnec, u Necc ad wceɣ marra Yahuda deg ifassen n ujeǧid n Babil nni ten i ɣa inedhen di tmeḥbast ɣar Babil u ad ten ineɣ s ssif.  
\v 5 Marra agřa n tendint-a ad ten sellmeɣ u marra min dayes iɣřan d marra tixuba n ijeǧiden n Yahuda ad ggeɣ aya \add marra\add* deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen. Nitni ad ten acaren, ad ten ksin \add akidsen\add* uca ad ten i-dd-awyen ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 20:5 \xt Irm. 15:13; 17:3\x*  
\v 6 Cek, Facḥur, d marra ayt n taddart nnec, kenniw ad teffɣem d imeḥbas. Cek ad dd-tawḍed ɣar Babil uca ad temmted dinni uca ad ttwaneḍřed dinni, cek d marra imeddukkař nnec inni umi tnebbid s ixarriqen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Cek tjebded ayi, \add a\add* SIDI, uca necc ttwassqenɛeɣ. Cek tjehded xafi aṭṭas, tɣeřbed ayi. Ass marra ttɣiman deḥḥcen dayi, marra idsen stehzan zzayi.  
\v 8 Maɣar meřmi ma ssiwřeɣ, sɣuyyuɣ ‘Řexcunect!’, řaɣiɣ ‘Anexřiɛ!’, maɣar awař n SIDI ittawi ayi-dd ass imun mɣir aseḥqar d ustehzi. \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt Ica. 57:4\x*  
\v 9 Nniɣ: ‘Necc war t ttidareɣ \add ɛad\add* u war ssiwiřeɣ \add ɛad\add* s Yisem nnes!’, \add xenni\add* idweř aya deg wuř inu am yict n tmessi yareqqen, tᵉttwaḥbes deg iɣsan inu. Necc ssaḥařeɣ ixef inu maḥend ad ṣbareɣ, maca war d as zemmareɣ.  
\v 10 Maɣar sřiɣ aceqqef s řhard n waṭṭas: ‘Majur-Missasib’, \add ‘Asiggʷed zi marra iɣezdisen!’\add*, ammu i qqaren. Uca xenni qqaren: ‘Sargeb aneɣ!, \add xenni\add* neccin ad \add zzayes\add* nbarreḥ!’ Kuř aryaz ak-d ddareɣ di řehna, ittraja ař ɣa nqarḍeɣ. \add Qqaren:\add* ‘Ad taɣ nzemmar ad t neɣwa, xenni ad t neɣřeb uca ad zzayes nexřef.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “SIDI ibedd akidi am yijj n bu-teɣruḍt d ameqqran, x uya i ɣa nnqarḍen inni d ayi iḍaffaren, war zemmaren ad ggen walu. Nitni ad seḍḥan s yixef nsen aṭṭas, minzi war ggin s řeɛqeř. Ad tiři d ict n řefḍiḥet i řebda i war ttᵉttun i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 20:11 \xt Irm. 1:8, 19; 15:20; 17:18; 23:40\x*  
\v 12 \add Cek\add*, \add a\add* SIDI n řɛeskarat, wenni ittqeǧaben amsegged, wenni ittwařan tiẓẓař d wuř, scen ayi nneqmet nnec xasen, maɣar necc ggiɣ ac taɣawsa inu deg ufus.” \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt Irm. 11:20; 12:3; 15:15; 18:19-23\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 “Zehhdem i SIDI, semɣarem SIDI, maɣar Netta ifekk amezřuḍ zeg ufus n iɛeffanen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Aqa ittwanɛeř ass i di dd-ttwarweɣ! Ass i d ayi dd-turu yemma war ittiři ittwabarek. \x ◘ \xo 20:14 \xt Irm. 15:10\x*  
\v 15 Ittwanɛeř weryaz nni dd-yiwyen řexbar aṣebḥan i baba, inna: ‘Aqa ittwaruw ac-dd uḥenjir!’ uca issfarḥ i-t \add ammu\add* s waṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 20:15 \xt Ayub 3:3\x*  
\v 16 Ejj aryaz nni ad yiři am tneddam nni issneqřeb SIDI břa ma indem zi man aya. Ejj i-t ad iseř i iɣuyyan \add n řeḥriq\add* ɣar teffut u iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add* ɣar ṭṭya n wass, \x ◘ \xo 20:16 \xt Amz. 19\x*  
\v 17 minzi Netta war d ayi inɣi deg uɛeddis n yemma. Ammu tedweř yemma d anḍeř inu uca iqqim uɛeddis nnes iksi s ddeyset i řebda!  
\v 18 Mayemmi i dd-ffɣeɣ zeg uɛeddis? Ma ḥima ad ẓareɣ tamara d wecḍan \add waha\add* u ḥima ad qḍiɣ ussan inu di řefḍiḥet?” \x ◘ \xo 20:18 \xt Ayub 3:20\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Asekki amezwaru n ujeǧid Ṣidqiya ɣar Irmiya  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya, umi ajeǧid Ṣidqiya issekk ɣares Facḥur, mmis n ukehhan Malkiya, d Ṣafanya, mmis n ukehhan Maɛasiya, inna: \f ◼ \fr 21:1 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*  
\v 2 “Seqsa maca SIDI xaneɣ, maɣar Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ittmenɣa akidneɣ. Ad taɣ SIDI ad dayneɣ igg ict n lmuɛjiza am mammec marra lmuɛjizat nnes, maḥend ad xaneɣ iḥeyyed \add Nabuxadraṣṣar\add*.”   
\m
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* inna asen Irmiya: “Ammu i ɣa tinim i Ṣidqiya:  
\v 4 ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ deg ifassen nwem řesnaḥ i zi ttmenɣam ak-d ujeǧid n Babil d Ikaldaniyyen, inni d awem dd-innḍen barra i řḥiḍ, u Necc ad ten ssmuneɣ di řwesṭ n tendint-a.  
\v 5 Necc simant inu ad kidwem menɣeɣ s ufus isswiẓẓḍen d uɣiř ijehden, s weɣḍab d wesɛar u s uduqqez ameqqran \add n weɣḍab\add*.  
\v 6 Necc ad wteɣ imezdaɣ n tendint-a, am iwdan uřa d řmar: nitni ad mmten s ijj n ṭṭaɛun ameqqran.  
\v 7 Awarni as, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, Necc ad sseɛduɣ Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d imsexxaren nnes d řgens nnes nni iqqimen di tendint-a zi ṭṭaɛun, zi ssif u zi řaẓ, deg ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen u deg ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nsen. Netta ad ten ineɣ s řeqḍeɛ n ssif u netta war ittḥinni, war issɛizzi u war yareḥḥem.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 8 \bd “I řgens-a ad tinid\bd*: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc ggiɣ awem abrid n tudart d webrid n řmewt.  
\v 9 Wenni i ɣa iqqimen di tendint-a, ad ittwaneɣ s ssif, s řaẓ u s ṭṭaɛun, \add maca\add* wenni zzayes i ɣa iffɣen uca ad iɛdu ɣar Ikaldaniyyen inni kenniw iḥeṣṣaren, ad iqqim iddar uca řeɛmar nnes ad as yiři am tkeccaḍt. \x ◘ \xo 21:9 \xt Irm. 38:2\x*  
\v 10 Maɣar Necc arriɣ-dd s wudem inu ḍidd i wemcan-a, war iǧi i řxar, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Amcan-a ad ittwasseɛdu deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil u netta ad as iqqed timessi.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 \bd Zi jjihet n taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda\bd*, sřem i wawař n SIDI:  
\v 12 “\add A\add* taddart n Dawud, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Seggdem nican di teffut, fekkem wenni ittwakeccḍen zeg ufus n wenni iḥeṣṣaren, niɣ ad yarreẓ wesɛar inu am tmessi ařami war izemmar uřa d ijj ad tt issexsi ɛad zi ssibbet n tmegga nwem tiɛeffanin. \x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt Irm. 22:3\x*  
\v 13 Xzar, ad cem řeqfeɣ, \add cem\add* tenni izeddɣen di teysart, \add cem\add*, \add a\add* taṣḍart n řwaṭa, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Kenniw teqqarem: Man wen izemmaren ad ɣarneɣ dd-ihwa, man wen izemmaren ad dd-yadef ɣar tzeddiɣin nneɣ?  
\v 14 Necc ad kenniw ɛaqbeɣ ɛlaḥsab řɣiǧet n tmegga nwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Necc ad ggeɣ timessi deg wezɣar nnes nni i ɣa iccen marra min d as dd-innḍen.’” \f ◼ \fr 21:14 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 21:14 \xt Irm. 17:27\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\m
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Hwa ɣar taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda, ini din awař-a,  
\v 2 ad tinid: \add A\add* ajeǧid n Yahuda, wenni iqqimen x řɛarc n Dawud, seř i wawař n SIDI, cek d imsexxaren nnec d řgens nnec i ittadfen zi tewwura-ya!  
\v 3 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Ggem řḥeqq d tsegda u ssnejmem min ittwakeccḍen zeg ufus n wenni iḥeṣṣaren. War ḥeṣṣarem, war ccatem řbarrani d uyujiř d tajjač. War ssizziřem idammen imezdagen di temmurt-a! \x ◘ \xo 22:3 \xt Irm. 7:6; 21:12\x*  
\v 4 Mařa kenniw ad teggem awař-a s tidett, \add xenni\add* ad adfen ijeǧiden zi tewwura n tendint-a, inni i ɣa iqqimen ɣar Dawud x řɛarc nnes, inni i ɣa inedhen ikarruten d yeysan, \add wah,\add* netta d imsexxaren nnes d řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Irm. 17:25; Ḥiz. 37:25. \x*  
\v 5 Mařa war tesřim ca ɣar wawařen-a, aqa jjuǧeɣ i Yixef inu, \add ammu\add* iqqar SIDI, ad tedweř Taddart-a d řxirbet.’”   
\m
\v 6 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI x taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda: ‘\add Waxxa\add* cek tusid ayi x řxaḍar am Jilɛad u am tqiccet n Lubnan, d tidett ad cek tteggeɣ d řexřa, tineddam war izdiɣen. \x ◘ \xo 22:6 \xt Zak. 10:10\x*  
\v 7 Necc ad ḥuzeɣ ḍidd nnec imteḥḥayyen, kuř ijj s řesnaḥ nnes \add i wenɣay\add*. Nitni ad qessen ticejjura nnec n tengelt i icnan aṭṭas \add s ccwaqar nsen\add* uca ad \add tent\add* wcen i tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 22:7 \xt Irm. 15:6\x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ad dd-kken aṭṭas n řegnus x tendint-a, ad inin, kuř ijj i umqarrab nnes: Mayemmi SIDI igga ammu i tendint-a tameqqrant? \x ◘ \xo 22:8 \xt Aɛwd. 29:23; 1 Ij. 9:8\x*  
\v 9 Ad inin: Minzi nitni semḥen di Řɛahd n SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uca sejden i irebbiten nneɣni uca dewřen ɛebbden asen.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 X Callum  
\m
\v 10 “War ttrum x umettin u war xas ccatem agejdur. Rum x wenni yuyuren, maɣar netta ɛemmarṣ ad dd-iɛqeb, ɛemmarṣ ad iẓar ɛad tammurt nnes mani ixřeq.  
\v 11 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI x Callum, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, wenni idewřen d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas Yuciya, \add Callum\add* wenni dd-iffɣen zeg wemcan-a: ‘Netta ɛemmarṣ ad dd-iɛqeb dinni ɛad.  
\v 12 Maɣar deg wemcan mani t nedhen di tmeḥbast, \add dinni\add* i ɣa immet, ɛemmarṣ ad iẓar tammurt-a ɛawed.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 X Yahuyaqim  
\m
\v 13 “Axeyyeb i wenni i ɣa issbedden tazeddiɣt nnes s řmuɛṣiyyet, tiɣurfin nnes s řɣecc, wenni issxeddamen wenni t yudsen nehřa axeǧeṣ u war d as ittic řmunet nnes, \x ◘ \xo 22:13 \xt Lawi 19:13; Aɛwd. 24:14, 15; Ḥab. 2:9\x*  
\v 14 wenni iqqaren: ‘Necc ad ssbeddeɣ i yixef inu ict n tzeddiɣt yuɛřan aṭṭas s tɣurfin iwesɛen.’ \add Xenni\add* ad dayes igg tiburjatin uca ad tt iseqqef s ukeccuḍ n tcejjura n tengelt uca ad tt izewweq s tintat tizeggʷaɣin.  
\v 15 Ma tḥekkmed am ujeǧid umi tᵉttemḥizwared zi ssibbet n tneglin? Babac ma war icci, ma war iswi u ma war iggi řḥeqq d tsegda? Netta tuɣa mliḥ xas xenni!  
\v 16 Netta iḥkem tamesřact n wenni ittwaḥṣaren d umezřuḍ. Tuɣa mliḥ xas xenni. Ma aya war ixs ad yini aqa bnadem issen ayi?, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 17 Maca tiṭṭawin nnec d wuř nnec aqa ten mɣir x tizi nnec waha, x idammen imezdagen maḥend ad ten tessizzřed, u x ddeǧ d ubeɛɛej, maḥend ad ten tegged.”   
\m
\v 18 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda: ‘Nitni war xas ceṭṭnen: Ax, uma! niɣ: Ax, učma! Nitni war ceṭṭnen: Ax, sidi! niɣ: Ax, lɛaḍim! \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Irm. 16:4, 5, 6\x*  
\v 19 Ad neḍřen s wenḍař n ijj n weɣyuř. Ad t jarren u ad t nḍaren ɣar řaggʷaj, barra i tiwwura n Urcalim.’” \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Irm. 15:3; 36:30\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 X Kun-Yahu  
\m
\v 20 “Geɛɛed x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, sɣuyy uca ejj tmijja nnem ad tᵉttwaseř di Bacan. Sɣuyy-dd ɛawed zi Abarim, maɣar marra inni cem ittexsen ttwarẓan.  
\v 21 Necc ssiwřeɣ akidem řami cem tuɣa di řaman, cem maca tennid: ‘Necc war xseɣ ad sřeɣ!’ Ammu i t teggid zi temẓi nnem, maɣar cem tuɣa war tᵉttexsed ad tesřed i tmijja inu. \x ◘ \xo 22:21 \xt Irm. 5:23; 7:23-28; 11:7, 8; 13:10, 11; 16:12; 17:23; 18:12; 19:15\x*  
\v 22 Marra imeksawen ad ten yarwes usemmiḍ uca inni cem ittexsen ad uyuren di tmeḥbast. Xenni ad tseḍḥid uca ad tenfeḍḥed zi ssibbet n marra tuɛeffna nnem. \f ◼ \fr 22:22 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 23 Cem, \add a\add* tenni izeddɣen x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan, tenni iḥebḍen di tcejjura n tneglin, mammec i ɣa tzehhared xmi d am dd ɣa yasen řewjeɛ, řeḥriq am yicten tᵉttaru!”   
\m
\v 24 “\add S tidett am\add* ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: ‘Waxxa, mařa Kun-Yahu, mmis n Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda, tuɣa d txadent n ucemmiɛ deg ufus inu, aqa ad cek kkseɣ ssenni.  
\v 25 Necc ad cek wceɣ deg ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nnec u deg ufus n wenni zi tᵉtteggʷeded, deg ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, u deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen. \f ◼ \fr 22:25 \ft \+fk yinni yarezzun tudart nnec\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘n yenni yarezzun řeɛmar nnec’.\f*  
\v 26 Cek d yemmac, ad kenniw nḍareɣ ɣar ict n temmurt nneɣnit mani war texřiqem, uca dinni ad tmetnem.  
\v 27 War ttɛiqqibem ɛemmarṣ ɣar temmurt nni di temmeẓrem maḥend ad ɣares dd-tɛeqbem.’”   
\m
\v 28 “Ma Kun-Yahu aryaz-a d ijj n uɣarraf immenḍar, yarreẓ? Niɣ netta d ijj n uɣarraf war t ittexs ɛad uřa d ijj? Mayemmi t ḥejjaren, netta d zzariɛet nnes, nḍaren \add ten\add* ɣar ict n temmurt war tt ssinen?  
\v 29 \add A\add* tammurt, tammurt, tammurt, seř i wawař n SIDI!  
\v 30 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Zemm aryaz-a nhřa iḥenjiren, ijj n weryaz nni war ɣar iǧi zzhir deg wussan nnes. Maɣar uřa d ijj zeg warraw nnes ad ɣares yiři zzhir \add ařami\add* i ɣa iqqim x řɛarc n Dawud, ad iḥkem ɛawed di \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Aɣeddu n tsegda  
\m
\v 1 “Uct x imeksawen i ineqqen u zuzzaran uǧi n ddmani inu n tarewsa, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 23:1 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 23:1 \xt Ḥiz. 34:2\x*  
\v 2 S uya ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x imeksawen nni yarekkwsen řgens inu: ‘Kenniw tzuzzarem uǧi inu uca tuẓẓřem xasen. Kenniw war ten teḥḍim. Xzar, Necc ad xeřfeɣ zi tuɛeffna d tmegga nwem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 3 Necc ad ssmuneɣ min iqqimen n wuǧi inu zi marra timmura mani xasent uẓẓřeɣ. Necc ad tent arreɣ ɣar řkurit nsent, ad arwent, ad mmarnint.  
\v 4 Necc ad asent ggeɣ imeksawen nni tent i ɣa yarewsen. Nitni war tteggʷdent ɛad u war ttnexřiɛent u war ttweddirint!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 23:4 \xt Ḥiz. 34:11, 12\x*   
\m
\v 5 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, aqa Necc ad ssekkareɣ i Dawud AƔEDDU n tsegda. Netta ad iḥkem am Ujeǧid, ad ifřeḥ uca ad igg řḥeqq d tsegda di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 23:5 \xt Ica. 4:2; 40:11; Irm. 33:14, 15; Dan. 9:24; Lk. 1:32,33\x*  
\v 6 Deg wussan nnes ad ittwassenjem Yahuda uca Israil ad izdeɣ di řaman. Wa ad yiři d Isem i zi d as i ɣa řaɣan: SIDI, Tasegda nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt Aɛwd. 33:28\x*   
\m
\v 7 “S uya, xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, war qqaren ɛad: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI nni dd-issuffɣen ayt n Israil zi Miṣra!’, \x ◘ \xo 23:7 \xt Irm. 16:14, 15\x*  
\v 8 maca: ‘S tidett am iddar SIDI nni dd-isgeɛɛden zzariɛet n taddart n Israil, wenni ten dd-yarrin zi temmurt n ccamal u zi marra timmura manis xasen uẓẓřeɣ. Nitni ad zedɣen di temmurt nsen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 \bd X inabiyyen.\bd*  
\m “Uř inu ittwarẓ di daxeř inu, marra iɣsan inu ttarjijin. Necc dewřeɣ am yijj n umescur, am weryaz nni yarni binu, zi ssibbet n SIDI u zi ssibbet n wawařen nnes iqeddsen.  
\v 10 Maɣar tammurt teccur s yinni izennan, maɣar tammurt tecḍen zi ssibbet n nneɛřet, ddmani n tarewsa di řexřa uẓɣent. Mani xsen ad awḍen aqa-t d aɛeffan, uřa d jjehd nsen war iǧi ca nican. \x ◘ \xo 23:10 \xt Irm. 5:7, 8; 9:2\x*  
\v 11 Maɣar am unabi am ukehhan ttwafesden, ɛad di Taddart inu ttafeɣ tuɛeffna nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 23:11 \xt Irm. 6:13; 8:10; 14:18\x*  
\v 12 S uya ad dd-asen idweř webrid nsen am yijj n řewḍa itteḥruǧuḍ di taǧest. Ad ttwaɛarrnen u nitni ad zzayes dd-wḍan, maɣar ad xasen dd-ssehwiɣ ict n tecti taɛeffant deg useggʷas i zzaysen i ɣa xeřfeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 23:12 \xt Izhd. 35:6; 73:18; Irm. 13:16\x*   
\m
\v 13 “Aqa Necc ẓriɣ timesřayin isstebhaten ɣar inabiyyen n Samarya: nitni tuɣa ttnabben s Baɛl uca ttɣarran řgens inu.  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* ɣar inabiyyen n Urcalim ẓriɣ ijj n nnɛi d aɛeffan qaɛ: nitni zennan, uyuren am ssxarriqen uca ssjehden ifassen n iɛeffanen ařami uřa d ijj war dd-iɛqeb zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan. Mammec ttwařiɣ Necc, marra idsen am Sadum, uca imezdaɣ n Urcalim \add i Necc\add* am Ɛamurra. \x ◘ \xo 23:14 \xt Ica. 1:9\x*  
\v 15 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad wceɣ cciḥ d macca i řgens-a uřa d aman n arrhaj maḥend ad ten swen, minzi zeg inabiyyen di Urcalim iffeɣ-dd uɣesseb \add n Ccariɛa\add* ɣar marra tammurt. \x ◘ \xo 23:15 \xt Irm. 8:14; 9:15\x*  
\v 16 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: War ttesřim ca i wawařen n inabiyyen nni d awem ittnebban, \add am\add* ssawařen akidwem baṭeř. Nitni ssawařen ijj n řewḥiy n wuř \add n yixef\add* nsen, war \add ssiwiřen\add* \add řewḥiy\add* zeg uqemmum n SIDI.  
\v 17 Řebda qqaren i yinni d ayi isseḥqaran: SIDI inna i-t, ad ɣarwem yiři řehna! U i kuř ijj wenni igguren di řeqsaḥet n wuř nnes, qqaren: War dd xawem ittemsar uřa d ijj n řɣar! \x ◘ \xo 23:17 \xt Irm. 6:14; 8:11; Ḥiz. 13:10; Zak. 10:2\x*  
\v 18 Maɣar man wen \add zzaysen\add* tuɣa ibedd di řḥeřqet n imcawaren n SIDI, iẓra awař nnes u isřa as? Wi issḥessen i wawař nnes uca isřa ɣares?  
\v 19 Xzar, taḥaryaḍt n SIDI, iffeɣ-dd \add zzayes\add* wesɛar, ict n tḥaryaḍt tezzebzib nni dd ɣa ihwan x uzeǧif n iɛeffanen. \x ◘ \xo 23:19 \xt Irm. 30:23, 24\x*  
\v 20 Aɣḍab n SIDI war dd-iddikkʷiř ca ař ɣa yiřin ixarriṣen n wuř nnes. Deg uneggar n wussan ad as tfehmem s řefhamet tekmeř.  
\v 21 Necc war dd-ssekkiɣ ca inabiyyen nni, \add waxxa amenni\add* gguren ttazzřen nitni. Necc war ɣarsen ssiwřeɣ ca, \add waxxa amenni\add* bdan ad nebban deɣya \add zeg yixef nsen\add*. \x ◘ \xo 23:21 \xt Irm. 14:14\x*  
\v 22 Mři tuɣa nitni bedden di řheřqet n imcawaren inu, iři arrin řgens inu ad iseř i wawařen inu u iři arrin ten ad dd-dewřen zeg webrid nsen aɛeffan u zi řɣar n tmegga nsen.”   
\m
\v 23 “Necc d ijj n AREBBI zi řadas, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, war iǧi ijj n AREBBI zi řaggʷaj?  
\v 24 Ma izemmar ca n yijjen ad innuffar deg imucan innuffaren, ařami Necc war t ẓarreɣ, iqqar SIDI. Ma war iǧi d Necc wenni iccuren ajenna d temmurt?, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 23:24 \xt Izhd. 139:7-12; Ɛam. 9:2, 3\x*  
\v 25 Necc sřiɣ min qqaren inabiyyen nni ittnebban am ssxarriqen deg Yisem inu, qqaren: ‘Tuɣa ɣari ict n tirja, ict n tirja!’  
\v 26 Ař meřmi \add ɛad\add* ad iřint tirja deg wuř n inabiyyen nni ittnebban am ssxarriqen? Nitni d inabiyyen n wecmaṭ n wuř \add n yixef\add* nsen,  
\v 27 inni yarezzun ad arren řgens inu ad ittu Isem inu s tirja nsen nni tthajan ijj i wenneɣni, am mammec ibabaten nsen ttun Isem inu s Baɛl. \x ◘ \xo 23:27 \xt Řqḍ. 3:7; 8:33,34\x*  
\v 28 Anabi nni ɣares ict n tirja, ejj i-t ad tt iḥaja, u \add anabi\add* nni ɣar iǧa wawař inu, ejj i-t ad issiweř awař inu s tidett. Maɣar min dd-yiwyen řum ɣar imendi, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 29 Ma war iǧi wawař inu am tmessi, iqqar SIDI, uca am yijj n wefḍis i iřebbzen taṣḍart?  
\v 30 S uya, xzar, Necc ad řeqfeɣ inabiyyen nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, inni ittacaren awařen inu ijj n wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 23:30 \xt Aɛwd. 18:20; Irm. 14:14, 15\x*  
\v 31 Xzar, Necc ad řeqfeɣ inabiyyen nni, iqqar SIDI, inni issxeddamen iřes nsen u ssawařen \add zzayes ammu\add*: ‘Netta iqqar!’  
\v 32 Xzar, Necc ad řeqfeɣ inni ittnebban s tirja ixarriqen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Nitni ttḥajan tirja nni u \add ammu i\add* ttɣarran řgens inu zeg ixarriqen nsen d řhard nsen ibeṭṭřen. Necc war ten dd-ssekkeɣ u war d asen wciɣ awař. Nitni war ǧin d nnfeɛ i řgens, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 23:32 \xt Ṣaf. 3:4\x*   
\m
\v 33 “Xmi cek i ɣa isseqsa ijj n řgens niɣ ijj n unabi niɣ ijj n ukehhan, ad yini: ‘Min iɛna \add xenni\add* řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI?’, xenni cek ad asen tinid: ‘Min iɛna \add xenni\add* řḥukm issaggʷaden?’ ‘Ad kenniw nḍareɣ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 34 Anabi d ukehhan d řgens nni iqqaren \add am stᵉhezzan\add*: ‘Řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI?’, aryaz nni d taddart nni ad zzayes xeřfeɣ.  
\v 35 Ammu ittxeṣṣa ad tinim, kuř ijj i jjar nnes u kuř ijj i umas: ‘Mammec xak dd-yarra SIDI?’, u: ‘Min inna SIDI?’  
\v 36 War tidarem ɛad řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI, maɣar řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI ad yiři min ɣa yini kuř ijj: aqa kenniw tessfarɣem awařen n AREBBI iddaren, SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI nneɣ.   
\m
\v 37 Ammu i ɣa tinid i unabi: ‘Mammec xak dd-yarra SIDI?’, niɣ: ‘Min inna SIDI?’  
\v 38 \add Maca\add* umi teqqarem kenniw: ‘Řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI?’, s uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, umi kenniw teqqarem awař-a: ‘Řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI?’, waxxa Necc ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarwem \add ijjen\add* ḥima ad awem yini: ‘Kenniw war teqqarem ca: Řḥukm issaggʷaden n SIDI?’,  
\v 39 s uya, xzar, Necc ad kenniw ttuɣ qaɛ. Necc ad kenniw nḍareɣ zi zzat i wudem inu ak-d tendint nwem nni d awem wciɣ i kenniw uřa i řejdud nwem.  
\v 40 Necc ad xawem dd-ssehwiɣ řḥegra i řebda d řefḍiḥet i řebda nni war ittwattun ɛemmarṣ.” \x ◘ \xo 23:40 \xt Irm. 20:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Tnayen n tsuǧatin n tazart  
\m
\v 1 SIDI ijja ayi ad ẓareɣ man aya. Xzar, ttwassarsent tnayen n tsuǧatin n tazart qibač i Zzawect Tameqqrant n SIDI awarni i umi tuɣa Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, indeh Yakunya, mmis n Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d řḥukkam n Yahuda ak-d iḥrayfiyyen d yemziřen zi Urcalim di lmenfa ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 24:1 \xt 2 Ij. 24:15; 2 Im. 36:10\x*  
\v 2 Deg ict n tsuǧet tuɣa \add din\add* tazart iṣebḥen, am řbacur. Di tsuǧet nneɣnit tuɣa din tazart war teḥri aṭṭas, zeɛma war teḥri ařami war izemmar ad tᵉttwacc.  
\v 3 Inna ayi SIDI: “Min tᵉttwařid cek, Irmiya?” Necc nniɣ: “Tazart. Tazart iṣebḥen teṣbeḥ aṭṭas, uca tenni war iḥřin aṭṭas, war teḥři ařami war tᵉttwicci.”   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 5 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Am tazart iṣebḥen ammu i ɣa ḥesbeɣ ṣebḥen inni ittwanedhen di tmeḥbast zi Yahuda, inni x uẓẓřeɣ zeg wemcan-a ɣar temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen.  
\v 6 Necc ad xasen ssarseɣ tiṭṭawin inu s arḍa uca ad ten arreɣ ad ɛeqben ɣar temmurt-a. Necc ad ten ssbeddeɣ, war ten heddmeɣ, ad ten ẓẓuɣ, war ten qeǧɛeɣ.  
\v 7 Necc ad asen wceɣ ijj n wuř maḥend ad ayi ssnen, belli aqa Necc d SIDI. Nitni ad iřin d řgens inu u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nsen, maɣar nitni ad ɣari dd-dewřen s wuř nsen imun.’” \x ◘ \xo 24:7 \xt Aɛwd. 30:6; Irm. 30:22; 31:33; 32:38,39; Ḥiz. 11:19; 36:26, 27\x*   
\m
\v 8 “Am tazart war iḥřin, tenni war teḥři aṭṭas ařami war tᵉttwicci, iqqar SIDI, ammu i ɣa arreɣ Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d řḥukkam nnes d min iqqimen zi Urcalim d yinni izeddɣen di temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 24:8 \xt Irm. 29:17\x*  
\v 9 Necc ad ten arreɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect, d řḥegra d ijj n umedya d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* ustehzi d ict n nneɛřet di marra imucan mani xasen i ɣa yaẓẓřeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Aɛwd. 28:25,37; 1 Ij. 9:7; 2 Im. 7:20; Irm. 15:4; 29:18; 34:17; 42:18\x*  
\v 10 Necc ad ssekkeɣ jar asen ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun ař dd-ttwakksen marra zi temmurt i asen wciɣ, i nitni u i řejdud nsen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Abarreḥ s lmenfa di Babil  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-yusin ɣar Irmiya x marra řgens n Yahuda, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Tuɣa-t d aseggʷas amezwaru n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil.  
\v 2 Inna unabi Irmiya \add awař-a\add* i marra řgens n Yahuda u i marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim, inna:  
\v 3 “Zeg useggʷas wiss třeṭṭac n Yuciya, mmis n Amun, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ař ass-a, aqa i yijj n řmijjař n třata u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa, yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI u necc tuɣa ssawařeɣ akidwem, \add wah,\add* zeg umezwaru tuɣa necc ssawařeɣ \add akidwem\add*, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim ca.  
\v 4 SIDI issekk-dd ɛawed marra imsexxaren nnes, inabiyyen, zeg umezwaru issekk i-ten-dd, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim u war tewcim ca amezzuɣ nwem ḥima ad tesřem. \x ◘ \xo 25:4 \xt Irm. 7:13, 25; 11:7, 8, 10; 13:10, 11; 16:12; 17:23; 18:12; 19:15; 22:21\x*  
\v 5 Nitni nnan: ‘Dewřem-dd, kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan u zi tuɛeffna n tmegga nwem uca zedɣem di temmurt nni d awem iwca SIDI u i řejdud nwem zi řebda i řebda qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 25:5 \xt 2 Ij. 17:13; Irm. 18:11; 35:15; Yun. 3:8\x*  
\v 6 War ttraddafem irebbiten nneɣni ḥima ad asen tɛebdem u ad asen tbendqem. War d ayi seɛɛarem s tmegga n ifassen nwem, maḥend war d awem tteggeɣ řɣar.’  
\v 7 Maca kenniw war ɣari tesřim ca, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ařami d ayi tesɛarem s tmegga n ifassen nwem, i txessart nwem.”   
\m
\v 8 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Minzi kenniw war tesřim ca ɣar wawařen inu,  
\v 9 xzar, s uya ad ggeɣ ad awyeɣ marra řaǧat zi ccamal, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, uřa d Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, amsexxar inu. Necc ad ten ssiwḍeɣ x temmurt-a u x imezdaɣ nnes u x marra řegnus i d as dd-innḍen uca ad ten ḥarrmeɣ i uteḥḥi. Necc ad ten ggeɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d tseḍḥact uřa d řxirbat i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 25:9 \xt Irm. 19:8\x*  
\v 10 Necc ad zzaysen kkseɣ řḥess n řefraḥet d řḥess n warcaq, tmijja n muřay d tmijja n tesřit, ddriz n yeẓra n tsirt uřa d tfawt n řefnar. \x ◘ \xo 25:10 \xt Ica. 24:7; Irm. 7:34; 16:9; Ḥiz. 26:13\x*  
\v 11 Tammurt-a marra ad tedweř d řxirbet uřa d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ, u řegnus-a ad sexxaren ajeǧid n Babil, \bd sebɛin n iseggʷusa\bd*.   
\m
\v 12 Xmi ɣa ɛdun sebɛin n iseggʷusa nni, xenni ad xeřfeɣ zeg ujeǧid n Babil d řgens nni x řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, uřa x temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen. Necc ad tt arreɣ d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 25:12 \xt 2 Im. 36:22; Ɛiz. 1:1; Irm. 29:10; Dan. 9:2\x*  
\v 13 Necc ad dd-ssehwiɣ x temmurt nni marra awařen inu nni xas nniɣ, marra min yurin deg wedlis ittwannḍen, min inebba Irmiya x marra řegnus.  
\v 14 Maɣar uřa d nitni, \add wah,\add* nitni, ad ɛebbden i waṭṭas n řegnus d ijeǧiden imeqqranen, uca \add ammu\add* Necc ad zzaysen xeřfeɣ ɛlaḥsab timegga nsen u ɛlaḥsab řxedmet n ifassen nsen.’” \x ◘ \xo 25:14 \xt Irm. 27:7\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řkas n weɣḍab n SIDI  
\m
\v 15 “Maɣar ammu i d ayi inna SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ksi řkas-a n binu n wesɛar zeg ufus inu u ewc i-t i marra řegnus mani cek i ɣa ssekkeɣ, ḥima ad swen, \x ◘ \xo 25:15 \xt Irm. 13:12\x*  
\v 16 maḥend ad swen, ad meyyřen ssa ɣar da, ad dewřen ttbuhřuyen zi ssibbet n ssif nni dd ɣa ssekkeɣ jar asen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 \add Awarni uya\add* ksiɣ řkas zeg ufus n SIDI, wciɣ t i marra řegnus, mani i d ayi issekk SIDI:   
\m
\v 18 ... \bd i Urcalim d tneddam n Yahuda\bd*, i ijeǧiden nnes d řḥukkam nnes, ḥima ad ten arreɣ d řxirbet, d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d tseḍḥact uřa d nneɛřet, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a,   
\m
\v 19 ... \bd i Fiřɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra\bd*, i umsexxaren nnes, řḥukkam nnes u i marra řgens nnes, \x ◘ \xo 25:19 \xt Irm. 46\x*   
\m
\v 20 ... \bd i ubarru n ɛřam kuř ibarraniyyen\bd*  
\m ... \bd i ijeǧiden n temmurt n Ɛuṣ\bd*  
\m ... \bd i marra ijeǧiden n temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen\bd*, i Acqalun, Ɣazza, Ɛaqrun u i marra min iqqimen zi Acdud, \x ◘ \xo 25:20 \xt Irm. 47:4-7\x*   
\m
\v 21 ... \bd i Idum, Mu’ab d ayt n Ɛammun,\bd* \x ◘ \xo 25:21 \xt Irm. 48; 49:1-22\x*   
\m
\v 22 ... \bd i marra ijeǧiden n Ṣur, i marra ijeǧiden n Ṣidun u i ijeǧiden n tegzirin\bd* x ujemmaḍ n řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 25:22 \xt Irm. 47:4\x*   
\m
\v 23 ... \bd i Dadan, Tayma, Buz\bd* d marra inni ittḥeffan \add acuwwaf\add* ɣar ṭṭrufa, \x ◘ \xo 25:23 \xt Lawi 19:27; 21:5; Irm. 9:25; Irm. 49:8, 32 \x*   
\m
\v 24 ... \bd i marra ijeǧiden n temmurt n Weɛraben u i marra ijeǧiden n ɛřam kuř ibarraniyyen nni izeddɣen di řexřa,\bd* \x ◘ \xo 25:24 \xt Irm. 49:31\x*   
\m
\v 25 ... \bd i marra ijeǧiden n Zimri, u i marra ijeǧiden n Ɛilam u i marra ijeǧiden n Maday,\bd* \x ◘ \xo 25:25 \xt Irm. 49:34\x*   
\m
\v 26 ... \bd i marra ijeǧiden n ccamal\bd*, inni yudsen d yinni iggʷejen, ijjen awarni i wenneɣni,  
\m ... \bd i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect i iǧan x wudem n temmurt\bd*,  
\m \bd uca awarni asen \+bdit marra\+bdit* ad isu ujeǧid n Cicak, \+bdit ixs ad yini Babil\+bdit*\bd*.   
\m
\v 27 “Ad asen tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Swem, scarem, ɛuqqem, wḍam u war tekkarem ɛad zzat i ssif i dd ɣa ssekkeɣ jar awem.’  
\v 28 Xmi ɣa agin ad ksin řkas zeg ufus nnec maḥend ad t swen, \add xenni\add* ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: Ad teswem s uɣiř!  
\v 29 Maɣar xzar, di tendint i x ittwabarreḥ s Yisem inu, ad bdiɣ s řɣar. Ma ad daywem ggen am tteggen ak-d imezdagen? Kenniw war ttwaḥesben d imezdagen, maɣar ad řaɣiɣ i ssif ḍidd i marra imezdaɣ n temmurt, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.’” \x ◘ \xo 25:29 \xt 1 Bṭ. 4:17\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 30 “Ad xasen tnebbid marra awařen-a uca ad d asen tinid: ‘SIDI ad dd-izehhar zi sennej uca Netta ad issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes zi Tzeddiɣt nnes Iqeddsen. Netta ad izehhar x Tzeddiɣt nnes, ad iřaɣa am t tteggen inni yareffsen aḍiř, ḍidd i marra imezdaɣ n ddunect.\x ◘ \xo 25:30 \xt Yuw. 4:16; Ɛam. 1:2; Asa. 19:15, 16\x*  
\v 31 Ad dd-yas ijj n řḥess issnexřiɛen ař tma n temmurt, minzi SIDI ɣares ict n ddeɛwet ak-d řegnus. Netta ad iḥkem x bnadem am ikmeř, ad iɛarren marra iɛeffanen ɣar ssif, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’  
\v 32 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Xzar, ijj n řɣar tessuruf zi řgens ɣar řgens nneɣni, ict n tharyaḍt tewɛar tekkar-dd zi tmuwwa n temmurt.  
\v 33 \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad iřin inni ittwassnuqqben \add s ssif\add* x ict n tma n temmurt ař tma nneɣni. War xasen ttrun, war ten jarrwen u war ten neṭṭřen. Ad dewřen d řeɣbar x wudem n temmurt.\x ◘ \xo 25:33 \xt Irm. 16:4\x*  
\v 34 Rum, \add kenniw\add* imeksawen, sɣuyem. Zuzzarem \add acař\add* x yixef nwem, \add kenniw\add* inni ɣar iǧa jjehd x tḥimriwin n wuǧi, maɣar yiweḍ-dd řḥař n tɣarṣt nwem, u Necc ad kenniw zuzzareɣ u kenniw ad tefruryem am yijj n uɣarraf iɣřa. \x ◘ \xo 25:34 \xt Ica. 65:12; Irm. 4:8; 6:26; 9:16; 12:3; 13:14, 24; 18:17\x*  
\v 35 War tneffeɛ tarewřa i imeksawen uřa d wenjam n yinni ɣar iǧa jjehd x tḥimriwin n wuǧi.  
\v 36 Sḥessem mammec sɣuyyun imeksawen s jjehd, \add mammec\add* ttrun inni ɣar iǧa jjehd x tḥimriwin n wuǧi, minzi SIDI ittareddeǧ ddmani nsen n tarewsa.  
\v 37 Maɣar ddmani n tarewsa ad dewřen ugnun zi ssibbet n řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI.  
\v 38 Am weyrad ameẓyan ijja Netta adurri nnes, maɣar tammurt nsen tedweř d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ s řḥaduq \add n ssif\add* n wenni iḥeṣṣaren, s řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 26
\s1 Irmiya di Zzawect Tameqqrant - Aneqqi n unabi Uriya  
\m
\v 1 Deg umezwaru n tgelda n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, yusa-dd wawař-a zi SIDI, inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Bedd di řemraḥ n zzat n Taddart n SIDI uca ini marra awařen-a nni zi cek weṣṣiɣ maḥend ad zzaysen tessiwřed i \add imezdaɣ n\add* marra tineddam n Yahuda nni dd-yusin maḥend ad bendqen di Taddart n SIDI. War ttejji uřa d ijj n wawař war t teqqared.  
\v 3 Ad taɣ ad sřen, ad dd-dewřen, kuř ijj zeg webrid aɛeffan nnes, uca ad nedmeɣ x řɣar nni nwiɣ ad daysen t ggeɣ zi ssibbet n tuɛeffna n tmegga nsen. \x ◘ \xo 26:3 \xt Irm. 18:8\x*  
\v 4 Ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Mařa kenniw war tᵉttexsem ad ɣari tesřem maḥend ad tuyurem ɛlaḥsab Ccariɛa inu nni d awem ggiɣ deg ufus,  
\v 5 \add u maḥend\add* ad tesřem ɣar wawařen n imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen nni d awem dd-ssekkeɣ zeg umezwaru, waxxa kenniw war \add d asen\add* tesřim, \x ◘ \xo 26:5 \xt Irm. 7:13, 25; 11:7; 25:3\x*  
\v 6 xenni ad ggeɣ ak-d Taddart-a am ggiɣ ak-d Cilu, uca ad arreɣ tandint d nneɛřet i marra řegnus di temmurt.’” \x ◘ \xo 26:6 \xt 1 Ṣm. 4:12; Izhd. 78:60; Irm. 7:12, 14\x*   
\m
\v 7 Ikehhanen d inabiyyen d marra řgens sřin mammec issiweř Irmiya awařen-a di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 8 Umi ikemmeř Irmiya awař x marra min tuɣa i d as iweṣṣa SIDI maḥend ad t inna i marra řgens, ṭṭfen t ikehhanen d inabiyyen d marra řgens uca nnan: “Ittxeṣṣa ad temmted!  
\v 9 Mayemmi tnebbid s Yisem n SIDI, tennid: ‘Taddart-a ad tedweř am Cilu u tandint-a ad tᵉttwareddeǧ ařami war dayes izeddeɣ uřa d ijjen?’” Marra řgens imun x Irmiya di Taddart n SIDI.   
\m
\v 10 Umi sřin řḥukkam n Yahuda awařen-a, ffɣen-dd zi taddart n ujeǧid geɛɛden ɣar Taddart n SIDI, qqimen ɣar wadaf n tewwart n jdid n Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* ssiwřen ikehhanen d inabiyyen ak-d řḥukkam u ak-d marra řgens, nnan: “Aryaz-a isdaheǧ řmewt, am mammec tt tesřam s imezzuɣen nwem.”   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Irmiya ak-d marra řḥukkam u ak-d marra řgens, inna: “SIDI issekk ayi-dd ḥima ad nebbiɣ marra awařen i tesřim ḍidd i Taddart-a u ḍidd i tendint-a.  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ɛedřem ibriden nwem d tmegga nwem uca ṣřem i tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, \add xenni\add* ad indem SIDI zi marra řɣar i xawem inna. \x ◘ \xo 26:13 \xt Irm. 7:3\x*  
\v 14 \add Maca\add* necc, xzar, aqa ayi deg ufus nwem, ggem zzayi mammec i d awem ittɣiř d lemliḥ d nican di tiṭṭawin nwem.  
\v 15 Snem \add maca\add* nican, mařa kenniw tenɣim ayi, ad dd-tawyem idammen imezdagen x yixef nwem u x tendint-a u x imezdaɣ nnes, minzi s tidett, SIDI issekk ayi-dd ɣarwem maḥend ad awem iniɣ marra awařen-a deg imezzuɣen nwem.”   
\m
\v 16 Řḥukkam d marra řgens nnan i ikehhanen u i inabiyyen: “Aryaz-a war issdiḥeǧ řmewt, maɣar netta issawař akidneɣ s Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.”  
\v 17 Ca n iryazen zeg imɣaren n temmurt kkaren, bedden. Nitni ssiwřen ɣar marra agraw n řgens, nnan:  
\v 18 “Mixa zi Muracit tuɣa ittnabba deg wussan n Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, uca issiweř ɣar marra řgens n Yahuda, inna: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: Ṣihyun ad tᵉttwacarz am yijj n yeyyar u \add tandint n\add* Urcalim ad tedweř d řxarbet u adrar n Taddart-a \add ad idweř\add* d řegɛudi \add mani ɣa wehhben tiwhibin\add* deg wezɣar.’ \f ◼ \fr 26:18 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 26:18 \xt Mixa 1:1; 3:12\x*  
\v 19 Ma inɣa i-t Ḥizqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d marra Yahuda? Ma war iggʷid netta SIDI u iksi s řmeɛruf řebda i SIDI ařami indem SIDI x řɣar i xasen iqqar? Neccin ad negg ijj n řɛib d ameqqran i yixef nneɣ.” \f ◼ \fr 26:19 \ft \+fk i yixef nneɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmur nneɣ’.\f*   
\m
\v 20 Tuɣa din ɛad ijj n weryaz \add nneɣni\add* wenni tuɣa ittnebban s Yisem n SIDI, Uriya, mmis n Camɛiya, zi Qaryat-Yaɛarim. Netta inebba ḍidd i tendint-a u ḍidd i temmurt-a ɛlaḥsab marra awařen nni inna Irmiya.  
\v 21 \add Xmi\add* isřa ujeǧid Yahuyaqim \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra řḥukkam awařen nnes, ixs ujeǧid ad t ineɣ. Isřa Uriya aya, iggʷed, yarweř u yiweḍ ɣar Miṣra.  
\v 22 Ajeǧid Yahuyaqim \add maca\add* issekk iryazen ɣar Miṣra: Il-Natan, mmis n Ɛakbur ak-d ca n iryazen. Issekk i-ten ɣar Miṣra.  
\v 23 Nitni iwyen-dd Uriya zi Miṣra uca nedhen t ɣar ujeǧid Yahuyaqim u wanita inɣa i-t s ssif. Netta inḍar řxecbet nnes deg imeḍřan n tarwa n řgens.   
\m
\v 24 \add Maca\add* afus n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, tuɣa-t ak-d Irmiya maḥend war t tticen deg ifassen n řgens maḥend ad t nɣen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 27
\s1 Axḍaɛ i Babil  
\m
\v 1 Deg umezwar n tgelda n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, yusa-dd wawař-a ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i d ayi inna SIDI: ‘Egg i yixef nnec iseɣwan d izayřuten, u ssars i-ten x yiri nnec \x ◘ \xo 27:2 \xt Irm. 28:10\x*  
\v 3 uca sekk i-ten i ujeǧid n Idum, i ujeǧid n Mu’ab, i ujeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun, i ujeǧid n Ṣur u i ujeǧid n Ṣidun, s ufus n imsexxaren inni dd-yusin ɣar Urcalim ɣar Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda.  
\v 4 Umur asen ad inin i isiditen nsen: Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, ammu i ittxeṣṣa ad tinim i isiditen nwem:  
\v 5 S jjehd inu ameqqran d ufus inu isswiẓẓaden ggiɣ tammurt d bnadem d řebhayem nni iǧan x wudem n temmurt uca Necc ad ten wceɣ i wenni isdaheǧen di tiṭṭawin inu. \x ◘ \xo 27:5 \xt Dan. 4:14, 22\x*  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, Necc ggiɣ marra timmura-ya deg ufus n Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, amsexxar inu. Wciɣ as uřa d řmař n yeyyar, maḥend ad xas sexxaren. \x ◘ \xo 27:6 \xt Irm. 25:9\x*  
\v 7 Marra řegnus ad as sexxaren uřa i mmis d mmis n mmis ařami i dd ɣa yas řḥař i temmurt nnes. \add Xenni\add* aṭṭas n řegnus d ijeǧiden imeqqranen ad ggen ad zzayes ttwasexxaren.  
\v 8 Řgens d tgeldit i war ixs ad as isexxar i Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, uca war ixs ad issehwa iři nnes swadday i uzayřu n ujeǧid n Babil, aqa Necc ad xeřfeɣ zi řgens nni s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ař ten i ɣa qḍiɣ s ufus nnes.  
\v 9 Kenniw \add xenni\add*, war ttesřim i inabiyyen nwem d igezzanen nwem d ayt n bu-tirja nwem d ibezgawen nwem d iseḥḥaren nwem nni ɣarwem issawařen, qqaren: Kenniw war tsexxaram ca i ujeǧid n Babil!,  
\v 10 maɣar nitni ttnebban s ixarriqen maḥend ad kenniw ssiggʷejen x temmurt nwem, ařami Necc ad xawen aẓẓřeɣ uca kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem.  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* řgens nni i ɣa issaḍaren iři nnes swadday i uzayřu n ujeǧid n Babil uca ad as issexxar, aqa řgens nni ad t jjeɣ ad iqqim di temmurt nnes, uca ad tt icarz u ad dayes izdeɣ!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* ssiwřeɣ ɣar Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɛlaḥsab marra awařen-a, nniɣ: “Ggem iřawen nwem swadday i uzayřu n ujeǧid n Babil u sexxarem as u i řgens nnes, \add xenni\add* ad teqqimem teddarem.  
\v 13 Mayemmi ɣa tᵉttwanɣem, cek d řgens nnec, s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun, am mammec issiweř SIDI x řgens i war ixsen ad isexxar i ujeǧid n Babil.  
\v 14 War ttesřim i wawařen n inabiyyen, inni ɣarwem issawařen, qqaren: ‘Kenniw war tᵉttsexxarem ca i ujeǧid n Babil!’, maɣar nitni ttnebban awem s ixarriqen, \x ◘ \xo 27:14 \xt Irm. 14:14; 23:21; 29:8\x*  
\v 15 minzi Necc war ten dd-ssekkeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, u nitni ttnebban s ixarriqen s Yisem inu maḥend ad kenniw aẓẓřeɣ u kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem, kenniw d inabiyyen nni d awem ittnabben,”   
\m
\v 16 Ssiwřeɣ uřa ak-d ikehhanen u ak-d marra řgens, nniɣ: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War tesřim ɣar wawařen n inabiyyen nwem i iqqaren: Xzar, řeqcuɛ zi Taddart n SIDI ad ttwarren deɣya zi Babil!, maɣar nitni ttnebban i kenniw s ixarriqen. \x ◘ \xo 27:16 \xt Irm. 28:3\x*  
\v 17 War ɣarsen ttesřim ca, \add maca\add* sexxarem i ujeǧid n Babil, \add xenni\add* ad teqqimem teddarem. Mayemmi ɣa tedweř tendint-a d ict n řxirbet?  
\v 18 Mři nitni d inabiyyen, u awař n SIDI iǧa \add s tidett\add* ɣarsen, ejj i-ten ad ttaren i SIDI n řɛeskarat, aqa řeqcuɛ i iqqimen ɛad di Taddart n SIDI u di taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda di Urcalim war ttriḥen ɣar Babil.  
\v 19 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat x ipilaren, x řebḥar n nnḥas, x tkarrutin u x marra řeqcuɛ nneɣni i iqqimen di tendint-a,  
\v 20 inni war kides iksi Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, umi indeh Yakunya, mmis n Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda, zi Urcalim ɣar Babil ak-d marra tarwa n taṣiřet n Yahuda d Urcalim, \x ◘ \xo 27:20 \xt 2 Ij. 24:14, 15\x*  
\v 21 \add wah,\add* ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, x řeqcuɛ i iqqimen di Taddart n SIDI u di taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda u di Urcalim:  
\v 22 Ɣar Babil ad mmeksin u ad qqimen dinni ař ass i ɣarsen dd ɣa arzfeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \add Xenni\add* ad ten ssuffɣeɣ u ad ten dd-arreɣ ɣar wemcan-a.’” \x ◘ \xo 27:22 \xt 2 Ij. 25:13; 2 Im. 36:18, 22; Irm. 29:10\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 28
\s1 Anabi Ḥananya  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas nni, deg umezwaru n tgelda n ujeǧid Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa, deg uyur wiss xemsa, issiweř akidi Ḥananya, mmis n Ɛazur, anabi zi Jibɛun, di Taddart n SIDI zzat i tiṭṭawin n ikehhanen d řgens imun, inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, iqqar: ‘Necc ad arẓeɣ azayřu n ujeǧid n Babil.  
\v 3 Ɛad tnayen n iseggʷusa \add xenni\add* Necc ad dd-arreɣ ɣar temmurt-a marra řeqcuɛ n Taddart n SIDI, inni iksi Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, zeg wemcan-a uca yiwy-i-ten ɣar Babil. \x ◘ \xo 28:3 \xt Irm. 27:16\x*  
\v 4 Necc ad ssɛeqbeɣ Yakunya, mmis n Yahuyaqim, d marra imenfiyyen zi Yahuda i dd-yiwḍen ɣar Babil, ɣar wemcan-a, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, minzi Necc ad arẓeɣ azayřu n ujeǧid n Babil.’”   
\m
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna unabi Irmiya i unabi Ḥananya - zzat i tiṭṭawin n ikehhanen u zzat i tiṭṭawin n řgens imun, inni ibedden di Taddart n SIDI -  
\v 6 \add wah ammu i\add* inna Irmiya: “Amin, ammu i ɣa yegg SIDI! Iři ad isseqfeř SIDI awařen nnec i tnebbid ařami ɣa yarr řeqcuɛ n Taddart n SIDI d marra inni ittwanedhen di lmenfa zi Babil ɣar wemcan-a!  
\v 7 Seř \add maca\add* i wawař-a i zi ssawařeɣ deg imezzuɣen nwem u deg imezzuɣen n řgens imun:  
\v 8 ‘Inabiyyen nni tuɣa \add din\add* iǧan qbeř inu d kenniw zeg wecḥař uya, nebban ḍidd i waṭṭas n temmura u ḍidd i waṭṭas n tgelditin x garra, x iceřwawen u x ṭṭaɛun.  
\v 9 \add Maca\add* anabi nni ittnabben x sřam, mařa awař n unabi nni ad dd-iffeɣ, \add xenni\add* ad yiři ittwassen \add s tidett\add* aqa SIDI issekk-dd anabi nni.’”   
\m
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* iksi unabi Ḥananya azayřu n yiri n unabi Irmiya, yarẓ i-t.  
\v 11 Uca issiweř Ḥananya zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra řgens, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Qbeř i ɣa ɛdun tnayen n iseggʷusa kemmřen ad arẓeɣ azayřu n Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, \add i iǧan\add* x yiřawen n marra řegnus.” Uca Irmiya yuyur abrid nnes.   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya awarni i umi yarẓa unabi Ḥananya azayřu x yiřawen n unabi Irmiya, inna:  
\v 13 “Uyur, siweř ak-d Ḥananya, ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Izayřuten n ukeccuḍ tarẓid ten, \add maca\add* teggid izayřuten n wuzzař deg wemcan nsen.’  
\v 14 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ijj n uzayřu n wuzzař ssarseɣ t x yiřawen n marra řegnus, maḥend ad sexxaren i Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil. Nitni ad as sexxaren. Uřa d řmař wciɣ ten deg ufus nnes.’” \x ◘ \xo 28:14 \xt Irm. 27:6\x*   
\m
\v 15 \add Xas uca\add* inna unabi Irmiya i unabi Ḥananya: “Seř, Ḥananya, SIDI war cek dd issekk ca u cek tɣarred řgens-a ad ittceř x ixarriqen.  
\v 16 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, xzar, Necc ad cek nḍareɣ. \add Ɛad\add* deg useggʷas-a ad temmted minzi tessiwřed x uḥeyyed n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 28:16 \xt Aɛwd. 13:6; Irm. 29:32\x*  
\v 17 Immut unabi Ḥananya deg useggʷas nni, deg uyur wiss sebɛa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 29
\s1 Tabrat n Irmiya i imeḥbas di Babil  
\m
\v 1 Ina d awařen n tebrat i dd-issekk unabi Irmiya zi Urcalim i imɣaren \add n řgens\add* i iqqimen jar ayt n lmenfa i ikehhanen d inabiyyen u i marra řgens nni tuɣa indeh Nabuxadnaṣṣar zi Urcalim di lmenfa ɣar Babil,  
\v 2 awarni i umi iffeɣ ujeǧid Yakunya d yemmas n ujeǧid, řa imsexxaren icennɛen, řa řḥukkam n Yahuda d Urcalim, řa řemɛuǧam uřa d imziřen zi Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 29:2 \xt 2 Ij. 24:12 \x*  
\v 3 \add Issekk Irmiya tabrat nni\add* s ufus n Alɛasa, mmis n Cafan, d Jamarya, mmis n Ḥilqiya, inni issekk Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar Babil ɣar Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil. \add Tabrat\add* tenna:   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, i marra ayt n lmenfa nni dd-iwyeɣ zi Urcalim ɣar Babil:  
\v 5 ‘Sgeɛɛdem tudrin uca zedɣem daysent, ẓẓum iḥwicen uca ccem řɣiǧet nsen,  
\v 6 awyem timɣarin uca jjem-dd iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin, awyem i iḥenjiren nwem timɣarin uca wcem tḥenjirin nwem i yeryazen, maḥend ad urwent iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin. Ḥḍam ad dinni temmarnim, war tneqqṣem,  
\v 7 arzum řehna i tendint mani kenniw i ɣa nedheɣ u ttarem i man aya i SIDI, maɣar di řehna nnes i iǧa řehna nwem.’  
\v 8 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘War ttejjim ad kenniw cemten inabiyyen d igezzanen nni iǧan di řwesṭ nwem u war ttesřim ca ɣar ayt n bu-tirja i kenniw ittejjan ad tarjam, \x ◘ \xo 29:8 \xt Irm. 14:14; 23:31; 27:15\x*  
\v 9 maɣar nitni ttnebban ixarriqen s Yisem inu. Necc war ten dd-sekkeɣ ca, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’  
\v 10 Minzi ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xmi ɣa qefřen sebɛin n iseggʷusa di Babil, xenni ad kenniw arzfeɣ uca ad awem kemmřeɣ awař inu aṣebḥan umi kenniw ɣa arreɣ ɣar temmurt-a. \x ◘ \xo 29:10 \xt 2 Im. 36:22; Ɛiz. 1:1; Irm. 25:12; Dan. 9:2\x*  
\v 11 Maɣar Necc ssneɣ man ixarriṣen i ɣari xawem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ixarriṣen n řehna, war iǧi n řɣar, ḥima ad awem wceɣ imar d řayas.  
\v 12 \add Mařa\add* kenniw ad ayi třaɣam, ad ɣari teẓẓaǧem, Necc ad ɣarwem sřeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 29:12 \xt Dan. 9\x*  
\v 13 Ad xafi tarzum uca ad ayi tafem mařa kenniw tarzum xafi s marra wuř nwem.  
\v 14 Ad zzaywem ttwafeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast nwem uca ad kenniw ssmuneɣ zi marra řegnus u zi marra imucan mani xawem uẓẓřeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, u Necc ad kenniw arreɣ ɣar wemcan i zi kenniw nedheɣ di lmenfa.’”\x ◘ \xo 29:14 \xt Irm. 23:3\x*   
\m
\v 15 “\add Maca\add* minzi tennam: ‘SIDI issnekkar aneɣ-dd inabiyyen di Babil!’,  
\v 16 x uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x ujeǧid, wenni iqqimen x řɛarc n Dawud, u x marra řgens i izeddɣen di tendint-a, aytmatwem inni war akidwem yuyuren di lmenfa,  
\v 17 \add wah,\add* ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: “Xzar, Necc ad ssekkeɣ jar asen ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun uca ad ten jjeɣ am tazart ixsaren, tenni war iḥřin maḥend ad zzayes ccen. \x ◘ \xo 29:17 \xt Irm. 24:8, 10\x*  
\v 18 Necc ad ten ḍfareɣ s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun u Necc ad ten arreɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect, ad tiřid d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* wexzi d usiggʷed d tseḍḥact d řḥegra jar marra řegnus mani ten i ɣa ssuffɣeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 29:18 \xt Aɛwd. 28:25,37; Irm. 15:4; 24:9, 10\x*  
\v 19 minzi nitni war sřin ɣar wawařen inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, umi ɣarsen dd-ssekkeɣ imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen. Ɛad zeg umezwaru ssekkeɣ ten, maca kenniw war tesřim ca, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 20 “Kenniw \add maca\add*, sřem i wawař n SIDI, marra kenniw inni ittwanedhen di lmenfa, inni ssekkeɣ zi Urcalim ɣar Babil.  
\v 21 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, x Axab, mmis n Qulaya, u x Ṣidqiya, mmis n Maɛasiya, inni d awem ittnebban deg Yisem inu s ixarriqen: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ten ggeɣ deg ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, u netta ad ten ineɣ zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem.  
\v 22 Marra ayt n lmenfa zi Yahuda nni \add iǧan\add* di Babil ad zzaysen kksen ict n nneɛřet, ad inin: SIDI ad cek yegg am Ṣidqiya d Aḥab nni icnef ujeǧid n Babil s tmessi!,  
\v 23 minzi nitni ggin ict n tubbuheřya di Israil: nitni znan ak-d temɣarin n wi ten yudsen u barrḥen s Yisem inu awařen n ixarriqen i tuɣa war d asen nniɣ. Necc d wenni issnen d wenni icehden \add x man aya\add*!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 24 \bd I Camɛiya zi Naḥlam\bd*, ittxeṣṣa ad kides tessiwřed ad as tinid \add ammu\add*:   
\m
\v 25 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, iqqar: ‘Minzi s isem nnec i-dd-tessekked tibratin i marra řgens di Urcalim u i ukehhan Ṣafanya, mmis n Maɛasiya, u i marra ikehhanen, yura daysen: \f ◼ \fr 29:25 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*   
\m
\v 26 SIDI igga cek d akehhan deg wemcan n ukehhan Yahuyadaɛ, maḥend ad din iřin iweqqafen di Taddart n SIDI x kuř ijj ubuhaři nni itteggen ixef nnes d anabi. Ad t teqqned x ukeccuḍ ak-d řgid x yiri \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 29:26 \xt Irm. 20:1, 2, 3\x*  
\v 27 Xenni řexxu, mayemmi war tɛaqbed Irmiya zi Ɛanatut, wenni xawem ittarran ixef nnes d anabi?  
\v 28 Maɣar netta issekk-dd \add ict n tebrat\add* i neccin di Babil mani iqqar: Aṭṭas i ɣa iqqimen! Sbeddem tudrin u zedɣem daysent, ẓẓum iḥwicen u ad tawyem řiqqi i řɣiǧet nsen!”   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Tuɣa iqqar ukehhan Ṣafanya tabrat-a deg imezzuɣen n unabi Irmiya.  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:   
\m
\v 31 “Sqad areqqas-a i marra ayt n lmenfa: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI x Cimɛiya zi Naḥlam: Minzi Camɛiya tuɣa ittnabb awem, waxxa Necc war t-i-dd ssekkeɣ, uca yarra kenniw ad tᵉttiqqem deg ixarriqen!’,\x ◘ \xo 29:31 \xt Irm. 28:15\x*  
\v 32 s uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad xeřfeɣ i Camɛiya zi Naḥlam u zi tarwa nnes. Uřa d ijjen zeg inni nnes war ittɣimi izdeɣ di řwesṭ n řgens-a u netta war iẓarr řxir i ɣa ggeɣ i řgens inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, minzi s řhard nnes igga ad ḥeyyden x SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 29:32 \xt Irm. 28:16\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 30
\s1 Ařeqqeḥ n Israil  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-yusin zi SIDI i Irmiya, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, iqqar: ‘Ari marra awařen nni d ac nniɣ deg ijj n wedlis.  
\v 3 Maɣar xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad qeřbeɣ tameḥbast n řgens inu, Israil d Yahuda, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Necc ad ten arreɣ ɣar temmurt i wciɣ i řejdud nsen u nitni ad tt ṭṭfen d tasɣart.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Ina d awařen i zi issiweř SIDI x Israil d Yahuda:   
\m
\v 5 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Nesřa řḥess issiggʷaden, \add ijj n řḥess\add* issnexřiɛen, war iǧi \add n\add* řehna.  
\v 6 Seqsam u xzarem, ma izemmar weryaz ad yaruw? Mayemmi i ttwařiɣ marra iryazen s ifassen x tejɛinna nsen am yict n temɣart tᵉttaru, u qaɛ aɣembub idweř iwarɣ am řxecbet? \x ◘ \xo 30:6 \xt Irm. 4:31; 6:24\x*  
\v 7 Uct, maɣar d ameqqran ass nni, war iǧi uřa d ijjen am netta. Ict n řweqt n řeḥṣaret i Yaɛqub, \add maca\add* netta ad zzayes ittwassenjem. \x ◘ \xo 30:7 \xt Yuw. 2:11; Ṣaf. 1:15\x*  
\v 8 Deg wass nni ad imsar, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, ad arẓeɣ azayřu x yiřawen nnec. Ibarraniyyen war t ttejjin ad xasen isexxar \add ɛad am yismeɣ\add*,  
\v 9 Nitni ad sexxaren i SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uřa i ujeǧid nsen Dawud wenni dd ɣa ssekkareɣ di ṭṭweɛ nsen.’” \x ◘ \xo 30:9 \xt Ḥiz. 34:23, 24; 37:24; Ḥuc. 3:5\x*   
\m
\v 10 “War teggʷed, \add a\add* cek amsexxar inu Yaɛqub, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, war tefciř ca, \add a\add* Israil, maɣar xzar, Necc ad cek ssnejmeɣ zi timmura iggʷejen uřa d zzariɛet nnec zi tmeḥbast nsen. Ad yareggʷeḥ Yaɛqub, ad ɣares tiři řhudnet, ad iddar di řaman uca uřa d ijj war t issnexřiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 30:10 \xt Ica. 41:13; 43:5; 44:1; Irm. 46:28\x*  
\v 11 Maɣar Necc akidek, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ḥima ad cek ssnejmeɣ, maɣar Necc ad qḍiɣ marra řegnus nni ɣar cek zuzzareɣ, maca ɛemmarṣ war cek qeṭṭiɣ, \add maca\add* ad cek arebbiɣ s řeɛbar iseggden u war cek heṣṣbeɣ d amezdag.” \x ◘ \xo 30:11 \xt Ica. 27:8; Irm. 4:27; 5:10, 18; 10:24; 46:28\x*   
\m
\v 12 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Tareẓẓit nnem war tzemmar ad teggenfa, ayezzim nnem itteqqes. \x ◘ \xo 30:12 \xt Irm. 10:19; 15:18\x*  
\v 13 Uřa d ijj war xam issɛizz ař i cem i ɣa icfen, war ɣarem ca ddawat ḥima ad tent tegged x tḥebbuct nnem.  
\v 14 Marra inni tuɣa i cem ittexsen ttun cem, war xam ttseqsin, maɣar am mammec iccat řeɛdu ammu i cem wtiɣ, am yijjen i yarebban s řeqsaḥet, zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nnem imɣaren, \add maɣar\add* ddnub nnem wesɛen aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 30:14 \xt Irm. 22:20\x*  
\v 15 Mayemmi tesɣuyyud \add ammu\add* x treẓẓit nnem, x řeḥriq nnem i war izemmaren ad iggenfa? Zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nnem imɣaren, \add maɣar\add* ddnub nnem wesɛen aṭṭas, Necc ggiɣ dayem man aya. \x ◘ \xo 30:15 \xt Irm. 5:6; 13:17\x*  
\v 16 S uya, marra inni cem itteffzen, ad ttwaccen \add simant nsen\add*, uca marra iɣrimen nnem ad uyuren di tmeḥbast, u inni cem ikeccḍen, ad ttwakeccḍen u marra inni cem yucaren, ad ten wceɣ d tukkarḍa. \x ◘ \xo 30:16 \xt Uf. 23:22; Ica. 41:11; Irm. 10:25\x*  
\v 17 Maɣar Necc ad cem cefneɣ u ad cem ssgenfiɣ zeg iyezzimen nnem nni i dayem wtin nitni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, minzi nitni řaɣan am ‘Tamenḍart!’, qqaren: Aqa-tt d Ṣihyun, war xas ittseqsi uřa d ijj!’”   
\m
\v 18 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n iqiḍan n Yaɛqub uca ad areḥmeɣ x tzeddiɣin nsen. Ad bnan tandint ɛawed x řxirbat nnes uca řeqṣar ad dd-idweř ɣar wemcan nnes iṣeḥḥ.  
\v 19 Ad zzaysen iffeɣ \add ijj n izři n\add* uqadi d ict n tmijja n yewdan ifarrḥen. Necc ad ten arreɣ deg waṭṭas, nitni war dikkwiřen drus, u Necc ad asen ggeɣ řɛezz u nitni war ttwasseḥqirin \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 30:19 \xt Irm. 31:4\x*  
\v 20 Iḥenjiren nnes ad iřin am yinni zeg wecḥař uya uca tamesmunt nnes ad tiři zzat i wudem inu u Necc ad xeřfeɣ zeg inni i-ten iḥṣaren.  
\v 21 Amzemmar nnes ad zzayes yiři u Řḥakem nnes ad zzayes iffeɣ u Necc ad t-i-dd-ssqarrbeɣ u Netta ad ayi dd-yades, maɣar man Wen iǧan d aḍman s wuř nnes maḥend ad ɣari dd-yades?’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 22 “Kenniw ad ayi tiřim d řgens inu d Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nwem.”\x ◘ \xo 30:22 \xt Irm. 24:7; 31:1,33; 32:38\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 “Xzar, taḥaryaḍt n SIDI, iffeɣ-dd \add zzayes\add* wesɛar, \add am\add* tḥaryaḍt tezzebzib nni i ɣa ihwan x uzeǧif n iɛeffanen. \x ◘ \xo 30:23 \xt Irm. 23:19, 20; 25:32\x*  
\v 24 Řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI war ittbeddi ca ař d igga ixarriṣen n wuř nnes uca ikemmeř i-ten. Deg uneggar n wussan ad as tfehmem.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 31
\m
\v 1 “Di řweqt nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i marra řaǧat n Israil u nitni ad iřin d řgens inu.”   
\m
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Řgens n yinni inejmen zi ssif, yufa arḍa di řexřa, ejj ayi ad raḥeɣ Necc maḥend ad t ssareyyḥeɣ, \add wah, maḥend ad ssareyyḥeɣ\add* Israil!’”   
\m
\v 3 “Zi řaggʷaj iban ayi-dd SIDI!” ...  
\b  
\m “Necc tuɣa ttexseɣ cem s tayri n řebda, x uya cem dd-jebdeɣ s tmexsiwt icewwaren.  
\v 4 Necc ad cem bniɣ ɛawed, ad tᵉttwabnid ɛawed, \add a cem\add* Israil taɛzarect. Cem ad tzewwqed ixef nnem ɛawed s ibendiren, ad teffɣed s ccḍiḥ s nnubtat n yinni ifarrḥen. \x ◘ \xo 31:4 \xt Irm. 30:19\x*  
\v 5 Ad teẓẓud tizayarin deg imarjaɛen x idurar n Samarya: inni itteẓẓun ad tent ẓẓun u řɣiǧet ad zzayes arren meẓri. \x ◘ \xo 31:5 \xt Ica. 65:21\x*  
\v 6 Maɣar ad dd-yas wass nni di ad řaɣan iɛessasen x idurar n Ifrayim: ‘Kkarem, ejj aneɣ ad ngeɛɛed ɣar Ṣihyun, ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ!’” \x ◘ \xo 31:6 \xt Ica. 2:2, 3; Mixa 4:2\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ɣennjem s řefraḥet i Yaɛqub, sřiwřiwem i uzeǧif n řegnus, barrḥem, semɣarem t, inim: \add A\add* SIDI, senjem řgens nnec, min iqqimen zi Israil.  
\v 8 Xzar, Necc ad ten arreɣ ad dd-asen zi temmurt n ccamal u Necc ad ten ssmuneɣ zeg ineggura n temmurt. Aqa din jar asen idarɣařen d ineɛḍaben, tinni iǧan s ddeyset d tinni ittarwen. Ad ɛeqben ɣar da s ijj n wegraw \add n řgens\add* ameqqran. \x ◘ \xo 31:8 \xt Irm. 3:18\x*  
\v 9 Ad dd-asen ttrun, ad ten gewwdeɣ am kessin s řmeɛruf. Ad ten ssnedheɣ ɣar teɣzarin n waman, x ijj n webrid iseggmen mani war ttneqriḍen, maɣar Necc d Babas i Israil u Ifrayim d mmi amenzu.’” \x ◘ \xo 31:9 \xt Uf. 4:22\x*   
\m
\v 10 “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, \add a\add* kenniw řegnus, barrḥem t x tegzirin nni iggʷejen aṭṭas, inim: ‘D wenni tuɣa izzuzaren Israil, ad t issmun ɛawed u ad t yarwes am mammec yarekkwes umeksaw taḥimart nnes.  
\v 11 Maɣar SIDI aqa ifdi Yaɛqub uca ifekk i-t zeg ufus n wenni xas ijehden.’\f ◼ \fr 31:11 \ft \+fk ifekk\ft  - s lḥarf ‘ad ifdi’. Xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 31:11 \xt Ica. 40:10; 49:24, 25\x*  
\v 12 Nitni ad dd-asen u ad sřiwřewen x řgeɛɛdet n Ṣihyun uca ad azzřen ɣar řxar n SIDI, ɣar imendi, ɣar binu n jdid, ɣar zzect, ɣar izmaren u ɣar ifunasen d tfunasin. Řeɛmar nsen ad yiři am řeɛraṣi ittwassun uca ɛemmarṣ \add ɛad\add* ad iřin ceḍnen. \x ◘ \xo 31:12 \xt Ica. 61:11\x*  
\v 13 Xenni ad tfarḥ teɛzarect ɣar ccḍiḥ s nnubtat, uřa d iḥudriyyen d iwessura, \add nitni marra\add* munen, minzi Necc ad arreɣ acḍan nsen d arcuq, ad ten ɛezziɣ, ad ten ssfarḥeɣ awarni wecḍan nsen.  
\v 14 Necc ad ssjiwneɣ řeɛmar n ikehhanen s tadunt \add n tɣarṣa\add* uca ad idweř řgens inu ijjiwen s řxar inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 15 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Tᵉttwaseř ict n tmijja di Rama, aweɛɛed d imeṭṭawen imarzagen: Raḥil tᵉttru x tarwa nnes u war tᵉttexs ad tᵉttwaɛezza x iḥenjiren nnes, maɣar nitni war ǧin \add ɛad\add*.’ \x ◘ \xo 31:15 \xt Mt. 2:17, 18\x*  
\v 16 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ṭṭef tmijja nnem i unixses u tiṭṭawin nnem i imeṭṭawen, maɣar aqa teǧa řmunet i warber nnem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar nitni ad dd-ɛeqben zi temmurt n řeɛdu.  
\v 17 Aqa din řayas i tarwa nnem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar iḥenjiren \add nnem\add* ad dd-dewřen ɣar temmurt nsen.’”   
\m
\v 18 “Necc sřiɣ mliḥ mammec dd-ittcetca Ifrayim, inna: ‘Cek tarebbid ayi u necc ttwarebbiɣ am yijj n uɛejmi war ittḍawaɛen. Arr ayi, \add deɣya\add* necc xseɣ ad dd-dewřeɣ, maɣar Cek d SIDI, AREBBI inu. \x ◘ \xo 31:18 \xt Igjd. 5:21\x*  
\v 19 Maɣar awarni řami dd-dewřeɣ, tubeɣ, u awarni řami dewřeɣ ssneɣ, wtiɣ ixef inu x tmeṣṣaḍin. Necc seḍḥiɣ, nfeḍḥeɣ, maɣar necc arbuɣ řefḍiḥet n temẓi inu.’ \x ◘ \xo 31:19 \xt Aɛwd. 30:2\x*  
\v 20 Ma war iǧi Ifrayim d mmi iɣřan ɣari d aḥenjir inu iɛizzen? Maɣar kuř ict n twařa ssiwřeɣ ɣares \add s ufus n inabiyyen\add*, qqimeɣ ttidareɣ t. X uya iccat jjuf inu dayi. Nican Necc ad xas arreḥmeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 21 “Sbedd iquǧay \add i wescan n webrid\add*, sars iẓra \add n jjurrat n webrid\add*, egg uř nnem x webrid iseggmen, x webrid nni di teggured. Dweř, \add a\add* taɛzarect Israil, dweř ɣar tneddam nnem.  
\v 22 Ař meřmi ɛad texsed ad teqqimed tᵉttliɛed, \add a cem,\add* yeǧis i \add xafi\add* iḥeyyden? Maɣar SIDI igga ict n řḥajjet n jdid di temmurt: Tamɣart ad tᵉtthilla \add marra\add* i weryaz.”   
\m
\v 23 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ad ssiwřen awař-a ɛawed di temmurt n Yahuda u di tneddam nnes xmi ɣa ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast nsen: Ad cem ibarek SIDI, \add a\add* Tazeddiɣt n tsegda, \add a\add* adrar iqeddsen! \x ◘ \xo 31:23 \xt Irm. 50:7\x*  
\v 24 Yahuda d marra tineddam nnes ad dayes zeddɣent jmiɛ, ifeǧaḥen d yinni ittetliɛen ak-d tḥimart.  
\v 25 Maɣar Necc ssessuɣ řeɛmar yuḥřen uca ssjiwneɣ kuř řeɛmar iḥzen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 26 Awarni aya faqeɣ-dd uca uciɣ mecḥar yiziḍ yiḍeṣ inu.   
\b  
\m
\v 27 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad zarɛeɣ taddart n Israil d taddart n Yahuda s zzarriɛet n iwdan d řmař.  
\v 28 Am mammec xasen ɛesseɣ ḥima ad qeřɛeɣ, ad hedmeɣ, ad arẓeɣ, ad areddǧeɣ u ad ggeɣ řɣar, ammu i xasen i ɣa ɛesseɣ ḥima ad ssbeddeɣ u ḥima ad ẓẓuɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 29 Deg wussan nni war ttɣimin ad inin ɛad: ‘Ibabaten ccin aḍiř asemmam uca dewřent teɣmas n iḥenjiren ḥfant.’ \x ◘ \xo 31:29 \xt Ḥiz. 18:2, 3\x*  
\v 30 Maca kuř ijj ad immet zi ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet \add n yixef\add* nnes. Zi mkuř bnadem nni i ɣa iccen aḍir asemmam, ad as dewřent teɣmas ḥfant.”   
\m
\v 31 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, nni di ɣa ggeɣ ijj n Řɛahd n Jdid ak-d taddart n Israil u ak-d taddart n Yahuda, \x ◘ \xo 31:31 \xt Irm. 31:31; Mt. 26:28, Mk. 14:24, Lk. 22:20, 1 Kur. 11:25, 2 Kur. 3:6, Ɛbr. 8:6, 8, 13; 9:15; 12:24\x*  
\v 32 war iǧi am mammec Řɛahd i ggiɣ ak-d řejdud nsen umi ten ṭṭfeɣ zeg ufus, ḥima ad ten nedheɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra, Řɛahd inu nni arẓin, waxxa zeɛma Necc dewřeɣ d Aryaz nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 33 Maɣar wa ad yiři d Řɛahd nni i ɣa ggeɣ awarni i wussan nni ak-d taddart n Israil, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI: Necc ad ggeɣ Ccariɛa inu deg wuř nsen uca ad tt ariɣ deg wuř nsen. Necc ad iřiɣ d SIDI i nitni u nitni ad iřin d řgens i Necc. \x ◘ \xo 31:33 \xt Irm. 24:7; 30:22; 31:33\x*  
\v 34 Uřa d ijjen war isseřmid \add ɛad\add* jjar nnes niɣ umas, am qqaren: ‘Ssen SIDI!’, maɣar nitni marra ad ayi ssnen, am umeẓyan am umeqqran jar asen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar Necc ad asen ɣfareɣ i řmuɛṣiyyet nsen u war ttidareɣ \add ɛad\add* ddnub nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 31:34 \xt Ica. 54:13; Irm. 33:8; Mixa 7:18; Yḥ. 6:45; Řex. 10:43\x*   
\m
\v 35 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, wenni iggin tfuct i tfawt deg wass, \add wenni yumuren\add* taziri d itran i tfawt di ǧiřet, wenni issehwařen řebḥar ařami dd-duqquzent řemwaj nnes, aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes: \x ◘ \xo 31:35 \xt Amz. 1:16; Ica. 51:15\x*  
\v 36 ‘Mařa lfarayiḍ-a ad dd-wḍant zeg wudem inu, iqqar SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad ibedd uřa d zzariɛet n Israil ad tiři d ijj n řgens zzat i wudem inu, marra ussan.’  
\v 37 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Mařa ttwaɛbaren ijenwan sennej u \add mařa\add* zemmaren ad arzun sadu dsusa n temmurt, \add xenni\add* uřa d Necc ad nḍareɣ zzariɛet n Israil zi ssibbet n marra min ggin, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 38 “Xzar, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad dd-asen wussan nni di ɣa bnan tandint \add ɛawed\add* i SIDI, zi Ṣṣumɛet n Ḥananiyil ař Tewwart n Teɣmart,  
\v 39 uca ad iffeɣ ufiřu n řeqyas ɛad ktar, nican ɣar zzat ɣar tewrirt n Jarib uca \add xenni\add* ad imeyyeř ɣar Juɛa.  
\v 40 Marra taysart s řxecbat immuten u s yiɣɣeḍ d marra iyyaren ař teɣzart n Qidrun ař teɣmart n Tewwart n Yeysan ɣar ccarq, marra aya ad yiři d amqeddas i SIDI. Ɛemmarṣ ad tᵉttwaqřeɛ u ad tᵉttwahdem uřa d ict n řḥajjet ɛad i řebda.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 32
\s1 Tamesɣiwt n yeyyar  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya deg useggʷas wiss ɛecra n Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Aseggʷas-a tuɣa d aseggʷas wiss tmenṭac n Nabuxadraṣṣar.  
\v 2 Deg wussan nni tuɣa řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Babil iḥeṣṣar-dd Urcalim uca anabi Irmiya tuɣa ittwaḥebbes di řemraḥ n řeḥbes nni tuɣa di taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda.  
\v 3 Maɣar tuɣa iḥebbes i-t Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, am d as inna: “Mayemmi tᵉttnabbed, teqqared: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ tandint-a deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil u netta ad tt tᵉṭṭef.  
\v 4 Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, war inejjem zeg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen, maca ad immewc deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil. Netta ad kides issiweř zeg uqemmum ɣar uqemmum u netta ad t iẓar tiṭṭ di tiṭṭ. \x ◘ \xo 32:4 \xt Irm. 34:3\x*  
\v 5 Netta ad yawi Ṣidqiya ɣar Babil u netta ad dinni iqqim, ař ɣares i ɣa raḥeɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Waxxa kenniw ad temmenɣem ak-d Ikaldaniyyen, war ttikkwiḍem ca.’”   
\m
\v 6 Irmiya inna: “Yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, inna:  
\v 7 ‘Xzar, Ḥanam’il, mmis n ɛemmic Callum, ad ɣarek dd-yas uca ad yini: Seɣ i yixef nnec iyyar inu di Ɛanatut, maɣar cek ɣarek řḥeqq n řefdiyyet maḥend ad t tesɣid.’”  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd ɣari Ḥanam’il, mmis n ɛemmi, ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI, di řemraḥ n řeḥbes, inna ayi: “Seɣ xenni iyyar inu di Ɛanatut, di temmurt n Binyamin, maɣar cek ɣarek řḥeqq ad t twarted uca ɣarek \add řḥeqq\add* n usufeɣ maḥend ad t tefdid, ad t tesɣed.” Řexdenni ssneɣ illa awař-a yusa-dd zi SIDI.  
\v 9 \add Ammu i\add* sɣiɣ iyyar nni \add iǧan\add* di Ɛanatut x Ḥanam’il, mmis n ɛemmi, uca wezneɣ as nnuqart: sbeɛṭac ciqlu n nnuqart.  
\v 10 Necc weqqɛeɣ x tabrat, cemmɛeɣ tt uca jjiɣ cchud ad tt ssmetnen uca wezneɣ nnuqart di řmizan.  
\v 11 Ksiɣ tabrat ittwannḍen n tmesɣiwt, tenni tuɣa ittwacemmɛen, \add ittwari dayes\add* mammec ittwagg řɛahd u \add min ǧant\add* lfarayiḍ, uřa tabrat yarezmen  
\v 12 uca wciɣ tabrat ittwanḍen n tmesɣiwt i Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, mmis n Maḥsiya, zzat i tiṭṭawin n Ḥanam’il, mmis n ɛemmi, u zzat i tiṭṭawin n řechud nni tuɣa iweqqɛen tabrat ittwannḍen n tmesɣiwt zzat i tiṭṭawin n marra Wudayen nni iqqimen di řemraḥ n řeḥbes.  
\v 13 Necc umureɣ Barux zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, nniɣ:  
\v 14 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ksi tibratin-a, tabrat ittwannḍen n tmesɣiwt, am tenni icemmɛen am tanita, tenni yarezmen, uca ssars i-tent deg ict n řqecɛet n třaxt, maḥend ad qqiment aṭṭas n wussan ḥḍant!’  
\v 15 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ad ttwasɣen ɛawed tudrin d iyyaren d imarjaɛen n uḍiř di temmurt-a.’”   
\m
\v 16 Awarni umi tuɣa wciɣ tabrat n tmesɣiwt i Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, ẓẓuǧeɣ s řaǧaɣ ɣar SIDI, nniɣ:  
\v 17 “Ax, Sidi inu, SIDI, xzar, Cek teggid ijenwan d tammurt s jjhed nnec ameqqran u s uɣiř nnec isswiẓẓḍen. War xak iwɛar walu.  
\v 18 \add Cek\add* d wenni iggin tamexsiwt icewwaren i řuřuf uca txeǧṣed řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten deg weḥsin n iḥenjiren nsen awarni asen, \add a\add* Cek Arebbi d ameqqran d ajebbar, wenni umi qqaren: SIDI n řɛeskarat. \x ◘ \xo 32:18 \xt Uf. 34:7\x*  
\v 19 Cek d ameqqran n ccwar u tejhed di tmegga, maɣar tiṭṭawin nnec ttɛessent x marra ibriden n tarwa n bnadem, ḥima ad txeǧṣeḍ kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab ibriden nnes u ɛlaḥsab řɣiǧet n tmegga nnes.\x ◘ \xo 32:19 \xt Ayub 34:21; Awřn. 5:21; Ica. 28:29; Irm. 16:17; 17:10\x*  
\v 20 Cek teggid řeɛřamat d lmujizat di Miṣra, ař ass-a, am deg Israil am deg iwdan nneɣni. Teggid ijj n Yisem i Yixef nnec, am mammec \add i teǧa\add* ass-a.  
\v 21 Cek tessuffɣed-dd řgens nnec Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra s řeɛřamat d lmuɛjizat, s ijj n ufus ijehden d ijj n uɣiř isswiẓẓaḍen, \add umi tessekkared\add* ict n teggʷudi tameqqrant \add jar řegnus\add*.\x ◘ \xo 32:21 \xt Uf. 6:7; 2 Ṣm. 7:23; 1 Im. 17:21\x*  
\v 22 Cek tewcid asen tammurt-a, tenni tejjuǧed i řejdud nsen maḥend ad asen tt tewced, ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment.  
\v 23 Nitni udfen-dd ɣares uca ṭṭfen tt d tasɣart, \add maca\add* nitni war sřin i tmijja nnec u war uyuren deg \add webrid n\add* Ccariɛa nnec u war ggin ɛlaḥṣab marra minzi ten tweṣṣid. \add S uya\add* i ten iřqef marra řɣar-a.  
\v 24 Xzar, icbaren i řeḥṣaret! Nitni iwḍen-dd ař tandint maḥend ad tt ṭṭfen, uca tandint temmewc deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen nni akides ittmenɣan, zi ssibbet n ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun. Min tessiwřed aqa yiweḍ-dd. Xzar, tᵉttwarid \add t\add* simant nnec.  
\v 25 \add Waxxa amenni\add* tennid ayi, \add a\add* Sidi inu, SIDI: Seɣ i yixef nnec iyyar nni s nnuqart uca ejj řechud ad tt ssmetnen, \add řami\add* temmewc tendint deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen.”   
\m
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 27 “Xzar, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI n marra nni ɣarsen arrimet \add n weysum\add*. Ma iwɛar xafi ca?’ \x ◘ \xo 32:27 \xt Řxř. 16:22\x*  
\v 28 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Necc ad ggeɣ tandint-a deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen u deg ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, u netta ad tt iṭṭef.  
\v 29 Ikaldaniyyen, inni ittmenɣan ak-d tendint-a, ad ɣares dd-adfen, ad qedden tandint s tmessi uca ad tt sscemḍen ak-d tudrin nni x tzeɣwin nsent i zi qeddmen tiwhibin n řebxur i Baɛl uca seyyben tiwhibin n useyyeb i irebbiten nneɣni ḥima ad ayi sɛaren. \x ◘ \xo 32:29 \xt Irm. 21:10\x*  
\v 30 Maɣar ayt n Israil d ayt n Yahuda zi temẓi nsen tteggen mɣir min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin inu. Ayt n Israil sɛaren ayi s řxedmet n ifassen nsen!’, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 31 ‘Maɣar tandint tuɣa tt i Necc \add d ssibbet\add* n weɣḍab d wesɛar zeg wass nni di tᵉttwabna ař ass-a, ařami tt ɣa nḍareɣ x wudem inu  
\v 32 zi ssibbet n marra řɣar n ayt n Israil d ayt n Yahuda maḥend ad ayi sɛaren, nitni d ijeǧiden nsen d řḥukkam nsen d ikehhanen nsen d inabiyyen nsen d iryazen n Yahuda d imezdaɣ n Urcalim.  
\v 33 Nitni wcin ayi-dd s weɛrur, war iǧi s uɣembub, \add waxxa\add* Necc ssřemdeɣ ten, \add ɛad\add* zeg umezwaru ssɣareɣ ten, \add maca\add* nitni war xsen ad sřen maḥend ad ṭṭfen ttarbiyyet. \x ◘ \xo 32:33 \xt Irm. 2:27; 7:13, 24, 25; 25:3; 26:5; 29:19\x*  
\v 34 Nitni ssbedden nnɛawat nsen n l’aṣnam di Taddart i xef ittwabarreḥ Isem inu maḥend ad tt ssxemjen.  
\v 35 Nitni ssbedden řegɛudi n Baɛl \add mani i d as ttwehhben ddbayeḥ nsen\add* di teɣzurt n mmis n Hinnum maḥend ad sseɛdun iḥenjiren nsen d tḥenjirin nsent i Mulak di tmessi, min war d asen umureɣ ɛemmarṣ u min war d ayi dd-iddaren di řbař inu, aqa ad ggen nnɛi am wa ařami ɛarnen Yahuda ɣar ddnub.’” \x ◘ \xo 32:35 \xt Irm. 19:5\x*   
\m
\v 36 “S uya, řexxu, ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x tendint-a i x teqqarem: ‘Aqa temmewc deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil, s ssif, s řaẓ u s ṭṭaɛun!’:  
\v 37 Xzar, Necc ad ten ssmuneɣ zi marra timmura mani xasen uẓẓřeɣ deg weɣḍab inu u deg wesɛar inu u deg uduqqez n weɣḍab inu, u Necc ad ten arreɣ ɣar wemcan-a u ad ten sszedɣeɣ di řaman. \x ◘ \xo 32:37 \xt Irm. 23:3; 29:14; 31:10\x*  
\v 38 Nitni ad iřin d řgens inu u Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nsen. \x ◘ \xo 32:38 \xt Irm. 24:7; 30:22; 31:1,33\x*  
\v 39 Necc ad asen wceɣ uř d ijj uřa d webrid d ijj ḥima ad ayi ggʷeden marra ussan i tizi nsen u i tizi n iḥenjiren nsen awarni asen.  
\v 40 Necc akidsen ggeɣ ijj n Řɛahd ittduman, aqa war ttḥeyyideɣ zi awarni asen, ḥima ad asen ggeɣ min iṣebḥen, u Necc ad asen ssarseɣ tiggʷudi zzayi deg wuř nsen, maḥend war xafi ttḥeyyiden \add ɛad\add*.  
\v 41 Necc ad zzaysen farḥeɣ maḥend ad daysen tthilliɣ u zi řmanet inu ad ten ẓẓuɣ di temmurt-a s marra uř inu u s marra řeɛmar inu.’” \x ◘ \xo 32:41 \xt Irm. 24:6; Ɛam. 9:15\x*   
\m
\v 42 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Am mammec i dd iwyeɣ x řgens-a tuɛeffna-ya tameqqrant, ammu i xasen i ɣa ssiwḍeɣ marra taṣebḥant i xasen nniɣ.  
\v 43 Ad sɣen \add ɛawed\add* iyyaren di temmurt-a i xef teqqarem kenniw: ‘Aqa-tt d ict temmurt ittwareddǧen nhřa bnadem d řmar, temmewc deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen.’  
\v 44 Ad sɣen \add ɛawed\add* iyyaren s \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart, ad weqqɛen u ad cemmɛen tibratin n tmesɣiwt, ad awyen řechud ḥima ad ssmetnen \add tamesɣiwt\add* di temmurt n Binyamin, di jjwayeh n Urcalim, di tneddam n Yahuda, di tneddam n Temmurt n Idurar, di tneddam n Temmurt Iwaṭan u di tneddam n \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub, maɣar Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast nsen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 33
\s1 Lwaɛd n ureqqeɛ  
\m
\v 1 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya i twařa wiss tnayen, umi tuɣa ɛad ittwabelleɛ xas di řemraḥ n řeḥbes, inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, wenni t iggin, SIDI, wenni tt yarecmen ařami tt ɣa ibedd d ubeddi, aqa SIDI d Isem nnes:  
\v 3 ‘Řaɣa ayi-dd uca ad xak dd-arreɣ u ad ac ssecneɣ timesřayin timeqqranin d innufaren, war tent tessined.  
\v 4 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x tudrin n tendint-a u x tudrin n ijeǧiden n Yahuda nni ittwahedmen, \add maḥend ad iřint i udurri\add* ḍidd n wecbaren n řeḥṣaret u ḍidd n ssif:  
\v 5 Inni dd-yusin ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d Ikaldaniyyen, \add aqa usin-dd\add* ḥima ad ɛemmaren \add tudrin nni\add* s řxecbat n iwdan nni nɣiɣ deg weɣḍab inu u deg wesɛar inu, minzi ssdurryeɣ udem inu x tendint-a zi ssibbet n marra tuɛeffna nsen!  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* xzar, Necc ad as-tt-i-dd-awyeɣ aɛdař d ugenfu, Necc ad ten ssgenfiɣ uca ad xasen ɛarriɣ ijj \add n řɛunṣar\add* ifeyyḍen s řehna d tidett.  
\v 7 Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n Yahuda d tmeḥbast n Israil, u ad ten bniɣ am deg umezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 33:7 \xt Irm. 24:6; 31:4; 32:44\x*  
\v 8 Necc ad ten ssizedgeɣ zi marra řmuɛṣiyyet nsen i zi kidi xḍan. Ad ɣfareɣ marra řmuɛṣiyyat nsen i zi xḍan akidi uca ɛeddan xafi. \x ◘ \xo 33:8 \xt Irm. 31:34\x*  
\v 9 Ad tiři \add tendint n Urcalim\add* i Necc d isem issefraḥen d usemɣar d ccan ɣar marra řegnus n ddunect nni i ɣa isřan řxar nni d asen i ɣa ggeɣ. Nitni ad ggʷeden u ad arjijen x marra řxar u x marra řehna nni d as i ɣa ggeɣ.’”   
\m
\v 10 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Deg wemcan-a i x teqqarem kenniw: ‘Aqa-t d řxirbet ařami war iqqim uřa d ijj n bnadem niɣ d řmař!’, \add wah,\add* di tneddam n Yahuda u deg ibriden n Urcalim, tinni ittwareddǧen ařami war iqqim uřa d ijj n bnadem niɣ d amezduɣ niɣ d řmař, ad ittwaseř \add ɛad\add*  
\v 11 tmijja n warcaq d tmijja n řefraḥet, tmijja n muřay d tmijja n tesřit, tmijja n yinni iqqaren: Qadam SIDI n řɛeskarat, maɣar SIDI iṣbeḥ, maɣar tamexsiwt nnes icewwaren tᵉttɣima i řebda!, tmijja n yinni i dd-ittawyen aqadi di Taddart n SIDI, maɣar Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n temmurt, \add ad tiři\add* am deg umezwaru, iqqar SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 33:11 \xt Irm. 7:34; Izhd. 136:6\x*   
\m
\v 12 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Deg wemcan-a i ittwareddǧen ařami war iqqim \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj n bnadem niɣ d řmař, \add wah,\add* di marra tineddam nnes ad iřint ɛawed ddmani n tarewsa i imeksawen nni i ɣa issareyyḥen uǧi. \f ◼ \fr 33:12 \ft \+fk imeksawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iničan’.\f*  
\v 13 Di Temmurt n Idurar, di tneddam n Temmurt Iwaṭan, di tneddam n Temmurt n Ljanub, di temmurt n Binyamin, deg imucan i d as dd-innḍen i Urcalim u di tneddam n Yahuda ad ɛdun wuǧi ɛawed sadu ifassen n yinni i ten iḥessben!’, \add ammu\add* i iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 14 “Xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad ssqefřeɣ awař aṣebḥan nni ssiwřeɣ i taddart n Israil d taddart n Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 33:14 \xt Irm. 29:10\x*  
\v 15 Deg wussan nni u di řweqt nni ad ssɣemyeɣ i Dawud AƔEDDU n tsegda. Netta ad yegg řḥeqq d tsegda di temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 33:15 \xt Irm. 23:5\x*  
\v 16 Deg wussan nni ad ittwassenjem Yahuda uca Urcalim ad tezdeɣ di řaman, ad as ggen \add i Urcalim\add* isem wanita: ‘SIDI d Tasegda nneɣ.’”   
\m
\v 17 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ɛemmarṣ ad inqeṣ i Dawud ijj n weryaz nni iqqimen x řɛarc n taddart n Israil,  
\v 18 uca uřa d ikehhanen Ilawiyyen war d asen ineqqeṣ ɛemmarṣ ijj n weryaz nni i ɣa iqeddmen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zzat i wudem inu niɣ ad issbexxar tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* niɣ ad issewjed ict n tɣarṣt, marra ussan.’” \x ◘ \xo 33:18 \xt Irm. 17:26\x*   
\m
\v 19 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 20 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Mařa izemmar ad tarẓmem řɛahd inu s wass d řɛahd inu s ǧiřet ař ass d ǧiřet war ttiřin ɛad di řweqt nsen ittwaggen,  
\v 21 \add xenni\add* iři ad ittwarẓ uřa d Řɛahd inu ak-d umsexxar inu Dawud, ařami war ɣares ittiři ɛad mmis nni i ɣa iḥekmen x řɛarc nnes, u ak-d ikehhanen zeg ayt n Lawi, imsexxaren inu.  
\v 22 Am mammec war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb řɛeskar n ujenna u uřa d ijdi n řebḥar war izemmar ad ittwaɛbar, ammu s waṭṭas i ɣa ggeɣ tarwa n umsexxar inu Dawud u \add n\add* Ilawiyyen nni d ayi ittsexxaren.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 24 “Ma war teẓrid mammec issawař řgens-a, qqaren: ‘Tnayen n řaǧat nni ifarz SIDI, aqa inḍar i-tent’? Aqa nitni stehzan zi řgens inu ařami war iǧi ɛad d řgens i nitni.”   
\m
\v 25 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Mařa Řɛahd inu s wass d ǧiřet war ittiři \add ɛad\add*, war ttɣimiɣ tteggeɣ lfarayiḍ n ijenwan d temmurt,  
\v 26 ad nḍareɣ uřa d tarwa n Yaɛqub d \add tarwa\add* n Dawud ařami war tteggeɣ \add ɛad\add* zi zzariɛet nnes inni ɣa iḥekmen x tarwa n Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Yaɛqub, maɣar Necc ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast nsen u Necc ad xasen ḥinneɣ.’” \x ◘ \xo 33:26 \xt Irm. 31:20\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 34
\s1 Aɛřam ɣar Ṣidqiya  
\m
\v 1 Awař i dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya - umi Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, d marra řɛeskar nnes d marra tigeldiwin n ddunect i iǧan sadu fus nnes d marra řegnus tuɣa ttmenɣan ak-d Urcalim u ak-d marra tineddam nnes - i innan: \x ◘ \xo 34:1 \xt 2 Ij. 25; Irm. 52 \x*   
\m
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Uyur uca siweř ak-d Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ini as: Ammu i iqqar SIDI, xzar, Necc ad wceɣ tandint-a deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil u netta ad as iqqed timessi. \x ◘ \xo 34:2 \xt Irm. 21:10; 32:29\x*  
\v 3 Uřa d cek s yixef nnec war tnejjmed i ufus nnes, maca ad cek ṭṭfen u ad cek wcen deg ufus nnes. Tiṭṭ di tiṭṭ ad tẓared ajeǧid n Babil uca ad kides tessiwřed zeg uqemmum ɣar uqemmum uca ad dd-tawḍed ař Babil. \x ◘ \xo 34:3 \xt Irm. 32:4\x*  
\v 4 Seř maca i wawař n SIDI, Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Ammu i xak iqqar SIDI: ‘Cek war tᵉttwanɣed ca s ssif.  
\v 5 Ad temmted di řehna uca am mammec ssarɣen timessiyat i řejdud nnec, ijeǧiden n zic nni tuɣa iǧan qbeř i cek, ad ssarɣen ɛawed d timessiyat i cek uca ad xak wten agejdur, ad inin: Ax, sidi!’, maɣar Necc ssiwřeɣ awař\add -a\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 6 Issiweř unabi Irmiya marra awařen-a i Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, di Urcalim,  
\v 7 \add umi\add* tuɣa řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Babil ittmenɣa ak-d Urcalim u ak-d marra tineddam n Yahuda nni iqqimen, ak-d Laxic d Ɛaziqa, maɣar tina tuɣa ɛad qqiment jar tneddam n Yahuda, minzi tuɣa atent d tineddam ifaryen.   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Awař nni dd-iffɣen zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya, awarni ma iqqen ujeǧid Ṣidqiya ijj n řɛahd ak-d marra řgens nni iǧan di Urcalim, maḥend ad barrḥen s ijj n usarreḥ jar asen, \x ◘ \xo 34:8 \xt Uf. 21:2\x*  
\v 9 maḥend kuř ijjen ad yarxu i ismeɣ nnes u i tayya nnes, i Uɛibrani u i Tɛibranect, ařami war ittɣimi jar asen uřa d ijjen \add wenni iǧan\add* d ismeɣ ɣar ijj n weryaz zi Yahuda, ɣar umas.  
\v 10 Marra řḥukkam d marra řgens nni iqqnen řɛahd, sřin aqa \add kuř\add* aryaz ad yarxu i ismeɣ nnes u \add kuř\add* aryaz ad yarxu i tayya nnes ḥima war ittɣimi ɣarsen uřa d ijj n ismeɣ. Nitni wcin amezzuɣ \add i man aya\add* uca ssekken ten.  
\v 11 \add Maca awarni as\add* beddřen, arrin-dd isemɣan d tiyya inni umi tuɣa arxun, ḥṣaren ten ɛawed maḥend ad iřin \add ɛawed\add* d imsemɣan d tiyya.   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 13 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc ggiɣ ijj n Řɛahd ak-d řejdud nwem deg wass nni di ten dd-ssuffɣeɣ zi Miṣra, zi taddart n tesmuɣi, nniɣ:  
\v 14 Awarni řami ɛdun sebɛa n iseggʷusa ittxeṣṣa kuř ijj ad issekk umas Aɛibrani nni d ac izzenzen ixef nnes uca tuɣa ixeddem i cek setta n iseggʷusa. Ittxeṣṣa ad as tarxud \add ad yuyur\add* di třelli! \add Maca\add* řejdud nwem war ɣari dd-sřin u war \add d ayi\add* wcin ca amezzuɣ. \x ◘ \xo 34:14 \xt Uf. 21:2; Aɛwd. 15:12\x*  
\v 15 Waxxa kenniw tdewřem-dd, teggim min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin inu am ibarreḥ kuř ijj s usarxu i jjar nnes uca teggim ijj n řɛahd zzat i wudem inu di Taddart min xef ittwabarreḥ Isem inu,  
\v 16 kenniw \add maca\add* tennqeřbem ɛawed uca tessɛiǧtem Isem inu. Kuř ijj yarra-dd ismeɣ nnes u kuř ijj yarra-dd tayya nnes nni umi tuɣa tarxum maḥend ad uyuren nitni mani xsen, uca kenniw teḥṣarem ten ɛawed maḥend ad awem iřin d imsemɣan d tiyya.’”   
\m
\v 17 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Kenniw war ɣari tesřim maḥend kuř ijj ad ibarreḥ s usarxu i umas u kuř ijj i jjar nnes. Xzar, ammu Necc ad awem barrḥeɣ s usarxu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, \add maḥend ad kenniw sellmeɣ\add* i ssif, i ṭṭaɛun u i řaẓ. Necc ad kenniw ggeɣ d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ i marra tigeldiwin n ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 34:17 \xt Aɛwd. 28:25; Irm. 15:4; 24:9, 10\x*  
\v 18 Necc ad arreɣ iryazen nni iɛdun x řɛahd inu, inni war iṭṭifen deg wawařen n řɛahd nni ggin zzat i wudem inu, \add am\add* uɛejmi nni bḍan x tnayen d wenni jar izeynat nnes cuqen nitni: \x ◘ \xo 34:18 \xt Amz. 15:10\x*  
\v 19 řḥukkam n Yahuda d řḥukkam n Urcalim, imsexxaren icennɛen, ikehhanen d marra řgens n temmurt, inni icuqen \add marra\add* jar iziynat n uɛejmi.  
\v 20 Necc ad ten wceɣ deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen u deg ufus n yinni yarezzun ad ten nɣen uca řxecbat nsen ad iřint d macca i ijḍaḍ n ujenna u i řmař n temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 34:20 \ft \+fk inni yarezzun ad ten nɣen\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘inni yarezzun řeɛmar nsen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 34:20 \xt Irm. 7:33; 16:4; 19:7\x*  
\v 21 Uřa d Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d řḥukkam nnes ad ten ggeɣ deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen, deg ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nsen, deg ufus n řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Babil nni xawem iffɣen \add řexxu\add*. \x ◘ \xo 34:21 \xt Irm. 37:11\x*  
\v 22 Xzar, Necc ad umureɣ, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, u Necc ad ten dd-arreɣ ɣar tendint-a u nitni ad kides mmenɣen, ad tt ṭṭfen uca ad as qqden timessi. Necc ad arreɣ tineddam n Yahuda d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen, war dayes ittɣimi uřa d ijj n umezduɣ \add ɛad\add*.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 35
\s1 Ayt n Rikab  
\m
\v 1 Awař n SIDI i dd-yusin ɣar Irmiya deg wussan n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna:  
\v 2 “Uyur ɣar taddart n ayt n Rikab uca siweř akidsen u awyi ten ɣar Taddart n SIDI, deg ijj zeg ixxamen \add nnes\add*, u ewc asen binu ḥima ad swen.”   
\m
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iwyeɣ-dd Yazanya\add hu\add*, mmis n Irmiya, mmis n Ḥabṣiniya, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra aytmas d marra iḥenjiren nnes d marra taddart n ayt n Rikab.  
\v 4 Iwyeɣ ten ɣar Taddart n SIDI, deg wexxam n ayt n Ḥanan, mmis n Yajdalya, aryaz n AREBBI, \add axxam\add* nni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wexxam n řḥukkam, tiwa i wexxam n Maɛasiya, mmis n Callum, aɛessas n tewwart.  
\v 5 Necc ssarseɣ iɣarrafen ccuren s binu d řkisan zzat i wudem n ayt n Rikab uca nniɣ asen: ‘Swem binu!’  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* nitni nnan: ‘Neccin war nsess ca binu, maɣar babatneɣ Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, iweṣṣa aneɣ, inna: Kenniw ɛemmarṣ war ttsessem binu, kenniw d iḥenjiren nwem, ař i řebda.  
\v 7 War iɛeddeř ad tebnam taddart niɣ ad tzarɛem zzariɛet niɣ ad teẓẓum tazayart deg umarjeɛ niɣ ad ɣarwem yiři umarjeɛ n uḍiř, \add maca\add* min ɣa tekkem teddarem ad tzedɣem deg iqiḍan, maḥend ad teddarem ussan aṭṭas di temmurt mani i ɣa tzedɣem am yibarraniyyen.  
\v 8 Neccin nesřa ɣar babatneɣ Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, di marra min zi i d aneɣ iweṣṣa, maḥend war nsess binu marra tudart nneɣ, neccin d temɣarin nneɣ d iḥenjiren nneɣ d yessitneɣ, \f ◼ \fr 35:8 \ft \+fk marra tudart nneɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘marra ussan nneɣ’.\f*  
\v 9 u maḥend war nbenni tudrin d tazeddiɣt i yixef nneɣ. War ɣarneɣ bu umarjeɛ n uḍiř niɣ iyyar niɣ zzariɛet,  
\v 10 uca neccin tuɣa nzeddeɣ deg iqiḍan. \add Ammu\add* i nesřa u negga ɛlaḥṣab marra min zi i d aneɣ iweṣṣa babatneɣ Yunadab.  
\v 11 Umi \add maca\add* Nabuxadnaṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, igeɛɛed x temmurt-a, imsar, aqa nenna: Asem-dd, ad nraḥ ɣar Urcalim zi ssibbet n řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen u zi ssibbet n řɛeskar n Aram! \add S uyenni i\add* nzeddeɣ di Urcalim.’”   
\m
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 13 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Uyur, ini i yeryazen n Yahuda u i imezdaɣ n Urcalim: ‘Ma war tᵉttexsem ad teksim ttarbiyyet s utesři i wawařen inu?’, iqqar SIDI.  
\v 14 Awařen n Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, inni yumur i iḥenjiren nsen ḥima war sessen binu, aqa ḍfaren ten-dd, maɣar ař ass-a war swin ca, minzi nitni sřin ɣar tewṣeyyet n babatsen, \add maca\add* Necc ssiwřeɣ akidwem, \add wah ɛad\add* zeg umezwaru ssiwřeɣ akidwem, \add maca\add* kenniw war ɣari dd-tesřim ca. \x ◘ \xo 35:14 \xt Irm. 11:7; 25:3; 26:5; 29:19; 32:33\x*  
\v 15 Necc ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarwem marra imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen. Ɛad zic sekkeɣ ten ḥima ad inin: Dewřem-dd xenni, kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan u ggem řexdayem tiṣebḥanin u war traddafem irebbiten nneɣni maḥend ad asen tsexxarem, xenni tzemmarem ad teqqimem \add tzedɣem\add* di temmurt i d awem wciɣ u i řejdud nwem. Kenniw maca war tewcim amezzuɣ u war ɣari tesřim. \x ◘ \xo 35:15 \xt Irm. 18:11; 25:5\x*  
\v 16 Iḥenjiren n Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, ssqefřen tawṣeyyet n babatsen nni ten yumur, \add maca\add* řgens-a war ɣari isři ca.”   
\m
\v 17 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad awyeɣ x Yahuda u x marra imezdaɣ n Urcalim marra řɣar nni d asen nniɣ, minzi ssiwřeɣ akidsen maca nitni war sřin ca, uca řaɣiɣ asen maca nitni war dd-arrin ca.”   
\m
\v 18 Inna Irmiya i taddart n ayt n Rikab: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Umi tesřim ɣar tewṣeyyet n babatwem Yunadab uca teḥḍam marra tiweṣṣa nnes u teggim ɛlaḥsab marra min d awem yumur,  
\v 19 x uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Marra ussan war ittxeṣṣi ɛemmarṣ i Yunadab, mmis n Rikab, ijj n weryaz nni ittbeddan zzat i wudem inu!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 36
\s1 Adlis ittwannḍen  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, imsar aqa yusa-dd wawař n SIDI wanita ɣar Irmiya, inna:  
\v 2 “Ksi ijj n wedlis ittwanḍen uca ari xas marra awařen i ɣarek ssiwřeɣ x Israil u x Yahuda u x marra řegnus, zeg wass i dd ɣarek ssiwřeɣ, zeg wussan n Yuciya ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 36:2 \xt 2 Im. 35:25; Ica. 8:1; Irm. 30:2\x*  
\v 3 Ad taɣ ad sřen inni n taddart n Yahuda x marra řɣar nni xseɣ ad asen ggeɣ maḥend ad dd-dewřen ad tuben, kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan, u Necc ad asen ɣfareɣ řmuɛṣiyyet nsen d ddnub nsen.”   
\m
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa-dd Irmiya x Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, uca yura Barux zeg uqemmum n Irmiya marra awařen n SIDI nni d as inna deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen.  
\v 5 Yumur Irmiya i Barux, inna: “Necc ttwassbeddeɣ, war zemmareɣ ad dd-adfeɣ ɣar Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 6 Adef-dd cek ɣar daxeř uca ɣar awařen n SIDI zeg wedlis ittwanḍen nni turid zeg uqemmum inu deg imezzuɣen n řgens di Taddart n SIDI deg wass n uẓummi. Ittxeṣṣa ad ten tɣared deg imezzuɣen n marra \add ayt n\add* Yahuda, inni dd-yusin zi marra tineddam nsen.  
\v 7 Ad taɣ ad yaf tutra nsen arḍa zzat i wudem n SIDI u ad dd-dewřen ad tuben nitni, kuř ijj zeg webrid nnes aɛeffan, maɣar d ameqqran i yeǧa weɣḍab d wesɛar i x tuɣa issiweř SIDI i řgens-a.”   
\m
\v 8 Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, igga marra am mammec t yumur unabi Irmiya, uca iɣra-dd awařen n SIDI \add i řgens\add* zeg wedlis \add ittwannḍen\add* di Taddart n SIDI.  
\v 9 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg uyur wiss tesɛa barrḥen s ijj n uẓummi zzat i wudem n SIDI i marra řgens di Urcalim u i marra řgens nni dd-yusin di Urcalim zi tneddam n Yahuda.  
\v 10 Iɣra-dd Barux awařen n Irmiya di Taddart n SIDI x imezzuɣen n marra řgens zeg wedlis \add ittwannḍen\add*, deg wexxam n Jamarya, mmis n Cafan, amarir, di řemraḥ n sennej, ɣar wadaf n tewwart n jdid n Taddart n SIDI.   
\m
\v 11 \add Umi\add* Mixa-Yahu, mmis n Jamarya, mmis n Cafan, isřa i marra awařen n SIDI zeg wedlis \add ittwannḍen\add*,  
\v 12 ihwa-dd netta ɣar taddart n ujeǧid, ɣar wexxam n umarir. Xzar, qqimen din marra řḥukkam: Alicamaɛ, amarir, Dalaya, mmis n Camɛiya, Il-Natan, mmis n Ɛakbur, Jamarya, mmis n Cafan, Ṣidqiya, mmis n Ḥananya, u marra řḥukkam.  
\v 13 Mixa-Yahu iɛawed asen marra awařen nni tuɣa isřa umi dd-iɣra Barux zeg wedlis \add ittwanḍen\add* deg imezzuɣen n řgens.  
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ssekken-dd marra řḥukkam Yahudi, mmis n Natanya, mmis n Calamya, mmis n Kuci, ɣar Barux, nnan: “Adlis ittwanḍen manis dd-teɣrid x řgens, ksi t deg ufus nnec uca as-dd!” \add Řexdenni\add* iksi Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, adlis ittwannḍen nni uca yudef-dd ɣarsen.  
\v 15 Nitni nnan as: “Qqim, tɣared adlis ittwannḍen xaneɣ!” \add Xenni\add* iɣra t Barux xasen.   
\m
\v 16 Umi sřin nitni marra awařen \add nni\add*, xzaren deg wayawya ggʷeden uca nnan i Barux: “Nican ad nɛawed marra awařen-a i ujeǧid.”  
\v 17 Nitni sseqsan Barux, nnan: “Ini aneɣ maca, mammec turid marra awařen-a zeg uqemmum nnes?”  
\v 18 Yarra-dd xasen Barux: “S uqemmum nnes i xafi iɣra marra awařen-a u necc uriɣ ten s ssmex deg wedlis\add -a\add* \add ittwannḍen\add*.”  
\v 19 \add Xas uca\add* nnan řḥukkam i Barux: “Uyur, ffar ixef nnec, cek uřa d Irmiya! Uřa d ijj war ittessen mani teǧam.”  
\v 20 Udfen nitni ɣar ujeǧid di řemraḥ, \add maca\add* nitni tuɣa xemmřen adlis ittwannḍen deg wexxam n Ilicamaɛ, amarir, u nitni ḥajan marra awařen-a ɣar imezzuɣen n ujeǧid.   
\m
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* issekk ujeǧid Yahudi maḥend ad dd-yawi adlis ittwannḍen. Wanita yiwi t i-dd zeg wexxam n Alicamaɛ, amarir, uca iɣra i-t-i-dd Yahudi deg imejjan n ujeǧid u deg imejjan n marra řḥukkam nni dd-ibedden ɣar ujeǧid.  
\v 22 Tuɣa iqqim ujeǧid di taddart n tagarst, tuɣa d ayur wiss tesɛa. Zzates tareqq \add dinni\add* tmessi x tmejmart.  
\v 23 Řami iɣra Yahudi třata niɣ arebɛa n iḍewḍan, iqess i-ten ujeǧid s řmuss n umarir uca inḍar i-ten di tmessi x řmejmar, ařami tuɣa timessi x řmejmar tecca marra adlis.  
\v 24 Ajeǧid d marra imsexxaren nnes inni isřin i wawařen-a marra, war nnxeřɛen u war carrgen arruḍ nsen.  
\v 25 Ttaren Il-Natan d Dalaya d Jamarya i ujeǧid aṭṭas ḥima war issecmiḍ \add adlis\add* ittwannḍen, \add maca\add* netta war ɣarsen isři.  
\v 26 \add Ɛad\add* yumur ujeǧid i Yarḥamiyil, mmis n ujeǧid, i Saraya, mmis n Ɛazrayil, u i Calamya, mmis n Ɛabdiyil, ḥima ad ṭṭfen amarir Barux d unabi Irmiya d imeḥbas. \add Maca\add* SIDI issnuffar i-ten.   
\m
\v 27 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya, awarni řami issecmeḍ ujeǧid adlis ittwannḍen d wawařen nni yura Barux, \add inni dd-iffɣen\add* zeg uqemmum n Irmiya, inna:  
\v 28 “Ksi ɛawed ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen nneɣni u ari xas marra awařen imezwura, inni tuɣa deg wedlis amezwaru i issecmeḍ Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda,  
\v 29 uca ini i Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Cek tesscemḍed adlis-a ittwannḍen, tennid: Mayemmi dayes turid, tennid: Ajeǧid n Babil ad dd-yas, ad ixarreb tammurt uca ad zzayes imḥa bnadem d řmař?’  
\v 30 ‘S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI x Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda: War ɣares ittiři wenni i ɣa iqqimen x řɛarc n Dawud uca řxecbet nnes ad temmenḍar i řeḥmu n uziř u i tesmeḍ n ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 36:30 \xt Irm. 22:19\x*  
\v 31 Necc ad zzayes xeřfeɣ řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, uřa zi tarwa nnes uřa zeg imsexxaren nnes. Necc ad ssɣeḍřeɣ xasen, x imezdaɣ n Urcalim u x iryazen n Yahuda, marra řɣar i d asen nniɣ, \add waxxa\add* nitni war xsen ad sřen.’” \f ◼ \fr 36:31 \ft \+fk tarwa nnes\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet nnes’.\f*   
\m
\v 32 Iksi Irmiya ijj n wedlis nneɣni ittwannḍen uca iwca i-t i umarir Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah. Wanita yura xas, zeg uqemmum n Irmiya, marra awařen n wedlis \add ittwannḍen\add* nni tuɣa Yahuyaqim, ajeǧid n Yahuda, issecmeḍ s tmessi uca ttwarnin ɛad ɣarsen waṭṭas n wawařen nneɣni i ten yudsen.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 37
\s1 Ajeǧid Ṣidqiya issekk ɣar Irmiya i twařa wiss tnayen  
\m
\v 1 Idweř Ṣidqiya, mmis n Yuciya, d ajeǧid deg wemcan n Kun-Yahu, mmis n Yahuyaqim, wenni tuɣa igga Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, d ajeǧid x temmurt n Yahuda.  
\v 2 Wanita war isři ca ɣar wawařen n SIDI nni issiweř Netta s ufus n unabi Irmiya, war iǧi wanita uřa d imsexxaren nnes uřa d řgens n temmurt.  
\v 3 \add Waxxa amenni\add* issekk ujeǧid Ṣidqiya Yahuxal, mmis n Calamya, d Ṣafanya, mmis n Maɛasiya, ɣar unabi Irmiya maḥend ad as inin: “Ẓaǧ xaneɣ ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ!” \f ◼ \fr 37:3 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*   
\m
\v 4 Irmiya tuɣa ɛad izemmar ad yadef u ad iffeɣ di řwesṭ n řgens u nitni tuɣa ɛad war t nḍaren di řḥebs.  
\v 5 Iffeɣ-dd řɛeskar n firɛun zi Miṣra uca umi sřin Ikaldaniyyen nni tuɣa iḥeṣṣaren Urcalim x man aya, aggʷejen x Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 37:5 \xt Irm. 34:21\x*   
\m
\v 6 Xenni yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar unabi Irmiya, inna:  
\v 7 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Ammu i ɣa tinim i ujeǧid n Yahuda, wenni kenniw ɣari dd-issekken ḥima ad ayi tesseqsam: Xzar, řɛeskar n firɛun nni dd-iffɣen maḥend ad awem iwc afus, ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar temmurt nnes, ɣar Miṣra!  
\v 8 Ad dd-dewřen Ikaldaniyyen, ad mmenɣen ak-d tendint-a uca ad tt ṭṭfen, ad as qqden timessi.’  
\v 9 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘War cemmtem ixef nwem xmi ɣa tinim: Ikaldaniyyen ad xaneɣ aggʷejen, ad uyuren!, minzi nitni war gguren.  
\v 10 Ɛad mařa kenniw tɣeřbem marra řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen inni akidwem ittmenɣan, uca ad zzaysen qqimen mɣir iryazen iyezmen aṭṭas, aqa nitni ad kkaren, kuř ijj deg uqiḍun nnes, uca ad qqden timessi i tendint-a.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Irmiya ittwaḥebbes  
\m
\v 11 Imsar umi dd-issgeɛɛed řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen zi Urcalim zi ssibbet n řɛeskar n firɛun,  
\v 12 iffeɣ Irmiya zi Urcalim maḥend ad iraḥ ɣar temmurt n Binyamin ḥima ad dinni iṭṭef ict n tesɣart di řwesṭ n řgens nnes.  
\v 13 \add Řami t tuɣa\add* di tewwart n Binyamin, tuɣa din akumandar n tɛessast, qqaren as Yariyya, mmis n Calamya, mmis n Ḥananya. Netta iṭṭef anabi Irmiya, inna: “Cek texsed ad tarewřed ɣar Ikaldaniyyen!”  
\v 14 Yarra-dd \add xas\add* Irmiya: “Man aya mɣir d axarriq! Necc war xseɣ ca ad arewřeɣ ɣar Ikaldaniyyen!” \add Maca\add* netta war ɣares isři ca uca iṭṭef Yariyya Irmiya uca yiwyi t ɣar řḥukkam \add n řgens\add*.  
\v 15 Ffugmen řḥukkam aṭṭas x Irmiya, wtin t uca ggin t di řeḥbes, di taddart n umarir Yunatan, maɣar tanita tuɣa arrin tt d taddart n tɛessast.  
\v 16 Ammu dd-iwḍa Irmiya deg weḥfur n imeḥbas u deg ixxamen n řeḥbes. Dinni iqqim Irmiya aṭṭas n wussan.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řhard n Ṣidqiya ak-d Irmiya i twařa tamezwarut  
\m
\v 17 Issekk ujeǧid Ṣidqiya ijjen maḥend ad t-i-dd-awyen uca isseqsa t ujeǧid s tnuffra di tzeddiɣt nnes, inna: “Ma aqa din \add zeɛma\add* ca n wawař n SIDI?” Inna \add as\add* Irmiya: “Aqa-t din!” \add Xenni\add* inna: “Cek ad tewḍid deg ufus n ujeǧid n Babil.”  
\v 18 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Irmiya i ujeǧid Ṣidqiya: “Man řɛib i dayek ggiɣ niɣ deg imsexxaren nnec niɣ di řgens-a ařami kenniw d ayi tenḍarem di řeḥbes?  
\v 19 Mani ǧan \add řexxu\add* inabiyyen nwem nni tuɣa ittnabben i kenniw, qqaren: Ajeǧid n Babil war dd-ittis ḍidd nwem u ḍidd i temmurt-a!  
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, seř maca, \add a\add* sidi inu ajeǧid! Iři ad taf tutra inu d arḍa zzat i wudem nnec! War ttejji ad ayi arren ɣar taddart n umarir Yunatan ḥima war dinni ttmettiɣ.”  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* yumur ujeǧid Ṣidqiya ad ḥḍan x Irmiya di řemraḥ n řeḥbes uca wcin as kuř ass ijj n wengur n weɣrum zi Zzenqet n Ixbayziyyen ařami iqḍa weɣrum zi tendint. \add Ammu i\add* iqqim Irmiya di řemraḥ n řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 37:21 \xt Irm. 32:2\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 38
\s1 Irmiya deg wanu  
\m
\v 1 \add Řami\add* Cafaṭya, mmis n Mattan, d Jadalya, mmis n Facḥur, d Yuxal, mmis n Calamya, d Facḥur, mmis n Malkiya, sřin i wawařen nni issiweř Irmiya ɣar marra řgens, umi wanita inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Wenni i ɣa iqqimen di tendint-a, ad ittwaneɣ s ssif, s řaẓ u s ṭṭaɛun, \add maca\add* wenni i ɣa iffɣen ɣar Ikaldaniyyen, ad iqqim iddar. Netta ad yawi akides buḥbeř nnes am tkeccaḍt, ad iqqim iddar!’. \x ◘ \xo 38:2 \xt Irm. 21:9\x*  
\v 3 Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Tandint-a ad temmewc deg ufus n řɛeskar n ujeǧid n Babil u netta ad tt iṭṭef!’”,  
\v 4 \add řexdenni\add* nnan řḥukkam i ujeǧid: “Ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ weryaz-a, minzi ammu i issefcař ifassen n iɛeskariyyen nni \add ɛad\add* iqqimen di tendint-a uřa d ifassen n marra řgens umi ɣarsen issawař awařen-a, maɣar aryaz-a war yarezzu ca řehna i tendint-a, maca yarezzu řɣar.”  
\v 5 Inna ujeǧid Ṣidqiya: “Xzar, netta aqa-t deg ufus nnem, maɣar ajeǧid war izemmar ad awem igg walu.”  
\v 6 Ṭṭfen nitni Irmiya uca nḍaren t deg wanu n mmis n ujeǧid Malkiya, wenni \add iǧan\add* di řemraḥ n řeḥbes. Seyyben Irmiya s iseɣwan swadday. Tuɣa war din bu waman deg wanu, maca mɣir abaryuḍ uca iɣḍes Irmiya deg ubaryuḍ.   
\m
\v 7 \add Umi\add* isřa Ɛabd-Malik, Akuci, ijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ di taddart n ujeǧid, aqa nḍaren Irmiya deg wanu, uca iqqim ujeǧid ɣar tewwart n Binyamin, \f ◼ \fr 38:7 \ft \+fk Akuci\ft  - ijj n weryaz zi temmurt n Kuc nni iǧan d Ssudan d Itiyupiyya n yiḍa.\f*  
\v 8 iffeɣ Ɛabd-Malik zi taddart n ujeǧid uca issiweř ak-d ujeǧid, inna:  
\v 9 “\add A\add* sidi inu ajeǧid, iryazen-a ggin min war iḥřin di marra min ggin i unabi Irmiya, wenni nḍaren nitni deg wanu. Tuɣa izemmar ad dinni immet s řaẓ, maɣar \add ɛad\add* walu aɣrum di tendint.”  
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* yumur ujeǧid Ɛabd-Malik Akuci \add zi temmurt n Kuc\add*, inna: “Ksi ssenni třatin n yeryazen sadu ufus nnec uca sgeɛɛed anabi Irmiya zeg wanu qbeř i ɣa immet.”  
\v 11 Ɛabd-Malik iksi iryazen \add nni\add* sadu ufus nnes uca yudef ɣar taddart n ujeǧid ař wadday n wexxam n txubay. Ssenni iksi ikettanen iqdimen d warruḍ iqqarṣen uca issehwa i-ten-dd s iseɣwan ɣar Irmiya deg wanu.  
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna Ɛabd-Malik Akuci i Irmiya: “Egg ikettanen iqdimen d warruḍ iqqarṣen sadu tiddiɣin n iɣaǧen nnec uca egg iseɣwan swadday!” Uca ammu i tt igga Irmiya.  
\v 13 Jebden-dd nitni Irmiya s iseɣwan uca ssgeɛɛden t-i-dd zeg wanu. \add Maca\add* Irmiya iqqim di řemraḥ n řeḥbes.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řhard n Ṣidqiya ak-d Irmiya i twařa wiss tnayen  
\m
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* issekk ajeǧid Ṣidqiya \add ca n imsexxaren nnes\add*, ijja ad as dd-awyen anabi Irmiya ɣar wadaf wiss třata ɣar Taddart n SIDI. Inna ujeǧid i Irmiya: “Necc xseɣ ad cek sseqsiɣ x ict n řḥajjet, war xafi tt tteffar walu.”  
\v 15 Yarra-dd Irmiya x Ṣidqiya: “Mařa necc ssargbeɣ cek, ma war d ayi tneqqed zeɛma? U mařa wciɣ ac ijj n array, cek war ɣari tᵉttesřid!”  
\v 16 \add Xas uca\add* ijjuǧ ujeǧid Ṣidqiya i Irmiya s tnuffra inna: “S tidett am iddar SIDI wenni d aneɣ iwcin tudart-a: ‘\add Uct xafi\add*, mařa necc nɣiɣ cek niɣ mařa wciɣ cek deg ifassen n yeryazen nni yarezzun tudart nnec!’” \x ◘ \xo 38:16 \xt Ica. 57:16\x*  
\v 17 Inna Irmiya i Ṣidqiya: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Mařa cek ad teffɣed s tidett ɣar řḥukkam n ujeǧid n Babil, ad teqqimed ad teddared, uca tandint-a war tᵉttwassecmaḍ s tmessi, cek ad teqqimed ad teddared, \add wah\add* cek d taddart nnec.  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* mařa war teffiɣed ca ɣar řḥukkam n ujeǧid n Babil, \add xenni\add* ad temmewc tendint-a deg ufus n Ikaldaniyyen. Nitni ad tt sscemḍen s tmessi u cek war tnejjmed zeg ifassen nsen.’”  
\v 19 Ajeǧid Ṣidqiya inna i Irmiya: “Necc tteggʷedeɣ zeg Wudayen nni yeɛdun ɣar Ikaldaniyyen, ařami nitni war d ayi ssɛeddun ɣar ufus nsen u war zzayi tteggen min xsen.”  
\v 20 Inna \add as\add* Irmiya: “Nitni war cek sellmen ca. Seř maca ɣar tmijja n SIDI, ɣar řḥařḍ inu, \add xenni\add* ad tiřid mliḥ u ad teqqimed ad teddared. \f ◼ \fr 38:20 \ft \+fk ad teqqimed ad teddared\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad iddar řeɛmar nnec’.\f*  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* mařa tugid ad teffɣed, \add xenni\add* d wa d awař nni d ayi isscen SIDI:  
\v 22 ‘Xzar, marra timɣarin nni tuɣa iqqimen di taddart n ujeǧid n Yahuda, ad ttwanedhent ɣar řḥukkam n ujeǧid n Babil. Xzar, nitenti ad inint:  
\b  
\m Iryazen nni ak-d tuɣa teddared di řehna,  
\m aqa ɣdaren cek u zemmaren xak,  
\m nnuɣen iḍaren nnec deg ubaryuḍ,  
\m \add uca nitni s yixef nsen\add* dewřen ɣar ḍeffar! \f ◼ \fr 38:22 \ft \+fk Iryazen nni ak-d tuɣa teddared di řehna\ft  - iryazen-a d iryazen icenɛen d inabiyyen nni tuɣa issmuna ujeǧid ɣares.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Marra timɣarin nnec d iḥenjiren nnec ad ttwanedhen ɣar Ikaldaniyyen, uca uřa d cek simant nnec war tnejjmed zeg ufus nsen, minzi ad tᵉttwaṭṭfed zeg ujeǧid n Babil u tandint-a ad tᵉttwassecmeḍ s tmessi.’”   
\m
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* Ṣidqiya inna i Irmiya: “Ittxeṣṣa uřa d ijj war ittessen awařen-a, \add ammu\add* war tmmetid.  
\v 25 Mařa řḥukkam sřin aqa necc ssiwřeɣ akidek, ad ɣarek dd-asen, ad ac inin: ‘Ini aneɣ min tennid i ujeǧid! War xaneɣ teffar \add walu\add*, niɣ aqa ad cek nenneɣ: Min xas kidek issiweř ujeǧid?’  
\v 26 \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad asen tinid: ‘Necc wḍiɣ s řqedd inu zzat i wudem n ujeǧid ḥima war ittejji ad ayi arren ɣar taddart n Yunatan maḥend ad dinni mmteɣ.’”   
\m
\v 27 \add Řami\add* dd-usin marra řḥukkam ɣar Irmiya, iḥaja ten marra awařen-a inni tuɣa yumur ujeǧid. \add Xas uca\add* jjin t maɣar uřa d ijj war isři tamesřact simant nnes.  
\v 28 \add Ammu i\add* iqqim Irmiya di řemraḥ n řeḥbes ař ass nni di tᵉttwaṭṭef Urcalim, \add wah,\add* netta tuɣa-t ɛad din umi tᵉttwaṭṭef Urcalim.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 39
\s1 Uḍuf n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa n Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg uyur wiss ɛecra, yusa-dd Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ak-d marra řɛeskar nnes ɣar Urcalim uca nnḍen as-dd. \x ◘ \xo 39:1 \xt 2 Ij. 25:1; Irm. 52:4\x*  
\v 2 Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n Ṣidqiya, deg uyur wiss arebɛa, deg wass wiss tesɛa n uyur, wtin ibuxxac di \add řḥiḍ n\add* tendint.  
\v 3 \add Xas uca\add* udfen marra řḥukkam n ujeǧid n Babil uca qqimen di tewwart n wammas: Narjal-Caraṣar, Camjar-Nabu, Sarsaxim, azeǧif n imsexxaren n taddart n ujeǧid, Narjal-Carṣar, azeǧif n ayt n bu-tseḥḥart, uřa d marra řḥukkam inneɣni n ujeǧid n Babil.  
\v 4 Řami Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, d marra iɛeskariyyen nnes ẓrin ten, arewřen nitni, ffɣen zi tendint s ǧiřet x webrid ɣar weḥwic n ujeǧid. Nitni kkin zi tewwart jar tnayen n řeḥyuḍ uca netta iṭṭef abrid ɣar Řewḍa.   
\m
\v 5 Ḍfaren ten řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen, ḥarten x Ṣidqiya di řewḍat n Ariḥa. Nitni ṭṭfen t d ameḥbus uca iwyen t ɣar Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ɣar Ribla di temmurt n Ḥamat, u wanita iḥkem xas.  
\v 6 Ijja ujeǧid n Babil ad ɣarṣen iḥenjiren n Ṣidqiya zzat i tiṭṭawin nnes di Ribla. Uřa d marra tarwa n taṣiřet n Yahuda iɣarṣ asen ujeǧid n Babil.  
\v 7 Issdarɣeř netta tiṭṭawin n Ṣidqiya uca iqqen i-t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnḥas maḥend ad t yawi ɣar Babil.  
\v 8 Sscemḍen Ikaldaniyyen taddart n ujeǧid d tudrin n řgens s tmessi uca ařẓin řeḥyuḍ n Urcalim.  
\v 9 Min iceṭṭen zi řgens nni ittwajjen di tendint, \add ixs ad yini\add* \add marra\add* inni tuɣa iɛdun ɣar ujeǧid n Babil d min iceṭṭen zi řgens, indeh i-ten Nabuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, di lmenfa.  
\v 10 Zeg imezřaḍ n řgens nni war ɣar iǧi walu, ijja Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, ijj n wezyen di temmurt n Yahuda. Iwca asen deg wass nni imarjaɛen n uḍiř d iyyaren.   
\m
\v 11 Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, tuɣa yumur Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, x Irmiya, inna:  
\v 12 “Awyi t-i-dd, ḥḍa xas. War dayes ttegg uřa d ijj n řɣar, \add maca\add* egg akides am mammec i d ac ɣa yini.”  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* issekk Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, \add ca n ireqqasen\add*, \add netta jmiɛ\add* ak-d Nebucazban, ameqqran n imsexxaren n ujeǧid, d Narjal-Caraṣar, azeǧif n ayt n tseḥḥart, u ak-d marra ikumandaren n ujeǧid n Babil.  
\v 14 Jjin ten ad awyen Irmiya zi řemraḥ n řeḥbes, sellmen t deg ufus n Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, maḥend ad t-i-dd-awyen ɣar taddart nnes. \add Ammu i\add* iqqim izeddeɣ jar řgens. \f ◼ \fr 39:14 \ft \+fk jar řgens\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘di řwest n řgens’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řwaɛd i Ɛabd-Malik  
\m
\v 15 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya umi tuɣa ittwaḥṣar di řemraḥ n řeḥbes, inna:  
\v 16 “Ruḥ, siweř ak-d Ɛabd-Malik, Akuci, ini: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ awařen inu ɣar tendint-a, i řɣar war iǧi i řxar, ad dd-ffɣen \add wawařen inu\add* \bd deg wass nni\bd* zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec.\f ◼ \fr 39:16 \ft \+fk Akuci\ft  - niɣ ‘aryaz zi Kuc’.\f*  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* ad cek ssnejmeɣ deg wass nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, u cek war tᵉttmewcid ca deg ifassen n yeryazen i zi teggʷeded.  
\v 18 Maɣar Necc ad cek ssnejmeɣ. War ccaten s ssif. Ad tiři tudart nnec d takeccaḍt nnec, maɣar cek tᵉttecřed xafi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 40
\s1 Irmiya ak-d Jadalya  
\m
\v 1 Awař i dd-yusin zi SIDI ɣar Irmiya awarni řami t-i-dd-yiwi Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, zi Rama. Umi t-i-dd-iwyen, ittwacarf netta s ssnaseř di řwesṭ n imenfiyyen zi Urcalim d Yahuda, inni ittwaneddhen d imenfiyyen ɣar Babil.  
\v 2 Řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet i dd-yiwi Irmiya, inna as: “SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tuɣa ittbarreḥ s řɣar-a x wemcan-a  
\v 3 uca yarra \add i-t\add* SIDI ad dd-yas uca Netta igga s min tuɣa inna, maɣar kenniw texḍam ak-d SIDI u war tesřim ca ɣar tmijja nnes. S uyenni kenniw iřqef man aya.  
\v 4 Řexxu \add maca\add*, xzar, ad fesyeɣ ass-a ssnaseř nni x ifassen nnec. Mařa d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec ad kidi dd-tased ɣar Babil, \add xenni\add* as-dd, u necc ad cek ksiɣ. Maca mařa d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin nnec maḥend ad kidi tuyured ɣar Babil, ejj i-t xenni. Xzar, marra tammurt zzatek. Cek tzemmared ad tuyured ɣar ijj n wemcan i d ac ittɣiř d mliḥ d nican di tiṭṭawin nnec!”  
\v 5 Umi tuɣa \add ɛad\add* war dd-iɛqib, \add yarni inna\add*: “Dweř-dd ɣar Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, wenni igga ujeǧid n Babil x tneddam n Yahuda uca qqim ɣares jar řgens, niɣ uyur mani tᵉttwarid mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec maḥend ad traḥed.” \add Xas uca\add* iwca as řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet řeɛweč \add i umuddu\add* d ict n tarzeft uca ijja i-t ad yuyur.  
\v 6 Yuyur Irmiya ɣar Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, ɣar Miṣfat. Iqqim ittnusa ɣares di řwesṭ n řgens nni tuɣa iqqimen \add ɛad\add* di temmurt.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aneqqi n Jadalya  
\m
\v 7 \add Řami\add* marra ikumandaren n řɛeskarat nni \add iǧan\add* deg iyyaren, nitni d iryazen nsen, sřin aqa ajeǧid n Babil igga Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, x temmurt u igga i-t x yeryazen d temɣarin d iḥenjiren, x imezřaḍ qaɛ n temmurt u x \add marra\add* inni tuɣa war ittwanedhen ɣar Babil,  
\v 8 usin-dd nitni ɣar Jadalya di Miṣfat: Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, Yuḥanan d Yunatan, iḥenjiren n Qariḥa, Saraya, mmis n Tanḥumat, \add arni xas\add* iḥenjiren n Ɛifa, Anṭufati, d Yazanya, mmis n Umaɛki, \add marra\add* nitni ak-d yeryazen nsen.  
\v 9 Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, ijjuǧ asen u i yeryazen nsen, inna: “War tteggʷdem maḥend ad tsexxarem i Ikaldaniyyen. Qqimem di temmurt uca sexxarem i ujeǧid n Babil, \add xenni\add* ad tiřim mliḥ.  
\v 10 Uca necc, xzar, necc zeddɣeɣ di Miṣfat maḥend ad beddeɣ \add d amendub di ṭṭweɛ nwem\add* zzat i wudem n Ikaldaniyyen nni ɣarneɣ i dd ɣa yasen. Ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tessmunem binu d tini n unebdu d zzect, uca ggem aya deg iqdiḥen nwem uca zedɣem di tneddam nni tᵉṭṭfem.”   
\m
\v 11 Uřa d marra Udayen nni \add iǧan\add* di Mu’ab u jar ayt n Ɛammun u di Idum u di marra timmura \add inneɣni\add*, sřin aqa ajeǧid n Babil \add ijja\add* min iqqimen \add n imezdaɣ\add* di Yahuda u igga xasen Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan.  
\v 12 \add S uyenni\add* dd-ɛeqben marra Wudayen zi marra imucan mani xasen uẓẓřen uca iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Yahuda ɣar Jadalya ɣar Miṣfat. Nitni ssmunen aṭṭas n binu d tini n unebdu.   
\m
\v 13 \add Uřa d\add* Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa, d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskarat nni tuɣa deg iyyaren usin-dd ɣar Jadalya ɣar Miṣfat.  
\v 14 Nitni nnan as: “Ma tessned cek, aqa Baɛlis, ajeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun, issekk-dd Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, ḥima ad cek ineɣ?” Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, \add maca\add* war ten yumin.  
\v 15 Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa, \add maca\add* issiweř ak-d Jadalya s tnuffra di Miṣfat, inna: “Ejj ayi ad din řaḥeɣ u ad nɣeɣ Ismayil, mmis n Natanya. War t issin uřa d ijj. Mayemmi ɣa ineɣ ḥed u marra ayt n Yahuda i dd-xak imunen ad ttwasszuzzaren d min iqqimen zi Yahuda ad iweddar?”  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, inna i Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa: “War ttegg aya, maɣar min teqqared cek x Ismaɛil d ixarriqen \add waha\add*.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 41
\m
\v 1 Imsar deg uyur wiss sebɛa aqa yusa-dd Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, mmis n Ilicamaɛ, wenni d ijj zi řwacun n ujeǧid, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d imeqqranen n ujeǧid u akides \add ɛad\add* ɛecra n yeryazen, ɣar Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, ɣar Miṣfat. Nitni munen ttᵉtten din di Miṣfat. \x ◘ \xo 41:1 \xt 2 Ij. 25:25\x*  
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, \add jmiɛ ak-d\add* ɛecra n yeryazen nni tuɣa ɣares iǧan uca wtin Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, s ssif, uca ammu i inɣa \add Ismaɛil\add* wenni tuɣa igga ujeǧid n Babil x temmurt.  
\v 3 Inɣa Ismaɛil uřa d marra Udayen i ɣares, ixs ad yini inni tuɣa ɣar Jadalya di Miṣfat, uřa d Ikaldaniyyen nni ittwafen din, iɛeskariyyen.   
\m
\v 4 Deg wass wiss tnayen awarni řami inɣa Jadalya, am uřa d ijj war yargib \add ɛad\add*,  
\v 5 usin-dd iryazen zi Cakim, Cilu d Samarya, tmenyin n yeryazen, s timira ḥeffent d werruḍ icarreg d ixebbicen. Nitni \add iwyen-dd\add* deg ifassen nsen ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d jjawi maḥend ad tt awyen ɣar Taddart n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 41:5 \xt Lawi19:28; Irm. 16:6\x*  
\v 6 Uca iffeɣ ɣarsen Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, zi Miṣfat i umsagar akidsen, iru am iggur. Umi ten immeřqa, inna: “Asem-dd ɣar Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam!”  
\v 7 Umi dd-iwḍen nitni ɣar řwesṭ n tendint, iɣarṣ asen Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya. Netta d yeryazen i kides \add iǧan,\add* nḍaren ten di řwesṭ n wanu.  
\v 8 \add Maca\add* ttwafen ɛecra n yeryazen jar asen inni innan i Ismaɛil: “War d aneɣ neqq ca, maɣar deg iyyar neccin ɣarneɣ řeɛweč ixemmřen n irden, imendi, zzect d tamment.” \add Xenni\add* iḥta xasen, war ten inɣi di řwesṭ n aytmas.  
\v 9 Anu nni di inḍar Ismaɛil marra arrimat n yeryazen nni inɣa ɣar uɣezdis n Jadalya, tuɣa d wenni igga ujeǧid Asa zi ssibbet n Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil. Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, iccur i-t s yinni ittwanɣen.   
\m
\v 10 Indeh Ismaɛil marra min iqqimen \add ɛad\add* zi řgens \add i iǧan\add* di Miṣfat, d imeḥbas, aqa yessis n ujeǧid d marra řgens nni tuɣa iqqimen \add ɛad\add* di Miṣfat, inni x tuɣa igga Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam. Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya indeh i-ten d imeḥbas uca yuyur ḥima ad iɛdu \add x L’Urdun\add* ɣar \add temmurt n\add* ayt n Ɛammun.  
\v 11 \add Umi\add* Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariha, d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskarat nni tuɣa ɣares iǧan, sřin s marra řɣar i tuɣa igga Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya,  
\v 12 iwyen nitni marra iryazen uca ṭṭfen \add abrid\add* ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya. Nitni ufin t ɣar uyeřmam ameqqran ɣar Jibɛun.  
\v 13 Řami marra řgens i tuɣa ak-d Ismaɛil, inṭeḥ Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa, d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskar nni ɣares, farḥen aṭṭas.  
\v 14 Marra řgens nni tuɣa indeh Ismaɛil d ameḥbus zi Miṣfat, qeřben, dewřen-dd uca ɛdun ɣar Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariḥa.  
\v 15 Ismaɛil \add maca\add*, mmis n Natanya, yarweř zi zzat n wudem n Yuḥanan ak-d tmenya n yeryazen uca yuyur ɣar ayt n Ɛammun.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tarewřa ɣar Miṣra  
\m
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* iksi Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, \add netta jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskarat nni ɣares \add iǧan\add*, marra min iqqimen ɣar ḍeffar n řgens i yiwi netta zi Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, zi Miṣfat, awarni řami inɣa wanita Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam: \add aqa\add* iryazen ijehden, iɛeskariyyen, timɣarin, iḥenjiren imeẓyanen d imsexxaren icennɛen nni dd-isseɛqeb netta zi Jibɛun.  
\v 17 Nitni uyuren \add deg webrid\add* uca qqimen deg wemcan n arraḥet n Kimhan nni ɣar Bayt-Laḥm, maḥend ad ssenni ɛdun ařami ɣa udfen nitni ɣar Miṣra.  
\v 18 \add Nitni arewřen\add* zi zzat n wudem n Ikaldaniyyen, maɣar ggʷeden zzaysen, maɣar Ismaɛil, mmis n Natanya, inɣa Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, wenni igga ujeǧid n Babil \add d řbaca\add* x temmurt.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 42
\m
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* qarrben-dd marra ikumandaren n řɛeskar, Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, d Yazanya, mmis n Hucaɛya, d marra řgens, zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran.  
\v 2 Nitni nnan i unabi Irmya: “Iři ad yaf tutra nneɣ arḍa zzat i wudem nnec. Ttar aneɣ ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di ṭṭweɛ n marra min iqqimen, minzi neccin neqqim \add ɛad\add* s drus zeg waṭṭas, am mammec tzemmared ad tᵉtwarid s tiṭṭawin nnec umi ɣarneɣ txezzared.  
\v 3 Iři SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ad aneɣ isscen man abrid i ɣa neḍfar d min ɣa negg.”  
\v 4 Inna asen unabi Irmiya: “Necc sřiɣ t. Xzar, necc ad ttareɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ɛlaḥsab awařen nwem. Necc ad awem iniɣ marra awař nni zi dd xawem i ɣa yarr SIDI, war zzaywem ssnuffareɣ uřa d ijj n wawař.”  
\v 5 Nitni nnan i Irmiya: “SIDI ad yiři d Ccahed d amtiqqi d aṣdiq jar aneɣ, mařa war nᵉttegg ɛlaḥsab kuř awař nni kidek ɣarneɣ dd ɣa issekk SIDI, AREBBI nnec!  
\v 6 D aṣebḥan niɣ d aɛeffan, ad nseř ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, i umi cek i ɣa nessekk maḥend ad niři mliḥ xmi ɣa nseř ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 42:6 \xt Irm. 7:23\x*   
\m
\v 7 Awarni řami ɛdun ɛecra n wussan, imsar aqa iffeɣ wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya.  
\v 8 \add Xas uca\add* iřaɣa netta x Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, u x marra ikumandaren n řɛeskar nni tuɣa ɣares \add iǧan\add*, uřa x marra řgens, zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran.  
\v 9 Inna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ɣar wenni d ayi tessekkem, ḥima ad as ssiwḍeɣ tutra nwem zzat i wudem nnes:  
\v 10 ‘Mařa kenniw teqqimem tzeddɣem di temmurt-a, ammu kenniw i ɣa ssbeddeɣ u war kenniw heddmeɣ, ad kenniw ẓẓuɣ u war kenniw qeřɛeɣ, maɣar Necc neddmeɣ x řɣar i daywem ggiɣ. \x ◘ \xo 42:10 \xt Irm. 24:6; 31:4; 33:7\x*  
\v 11 War tteggʷdem ca zeg ujeǧid n Babil, wenni zi tᵉtteggʷedem. War zzayes tteggʷdem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Maɣar Necc akidwem ḥima ad kenniw ssnejmeɣ u ad kenniw fekkeɣ zeg ufus nnes.  
\v 12 Necc ad kenniw areḥmeɣ maḥend netta ad kenniw yarḥem u ad kenniw yarr ad tdewřem ɣar temmurt nwem.   
\m
\v 13 \add Maca\add* mařa kenniw teqqarem: Neccin war nettɣimi ca di temmurt-a, u \add mařa kenniw\add* war tᵉttesřim ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nwem,  
\v 14 ad tinim: Lla, nexs ad nuyur ɣar Miṣra mani war nẓarr amenɣi u war nᵉttesři i usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri u war nettřiẓi aɣrum. Aqa dinni i nexs ad neqqim!’,  
\v 15 xenni sřem řexxu ɣar wawař n SIDI, kenniw min iqqimen n Yahuda. Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Mařa kenniw tɛemmdem ad tuyurem ɣar Miṣra uca ad dd-tawḍem ḥima ad din tzedɣem am yibarraniyyen,  
\v 16 \add xenni\add* ssif i zi tᵉtteggʷedem ad kenniw iřqef dinni di Miṣra u řaẓ i zi tᵉtteggʷedem ad kenniw dd-iḍfar dinni di Miṣra u ad dinni temmtem.  
\v 17 Xenni marra iryazen nni ixsen ad uyuren ɣar Miṣra ḥima ad din zedɣen am yibarraniyyen ad mmten s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun. War zzaysen inejjem niɣ ittarekkwař uřa d ijjen zi řɣar i xasen dd ɣa ɣeḍřeɣ.’  
\v 18 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Am mammec aɣḍab inu d wesɛar inu ttwazeǧɛen x imezdaɣ n Urcalim, ammu i ɣa ittwazeǧeɛ uřa d asɛar inu xawem mařa tiwḍem ɣar Miṣra. Kenniw ad tdewřem d \add řqecɛet n\add* wexzi d unexřiɛ d tseḍḥact, uřa d nneɛřet d řḥegra. Amcan-a ɛemmarṣ ad tt tẓarem ɛad.’ \x ◘ \xo 42:18 \xt Ica. 65:15; Irm. 7:20; 18:16; 19:8; 24:9; 25:9, 18; 26:6; 29:18\x*  
\v 19 SIDI issiweř ɣarwem, \add a\add* min iqqimen n Yahuda! War ttidfem ɣar Miṣra. Snem mliḥ aqa necc ɛeřmeɣ awem ass-a.  
\v 20 Maɣar kenniw tɣeccem x yixef nwem. Kenniw simant nwem tessekkem ayi-dd ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, tennam: ‘Ẓaǧ aneɣ ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ. Ini aneɣ marra min ɣa yiři ad yini SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, uca neccin ad t negg!’  
\v 21 Ass-a nniɣ awem, \add maca\add* kenniw war tesřim ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, ɣar marra s min zi i d ayi ɣarwem dd-issekk.  
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, snem mliḥ aqa ad temmtem s ssif d řaẓ d ṭṭaɛun deg wemcan mani texsem ad tuyurem ḥima ad dinni teqqimem am yibarraniyyen.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 43
\m
\v 1 Imsar umi ikemmeř Irmiya řhard nnes i marra řgens s marra awařen n SIDI, AREBBI nsen, s min zi tuɣa SIDI, AREBBI nsen, issekk i-t-i-dd ɣarsen,  
\v 2 aqa issiweř Ɛazarya, mmis n Hucaɛya, u nnan \add ɛawed\add* Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, d marra yeryazen imɛeffaren i Irmiya: “Cek tessxarriqed. SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, war cek dd-isekk maḥend ad tinid: ‘War iɛeddeř ad traḥem ɣar Miṣra maḥend ad dinni teqqimem am yibarraniyyen!’  
\v 3 Maca Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, i cek i dd-iḥarrcen xaneɣ, ḥima ad aneɣ tsellmed ɣar ifassen n Ikaldaniyyen, maḥend ad aneɣ nɣen u ad aneɣ nedhen di lmenfa ɣar Babil.”   
\m
\v 4 \add Ammu\add* war isři Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskar uřa d marra řgens ɣar tmijja n SIDI, maḥend ad qqimen di temmurt n Yahuda.  
\v 5 Yuḥanan, mmis n Qariyaḥ, d marra ikumandaren n řɛeskar ksin marra min iqqimen n Yahuda, inni tuɣa dd-idewřen zi marra řegnus ɣar mani xasen uẓẓřen, ḥima ad qqimen di temmurt n Yahuda:  
\v 6 iryazen ijehden d temɣarin d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen d yessis n ujeǧid d marra řeɛmar nni tuɣa ijja Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, ɣar Jadalya, mmis n Axiqam, mmis n Cafan, uřa d anabi Irmiya d Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah.  
\v 7 Nitni usin-dd ɣar temmurt n Miṣra, minzi nitni war sřin ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI uca usin-dd ař Taḥfanis.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Irmiya ittnabba di Taḥfanḥis  
\m
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Irmiya di Taḥfanḥis, inna:  
\v 9 “Ksi iẓra imeqqranen deg ufus nnec uca nuffar i-ten deg ubeǧaɛ n tisi n luṣa ɣar wadaf n taddart n firɛun di Taḥfanis. \add Egg i-t\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin n yeryazen n Yahuda,  
\v 10 ini asen: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Xzar, Necc ad awyeɣ Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, amsexxar inu, uca ad ggeɣ řɛarc nnes x yeẓra-ya nni nuffareɣ \add dinni\add*, uca netta ad iwwet aqiḍun nnes igellden tiwa nsen. \x ◘ \xo 43:10 \xt Irm. 25:9; 27:6\x*  
\v 11 Netta ad dd-yas uca ad iwwet tammurt n Miṣra: wenni \add iǧan\add* i řmewt, s řmewt, d wenni \add iǧan\add* i tmeḥbast, i uḥebbes, d wenni \add iǧan\add* i ssif, s ssif. \x ◘ \xo 43:11 \xt Irm. 15:2; Zak. 11:9\x*  
\v 12 Netta ad ssareɣ ict n tmessi deg ixxamen n l’aṣnam n Miṣra, ad sscemḍeɣ ixammen nni u ad awyeɣ l’aṣnam d imeḥbas. Netta ad yarḍ tammurt n Miṣra am umeksaw yarḍ arruḍ nnes uca netta ad zzayes dd-iffeɣ di řehna.  
\v 13 Netta ad yarẓ imayḍuten nsen \add iqeddsen\add*, nni \add iǧan\add* di temmurt n Miṣra, uca ad issecmeḍ ixxamen n l’aṣnam n Miṣra s tmessi.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 44
\s1 Řgens n Israil di Miṣra iɛebbed tajeǧidt n ujenna  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni dd-iffɣen ɣar Irmiya i marra Udayen nni tuɣa izeddɣen di temmurt n Miṣra, inni tuɣa izeddɣen di Majdal d Taḥfanḥis d Nuf u di temmurt n Fatrus, i innan:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Kenniw simant nwem teẓrim řɣar i ggiɣ x Urcalim u x marra tineddam n Yahuda, uca xzar, řexxu dewřent nitenti d řxirbet, war daysent izeddeɣ ɛad uřa d ijj,  
\v 3 zi ssibbet n řɣar i ggin umi d ayi sɛaren ařami wehhben řebxur maḥend ad \add zzayes\add* ɛebden i irebbiten nneɣni inni war ssinen nitni, řa d kenniw uřa d řejdud nwem.  
\v 4 Necc ssekkeɣ-dd ɣarwem marra imsexxaren inu, inabiyyen, ɛad zeg umezwaru ssekkeɣ ten ḥima ad inin: War tteggem nnɛi-ya nni carrheɣ Necc \add aṭṭas\add*.  
\v 5 Nitni \add maca\add* war sřin u war d ayi wcin amezzuɣ nsen umi dd-dewřen nedmen zi řɣar nsen, umi war wehhben \add ɛad ktar\add* tiwhibin nsen n řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni.  
\v 6 \add S uya\add* i farɣeɣ asɛar inu d weɣḍab inu x tneddam n Yahuda u x ibriden n Urcalim, \add ařami\add* dewřent d řxirbet, ttwaredǧent am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.’” \x ◘ \xo 44:6 \xt Irm. 7:20; 42:18\x*   
\m
\v 7 “\add Xenni\add* řexxu, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Mayemmi tᵉtteggem řɣar am wanita x tudart nwem ařami tqeṭṭam x weryaz d temɣart, aḥenjir d useymi zi řwesṭ n Yahuda ařami war xawem iceṭṭ min iqqimen?  
\v 8 Mayemmi i d ayi tseɛɛarem s řxedmet n ifassen nwem, umi tessbexxaram řebxur i irebbiten nneɣni zi temmurt n Miṣra mani ɣar dd-tiwḍem řexxu ḥima ad dinni tzedɣem am yibarraniyyen, ařami ɣa tqeḍɛem ixef nwem \add ammu\add* u ḥima ad tdewřem d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* wexzi d řḥegra jar marra řegnus n temmurt?  
\v 9 Ma tᵉttum kenniw qaɛ řɣar i ggin řejdud nwem d řɣar i ggin ijeǧiden n Yahuda d řɣar i ggint temɣarin nsen uřa d řɣar i teggim kenniw simant nwem d řɣar i ggint temɣarin nwem di temmurt n Yahuda u deg ibriden n Urcalim?  
\v 10 Ař ass-a i di neǧa ɛad war ttwarrẓen \add deg wuř\add*, war zzayi tteggʷden u war ḍeffaran Ccariɛa inu d tweṣṣa inu nni kenniw wciɣ zzat i wudem nwem u zzat i wudem n řejdud nwem.’”   
\m
\v 11 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Xzar, Necc ad arreɣ udem inu i řɣar xawem u ḥima ad qḍiɣ marra Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 44:11 \xt Irm. 21:10; Ɛam. 9:4\x*  
\v 12 Necc ad kkseɣ min iqqimen n Yahuda, inni iɛemmden ad uyuren ɣar temmurt n Miṣra ḥima ad dinni zedɣen am yibarraniyyen. Nitni ad ttwahellken marra, ad wḍan di temmurt n Miṣra. Nitni ad ttwahellken s ssif d řaẓ, am umeẓyan am umeqqran. Nitni ad mmten s ssif d řaẓ uca ad dewřen d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* wexzi d unexřiɛ d nneɛřet d řḥegra. \x ◘ \xo 44:12 \xt Irm. 42:15, 16, 17, 22\x*  
\v 13 Necc ad xeřfeɣ zeg inni izeddɣen di temmurt n Miṣra am mammec tuɣa xeřfeɣ zi Urcalim, s ssif, s řaẓ u s ṭṭaɛun.  
\v 14 Zi min iqqimen n Yahuda, zeg inni iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad dinni zedɣen am yibarraniyyen, war inejjim niɣ ittarekkwař uřa d ijj, ḥima ad dd-iɛqeb ɣar temmurt n Yahuda mani ttexsen ad dd-ɛeqben maḥend ad din zedɣen. War dd-tteɛqiben ca, mɣir \add ca\add* inni inejmen.’”   
\m
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* arrin-dd x Irmiya marra iryazen, inni issnen aqa timɣarin nsen wehhbent řebxur i irebbiten inneɣni, uřa d marra timɣarin i din ibedden, ijj n ubarru d ameqqran, marra řgens nni tuɣa izeddɣen di temmurt n Miṣra, di Fatrus, nnan:  
\v 16 “X wawař i kidneɣ tessiwřed deg Yisem n SIDI, war ɣarek nᵉttesři ca.  
\v 17 Maɣar kuř awař i dd-iffɣen zeg uqemmum nneɣ ad t negg umi ɣa nessbexxar i tjeǧidt n ujenna u umi d as i ɣa nseyyeb tiwhibin n useyyeb am mammec tuɣa negga, neccin d řejdud nneɣ uřa d ijeǧiden nneɣ d řḥukkam nneɣ, di tneddam n Yahuda u deg ibriden n Urcalim, \add umi\add* tuɣa nejjiwen neccin s weɣrum u tuɣa aneɣ mliḥ, tuɣa war din tarjijat zi ḥed. \x ◘ \xo 44:17 \xt Irm. 7:18\x*  
\v 18 Zeg wami maca nessbedd nettwehheb řebxur i tjeǧidt n ujenna u zeg useyyeb n tewhibin i nettat, aqa neḥwaj u nefna neccin s ssif d řaẓ.  
\v 19 Mařa neccin nessbexxar i tjeǧidt n ujenna, nseyyeb as tiwhibin n useyyeb, ma nhřa \add argab d řxaḍar n\add* yeryazen nneɣ negga as tifḍirin i ṣṣedqet nni dayes yarwesen u nseyyeb as tiwhibin n useyyeb?”   
\m
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Irmiya ɣar marra řgens, ɣar iryazen d temɣarin, ɣar marra řgens nni tuɣa i dd xas yarrin \add ammu\add*, inna:  
\v 21 “Tiwhibin n řebxur nni tessbexxarem di tneddam n Yahuda u x ibriden n Urcalim, kenniw d řejdud nwem, ijeǧiden nwem d řḥukkam nwem d řgens n temmurt, ma war tent idar SIDI niɣ war dd-usint ɣar řbař nnes?  
\v 22 SIDI war iqqim \add ɛad\add* iṣebbar awem x tmegga nwem tiɛeffanin, x jjɛayef i teggim. S uyenni tedweř temmurt nwem d řxarbet d ict n temmurt ixřan uřa d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d nneɛřet ařami war din izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.  
\v 23 Minzi kenniw tiwyem-dd řebxur u texḍam ak-d SIDI u war tesřim ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI u war tuyurem di Ccariɛa nnes, di tweṣṣa nnes u di cchadat nnes, x uya i kenniw iřqef řɣar-a, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.”   
\m
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* inna Irmiya i marra řgens u i marra timɣarin: “Sřem i wawař n SIDI, marra Yahuda nni iǧan di temmurt n Miṣra.  
\v 25 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, iqqar: ‘X kenniw u x temɣarin nwem, aqa tennam \add t\add* s uqemmum nwem u s ifassen nwem teggim \add t\add*, tennam: Amewci n wawař i negga, ad t nkemmeř nican ḥima ad nqeddem tiwhibin n řebxur i tjeǧidt n ujenna u ḥima ad nseyyeb tiwhibin n useyyeb. \add Xenni\add* kemmřem nican lwuɛud i twaɛdem u ggem s tidett min tuɣa twaɛdem.’”   
\m
\v 26 “S uya sřem i wawař n SIDI, marra Yahuda i izeddɣen di Miṣra: ‘Xzar, Necc jjuǧeɣ s Yisem inu ameqqran, iqqar SIDI, war ittwařaɣa s Yisem inu \add ɛad\add* zi ca n weryaz mammec ma igga zi Yahuda di marra tammurt n Miṣra, ad yini: S tidett am iddar Sidi inu, SIDI!  
\v 27 Xzar, Necc ad xasen ɛesseɣ i řɣar, war iǧi i řxar. Marra iryazen n Yahuda nni iǧan di temmurt n Miṣra, ad hellken s ssif d řaẓ ař ɣa ttwakksen. \x ◘ \xo 44:27 \xt Irm. 31:28\x*  
\v 28 \add Maca\add* inni yarewřen zi ssif, ad dd-dewřen zi temmurt n Miṣra ɣar temmurt n Yahuda, \add mɣir\add* ijj n wuru n yeryazen. Marra min iqqimen n Yahuda i dd-iwḍen ɣar temmurt n Miṣra ḥima ad din zedɣen am yibarraniyyen, ad ssnen awař n man wen i ɣa iqqim ibedd, wenni inu niɣ wenni nsen.  
\v 29 Man aya ad awem tiři d řeɛřamet, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, aqa Necc ad kenniw ɛaqbeɣ deg wemcan-a ḥima ad tessnem aqa awařen inu xawem ad xawem iřin i řɣar.  
\v 30 \add Man aya ad yiři d řeɛřamet\add*, ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ firɛun Ḥufraɛ, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ɣar ufus n řɛedyan nnes u ɣar ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nnes, am mammec ssiwḍeɣ Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, řeɛdu nnes wenni tuɣa yarezzun tudart nnes.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 45
\s1 Awař n Irmiya i Barux  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni issawař unabi Irmiya i Barux, mmis n Niri-Yah, umi yura wanita awařen zeg uqemmum n Irmiya deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Inna:  
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, xak, \add a\add* Barux!  
\v 3 Cek tennid: ‘Axeyyeb i necc, maɣar SIDI yarenni ɛad acḍan x řeḥriq inu. Necc uḥřeɣ s wezhar, war ufiɣ arraḥet!’  
\v 4 Ittxeṣṣa ad as tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Xzar, min ssbeddeɣ, ad t ɣeḍřeɣ, u min ẓẓuɣ, ad t qeřɛeɣ, \add wah,\add* marra tammurt-a.  
\v 5 Ma texsed cek ad tarzud x tmesřayin timeqqranin i yixef nnec? War tent tarezzud ca, maɣar xzar, Necc ad ssiwḍeɣ ijj n řɣar x marra ddat, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, \add maca\add* ad ac wceɣ řeɛmar nnec d takeccaḍt di marra imucan mani ɣa traḥed.’” \x ◘ \xo 45:5 \xt Irm. 21:9; 38:2; 39:18\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 46
\s1 Awařen x řegnus  
\m
\v 1 Awař n SIDI nni dd-yusin ɣar unabi Irmiya x řegnus.   
\b  
\m
\v 2 \bd X Miṣra\bd*  
\m Ḍidd n řɛeskar n firɛun Naxu, ajeǧid n Miṣra, wenni din ɣar yeɣzar n Lfuraṭ, ɣar Karkamic, wenni yarna Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n Yahuyaqim, mmis n Yuciya, ajeǧid n Yahuda.   
\m
\v 3 “Swejdem taseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* d tseddart \add nnes\add* tameqqrant uca sgeɛɛdem ɣar umenɣi!  
\v 4 Ḥezzmen i iysan, nyem xasem, \add a\add* imnayen n yeysan! Sbeddem ixef nwem s lkaskat \add x izeǧifen nwem\add*. Sqeḍɛem fřitcat uca ḥezzmem s warruḍ n wuzzař! \x ◘ \xo 46:4 \xt Irm. 51:11\x*  
\v 5 Mayemmi ttwařiɣ Necc aqa nitni nnxeřɛen ařami dewřen ɣar ḍeffar? Ɛad ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nsen ttwarẓen, menɛen di tarewřa uca war i-dd-nnqeřben ɣar ḍeffar. Aqa din asnexřiɛ di marra iɣezdisen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 6 Ejj wenni ifsusen s iḍaren war ittarekkwař uřa d bu-teɣruḍt war inejjem: nnqarḍen, wḍan di ccamal, ɣar tma n iɣzar n Lfuraṭ.”   
\m
\v 7 “Man wen i din dd-igeɛɛden am waman \add n Miṣra\add*, aman nnes zehharen am yiɣezran?  
\v 8 Miṣra tgeɛɛed-dd am waman, aman nnes zehharen am yiɣezran, teqqar: ‘Necc ad geɛɛdeɣ, ad dřeɣ tammurt, ad qḍiɣ x tendint d yinni dayes izeddɣen.  
\v 9 Geɛɛdem, \add a\add* iysan, muzzarem, \add kenniw, a\add* ikarruten n umenɣi! Jjem ayt n bu-teɣruḍt ad ffɣen: ayt n Kuc, ayt n Fuṭ inni yarebbun taseddart \add n uɛeskari\add* d ayt n Lud inni itteṭṭfen řqews uca meḥḥḍen t. \x ◘ \xo 46:9 \xt Ica. 66:19\x*  
\v 10 Ass-a d ijj n wass i Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, ijj n wass n wexřaf maḥend ad ixřef i yixef nnes zeg iɣrimen nnes. Ad yecc ssif, ad ijjawen uca ad iscar s idammen nsen, maɣar aqa din ict n tɣarṣt i Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, di temmurt n ccamal ɣar yeɣzar n Lfuraṭ.  
\v 11 Geɛɛdem ɣar Jilɛad, awyem-d balsam, \add a cem\add* taɛzarect, iǧis n Miṣra!. Baṭeř tarennid di ddwawat aṭṭas, \add maɣar\add* war ɣarem bu ddawat ḥima ad tent tegged \add x uyezzim\add*.\x ◘ \xo 46:11 \xt Irm. 8:22\x*  
\v 12 Sřin řegnus x řefḍiḥet nnem uca teccur temmurt zeg iɣuyyan \add n řeḥřiq\add* nnem, maɣar bu-teɣruḍt imqarqeb ak-d bu-teɣruḍṭ nneɣni, munen wḍan s tnayen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 13 Awař nni issiweř SIDI ɣar unabi Irmiya x twasit n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ḥima ad iwwet tammurt n Miṣra.   
\m
\v 14 “Barrḥem \add t\add* di Miṣra u jjem ad as sřen di Majdal, jjem ad as sřen di Nuf d Taḥfanḥis. Inim: ‘Bedd abeddi, wjed!’, maɣar ssif icca \add marra\add* iɣezdisen i d ac dd-innḍen.  
\v 15 Mayemmi ttwamḥan ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa nnec? War izemmar netta ad iqqim ibedd, minzi SIDI iɛarren i-t.  
\v 16 Netta yarra aṭṭas ad nqarḍen, \add wah,\add* aryaz iwḍa x wenneɣni, uca nitni nnan: ‘Kkarem, jjem aneɣ ad nedweř ɣar řgens nneɣ u ɣar temmurt mani nexřeq zi ssibbet n ssif iwɛaren.’  
\v 17 Din i řaɣan nitni: ‘Aqa firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ittwareddeǧ, aqa ijja řweqt ittwaggen ad teɛdu.’”   
\m
\v 18 “S tidett am ddareɣ Necc, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Ujeǧid, SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes: ‘Netta ad dd-yas, am \add wedrar n\add* Tabur jar idurar u am \add wedrar n\add* Karmil ɣar řebḥar!  
\v 19 Smun řeḥwayej nnem i lmenfa, \add a cem\add* tamezduɣt, iǧis n Miṣra, maɣar \add tammurt n\add* Nuf ad tedweř d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ uca ad tᵉttwareddeǧ, ařami war din iqqim uřa d ijj izeddeɣ.   
\m
\v 20 \add Tammurt n\add* Miṣra d ict n taɛejmit tecna, \add maca\add* ad ɣares dd-yas ijj n yarezzi d adarɣař, ad dd-yas zi ccamal.  
\v 21 Uřa d icewwařen nnes di řwesṭ nnes ggin am yiɛejmiyyen iṣeḥḥen, \add maca\add* uřa d nitni ɛeqben-dd, nitni arewřen jmiɛ, war qqimen bedden, maɣar ass n uḍeyyeɛ nsen ad xasen dd-yas, tasaɛɛet n wexřaf nsen.  
\v 22 Tmijja nnes tegga am řḥess n ufiɣar iḥrarran, maɣar ad din uyuren ak-d ijj n řɛeskar u ad ɣares dd-asen s ccwaqar am yinezdamen n ukeccuḍ. \f ◼ \fr 46:22 \ft \+fk Tmijja nnes\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘tmijja n Miṣra’. Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ad ihjem x temmurt n Misřa s řɛeskar nnes amecnaw hejmen s ccwaqer x ijj n ufiɣar deg iyyar.\f*  
\v 23 Nitni ad qessen azɣar nnes, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar \add řɛeskar\add* war izemmar ad ittwaḥseb, minzi nitni aqa aten deg waṭṭas x iburexsen, war zemmaren ad ttwaḥesben. \f ◼ \fr 46:23 \ft \+fk azɣar\ft  - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  
\v 24 Tseḍḥa yeǧis n Miṣra, aqa tᵉttwagg deg ufus n ijj n řgens zi ccamal.’”   
\m
\v 25 “SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil, inna: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ɛaqbeɣ Amun zi \add temmurt n\add* Nu, d firɛun d Miṣra, irebbiten nnes d ijeǧiden nnes, \add wah,\add* firɛun d yinni xas ittcařen.  
\v 26 Necc ad ten wceɣ deg ufus n yinni yarezzun tudart nsen řa deg ufus n Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, uřa deg ufus n imsexxaren nnes. \add Awarni i uya\add* ad tedweř temmurt s imezdaɣ ɛawed am deg wussan n zic, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 27 “War teggʷed, \add a\add* cek amsexxar inu Yaɛqub, war tefciř ca, \add a\add* Israil, maɣar xzar, Necc ad cek ssnejmeɣ zi timmura iggʷejen uřa d zzariɛet nnec zi tmeḥbast nsen. Ad yareggʷeḥ Yaɛqub, ad ɣares tiři řhudnet, ad iddar di řaman uca uřa d ijj war t issnexřiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 46:27 \xt Ica. 41:13; 43:5; 44:1; Irm. 30:10\x*  
\v 28 War tteggʷed, \add a\add* cek amsexxar inu Yaɛqub, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar Necc akidek, minzi Necc ad qḍiɣ x marra řegnus nni mani kenniw ssiggʷejeɣ, \add maca\add* ɛemmarṣ war xak qeṭṭiɣ, \add maca\add* ad cek webbxeɣ s řeɛbar iseggden u war cek heṣṣbeɣ d amezdag.’” \x ◘ \xo 46:28 \xt Irm. 10:24; 30:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 47
\s1 X Ifilisṭiniyyen  
\m
\v 1 Awař n SIDI nni dd-yusin ɣar unabi Irmiya, \add awař i iwejjhen\add* \bd ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen\bd* qbeř ma iwta firɛun Ɣazza.   
\m
\v 2 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, aman geɛɛden zi ccamal, ad dewřen d ict n teɣzart tessfay. Ad ḥemřen x temmurt u x marra min dayes iǧan, tandint d imezdaɣ nnes. Ad sɣuyen iwdan u marra imezdaɣ n temmurt ad ceḍnen aṭṭas  
\v 3 zi ssibbet n wezbar n tecti n tceḍyin n \add yeysan\add* ijehden, zi ssibbet n ddriz n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* d uqarqeb n tjarrarin. \add Ɛad\add* ibabaten war ḥekkaren ca i iḥenjiren \add nsen\add* maɣar ifassen nsen dewřen arehfen \x ◘ \xo 47:3 \xt Ica. 5:28; Irm. 4:13; 6:23\x*  
\v 4 zi ssibbet n wass i dd ɣa yasen ḥima ad ttwateḥḥan marra ayt n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ḥima ad ittwakkes zi Ṣur d Ṣidun kuř bu-twiza i yarewřen, maɣar SIDI ad iteḥḥa Ifilisṭiniyyen, min iqqimen n tegzirt n Kaftur. \x ◘ \xo 47:4 \xt Irm. 25:22\x*  
\v 5 Tusa-dd tqeccart x Ɣazza, tesseɣd \add temmurt n\add* Acqalun \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d min iqqimen n řewḍa n teɣzurt nsen. Ař meřmi ɣa teqqimed ɛad txebbced ixef nnem? \x ◘ \xo 47:5 \xt Aɛwd. 14:1; Irm. 16:6; 25:20\x*  
\v 6 Uct \add xak, a\add* ssif n SIDI, ař meřmi i ɣa teqqimed ɛad nehřa arraḥet? Dweř-dd ɣar furru n weɣřaf nnec, qqim war tenhezza!  
\v 7 Mammec i ɣa teqqimed tarsid? Aqa SIDI yumur ssif ḍidd i Acqalun u ḍidd i tma n řebḥar, i manayenni i ittwagg.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 48
\m
\v 1 \bd X Mu’ab\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Uct x Nabu, maɣar aqa \add tandint\add* tᵉttwaxarreb, \add tandint n\add* Qaryatayim tᵉṭṭef i-tt řeḥya, aqa tᵉttwaṭṭef. Lburj yuɛřan tᵉṭṭef i-tt řehya u tᵉttenhezza. \x ◘ \xo 48:1 \xt Irm. 25:21; 27:3\x*  
\v 2 Řɛezz n \add temmurt n\add* Mu’ab war iǧi \add ɛad\add*. Di Ḥacbun xarrṣen di řɣar ḍidd nnes, nnan: Ejj aneɣ ad tt nekkes zi jar řegnus. Uřa d cek, Madmin, ad cek ssbekmen, ssif ggur ad cek iḍfar.  
\v 3 \add Teffeɣ\add* ict n tɣuyyit \add n řeḥriq\add* zi Ḥurunayim: Axarreb d lmuṣiba d tameqqrant!  
\v 4 \add Tammurt n\add* Mu’ab tᵉttwarẓ, iḥenjiren nnes imeẓyanen ggin ad tᵉttwaseř tɣuyyit tejhed.  
\v 5 Wah, am ittru ittgeɛɛad netta tsawent n Luḥit, maɣar ɣar uhekkwu ɣar Ḥurunayim sřin aduqqez n iɣuyyan n txessart. \x ◘ \xo 48:5 \xt Ica. 15:5\x*  
\v 6 Arewřem, snejmem tudart nwem, dewřem am yijj n uxeccab di tnezruft. \x ◘ \xo 48:6 \xt Irm. 17:6\x*  
\v 7 Minzi cem tᵉttecřed x tmegga nnem d řeknuz nnem, uřa d cem ad tᵉttwaṭṭfed. Kamuc ad yuyur di lmenfa, ikehhanen nnes \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d řḥukkam nnes. \x ◘ \xo 48:7 \xt Irm. 49:3\x*  
\v 8 Amteḥḥay ad dd-yas ɣar kuř tandint uca uřa d ict n tendint war tzemmar ad tenjem. Ad tᵉttwabḍeř řewḍa n teɣzurt uca řwaṭa ad tᵉttwaxarreb, am mammec t inna SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 9 “Wcem afriwen i Mu’ab, maɣar nitni ad ffɣen s tazřa uca tineddam nnes ad dewřent d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ, mani war ittɣimi izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj.  
\v 10 Ittwanɛeř wenni yarxun di tsexxart n SIDI, ittwanɛeř wenni issbedden ssif nnes x \add usizzeř n\add* idammen.  
\v 11 Tuɣa Mu’ab di řaman zi temẓi nnes, yarsa \add am binu\add* x řexmira nnes, war t farrɣen zeg uqdiḥ ɣar uqdiḥ \add nneɣni\add* u ɛemmarṣ war iffiɣ ɣar lmenfa. X uya iqqim as uředdi nnes d řefwaḥ nnes war ibeddeř. \x ◘ \xo 48:11 \xt Ṣaf. 1:12\x*  
\v 12 S uya, xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, iqqar SIDI, ad ɣares dd-ssekkeɣ inni i ɣa ifarrɣen iqdiḥen uca nitni ad t farrɣen. Nitni ad ssexwan řeqcuɛ nnes u ad arẓen iɣarrafen nnes.  
\v 13 Mu’ab ad innefḍeḥ zi ssibbet n Kamuc, am mammec tennefḍeḥ taddart n Israil zi ssibbet n Bayt-Il, i xef tuɣa ttᵉtcřen nitni. \x ◘ \xo 48:13 \xt 1 Ij. 12:29\x*  
\v 14 Mammec tzemmarem ad tinim: ‘Neccin d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt, iryazen imeḥḍen, \add iwejden\add* i umenɣi?’  
\v 15 Mu’ab ittwaxarreb uca igeɛɛed \add řeɛdu\add* ɣar tneddam nnes. Acewwar n iḥudriyyen nnes hwan-dd ɣar tɣarṣt, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Ujeǧid, Isem nnes SIDI n řɛeskarat.”   
\m
\v 16 “Aḍeyyeɛ n Mu’ab yudes-dd aṭṭas u řɣar nnes yiweḍ-dd deɣya.  
\v 17 Cetcam xas, marra kenniw i d as dd-innḍen u marra inni issnen isem nnes. Inim: ‘Mammec igga yarreẓ uzeǧaḍ \add n ṣṣulṭa\add* ijehden, taseṭṭa nni iṣebḥen aṭṭas?’  
\v 18 Hwa-dd zeg wemcan nnem yuɛřan, qqim deg \add ict n jjihet n\add* ufadi, cem tenni \add din\add* izeddɣen, yeǧis n Dibun, maɣar amteḥḥay n Mu’ab ihejjem-dd xam, aqa yareddeǧ lqelɛat nnem.  
\v 19 Beddet ɣar webrid uca xzaret, cem tenni izeddɣen di Ɛaruɛir! Seqsat aryaz nni yarewřen, tamɣart nni inejmen, ini: ‘Min imsaren?’  
\v 20 Innefḍeḥ Mu’ab, minzi ittwařbez. Cetca, sɣuyy, ejj ad ssnen di Arnun aqa Mu’ab ittwaxarreb. \x ◘ \xo 48:20 \xt Ica. 16:7\x*  
\v 21 Yiweḍ-dd řḥukm x řwaṭa, x Ḥulun, x Yaḥṣa, x Mayfaɛat,  
\v 22 x Dibun, x Nabu, x Bayt-Dablatayim,  
\v 23 x Qaryatayim, x Bayt-Jamul, x Bayt-Maɛun,  
\v 24 x Qaryut u x Buṣra, u x marra tineddam n temmurt n Mu’ab, tinni iggʷejen d tinni yudsen.  
\v 25 Ittwaqḍeɛ yicc n Mu’ab, yareẓ uɣiř nnes, iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 26 “Scarem t maɣar netta tuɣa ittɛeffar ḍidd i SIDI s wawařen n ukebbar. Ad iwḍa Mu’ab deg iɛuqqan n yixef nnes uca ad idweř simant nnes i tseḍḥact.  
\v 27 Niɣ ma war tuɣi Israil i tseḍḥact i cek? Ma ṭṭfen t zeɛma jar iceffaren aqa cek tᵉttɛeyyabed t am tessenhezzid azeǧif meřmi ma iwḍa ac-dd x yiřes?  
\v 28 Ffɣem zi tneddam, zedɣem di řejruf, \add kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n Mu’ab! Ggem am tedbirt i iggin řɛucc x ujemmaḍ n uqemmum n yefri ittfan.  
\v 29 Neccin nesřa x nnfaxet n Mu’ab, dayes nnfaxet aṭṭas: nnfaxet nnes, aɛeffar nnes d wuř nnes ittuɛřan.” \x ◘ \xo 48:29 \xt Ica. 16:6\x*   
\m
\v 30 “Necc ssneɣ zzɛamet nnes, iqqar SIDI, uřa d řɣecc n řhard nnes. Nitni war tteggen min qqaren.  
\v 31 X uya i ɣa wteɣ agejdur x Mu’ab, x marra Mu’ab ad sɣuyeɣ, ad zehharen x iryazen n Qir-Ḥaris.  
\v 32 S imeṭṭawen aṭṭas x imeṭṭawen n Yaɛzir ad xam ruɣ, \add a\add* cem tzayart n Sibma. Řefruɛ nnem ɛdun řebḥar, iwḍen-dd ař řebḥar n Jaɛzir. Yusa-dd \add maca\add* umteḥḥay ihjem x tini nnem n unebdu uřa x řɣiǧet nnem n uḍiř.  
\v 33 Truḥ řefraḥet d wercaq zi temmurt isseɣ̮mayen, zi temmurt n Mu’ab, minzi ssbeddeɣ binu zi teysirin n uḍiř. War ttɣimin ad ddzen ɛad aḍiř s usřiwřew. Asřiwřew? Cfa usřiwřew. \x ◘ \xo 48:33 \xt Ica. 16:10\x*  
\v 34 Zi ssibbet n tɣuyyit n Ḥacbun ař Aliɛala, ař Yahaṣ, \add wah, nitni\add* tteggen ad sřen tmijja nsen zi Ṣuɛar ař Ḥurunayim, taɛejmit \add nni\add* n třata n iseggʷusa. Maɣar ɛad aman n Nimrim ad dewřen d iyermamen ittwaxarrben. \x ◘ \xo 48:34 \xt Ica. 15:5, 6\x*  
\v 35 Wenni iqeddmen taɣarṣt di řegɛudi d wenni ittawyen tiwhibin n řebxur i irebbiten nnes, ad t arreɣ ad ibedd \add zi man aya\add* di Mu’ab, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 36 “X uya ittɛeffar wuř inu x Mu’ab am temja, uř inu ittɛeffar x yeryazen n Qir-Ḥaris am yict n temja, minzi afeyyeḍ nni ikseb, aqa iweddar.  
\v 37 Qaɛ izeǧifen d iqeccura u qaɛ timira ttwaqeḍɛent, di marra ifassen nsen \add aqa\add* iqessiten \add n wecḍan\add* u i tejɛinna nsen \add aqa\add* taxancet \add n wecḍan\add*. \x ◘ \xo 48:37 \xt Ica. 15:2, 3; Irm. 47:5\x*  
\v 38 X marra tizeɣwin n Mu’ab u x marra wazzayen nnes, \add wah,\add* mani ma \add aqa din\add* tɣuyyit n wecḍan, maɣar Necc arẓiɣ Mu’ab am yict n řqecɛet war dayes bu arḍa \add ɛad\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 39 Mammec ittwawwet Mu’ab, mammec ssɣuyyun nitni. Mammec \add i d asen d\add* yarra Mu’ab s weɛrur s useḍḥi! Mu’ab idweř d ict n řqecɛet n ustehzi d ijj n umedya n usnexřiɛ i marra inni d as dd-innḍen.”   
\m
\v 40 “Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, am yijj n ugider ad iḥewwem netta uca ad ibezzeɛ afriwen nnes tiwa n Mu’ab.\x ◘ \xo 48:40 \xt Irm. 4:13\x*  
\v 41 Qaryut ṭṭfen t uca ɣeřben x lqelɛat \add deg idurar\add*. \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři wuř n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt n Mu’ab am wuř n ict n temɣart ittarun.  
\v 42 Mu’ab ad ittwareddeǧ ařami war ittiři \add ɛad\add* d řgens maɣar issemɣar ixef nnes x SIDI.  
\v 43 Tiggʷudi d wenday d řfex ad xak iřin, \add a\add* cek wenni izeddɣen di Mu’ab, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 44 Wenni i ɣa yarewřen zi tiggʷudi, ad iwḍa di tesraft, u wenni dd ɣa igeɛɛden zi tesraft, ad innaɣ di řfex, maɣar Necc ad awyeɣ x Mu’ab aseggʷas n wexřaf nnes, iqqar SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 45 “Di tiři n Ḥacbun qqimen imarwařen ttbeddan břa jjehd, maɣar timessi teffeɣ-dd zi Ḥacbun, ijj n uhaduq zi Siḥun, uca wanita icca lḥenkat n \add uzeǧif\add* Mu’ab d aceqquf n marra ayt n bu-řexcunet.\x ◘ \xo 48:45 \xt Řxř. 21:28\x*  
\v 46 Uct xak, Mu’ab, aqa ixsar řgens n Kamuc, maɣar iḥenjiren nnec ttwanedhen di tmeḥbast uca uřa d yessic ttwaḥebbsen.  
\v 47 Deg uneggar n wussan ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n Mu’ab!’, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” Ař danita \add iǧa wawař i yurin x\add* řḥukm x Mu’ab.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 49
\m
\v 1 \bd X ayt n Ɛammun\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ma Israil war ɣares bu iḥenjiren? Ma war ɣares bu awrit? Mayemmi \add xenni\add* iṭṭef ujeǧid nwem \add tammurt n\add* Jad d řwart i yixef nnes u mayemmi izeddeɣ řgens nnes di tneddam \add n Jad\add*? \x ◘ \xo 49:1 \xt Ɛam. 1:13\x*  
\v 2 S uya, xzar, ussan ad dd-asen, ammu i iqqar SIDI, ad jjeɣ ad ttwasřen iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add* x \add tendint n\add* Rabba n ayt n Ɛammun. Ad tedweř \add tendint\add* d ict n řgeɛɛdet n řxarbet u tineddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen ad tent qqden s tmessi. Israil ad iwart \add ɛawed\add* min zzayes kksen d řwart, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.\x ◘ \xo 49:2 \xt Ɛam. 1:14\x*  
\v 3 Ru, \add a\add* Ḥacbun, maɣar \add tandint n\add* Ɛay tᵉttwareddeǧ, sɣuyyent, \add a kennint\add* yessis n Rabba, ḥezzment s txuncay \add n wecḍan\add*, ceḍnent uca uyurent ɣar da d diha ɣar uɣezdis n icbaren, maɣar ajeǧid nwem, \add Milkum\add*, ad ittwandeh di lmenfa, ikehhanen nnes ak-d řḥukkam nnes.’” \x ◘ \xo 49:3 \xt Ica. 32:12; Irm. 4:8; 6:26; 48:7 \x*   
\m
\v 4 “Mecḥař tᵉttfeyyced s řewḍat n teɣzurin nnem, s ufeyyeḍ n řewḍa nnem n teɣzurt, \add a cem\add* yeǧis ikfaren, tenni ittcařan x wagřa nnes, \add teqqar:\add* ‘Wi dd ɣari i ɣa iqarrben?’ \x ◘ \xo 49:4 \xt Irm. 21:13; 48:7\x*  
\v 5 Xzar, ad xam dd-ɣeḍreɣ tiggʷudi zi marra iɣezdisen nnem, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat. Kenniw ad tᵉttwaɛarrnem, kuř ijj nican ɣar zzat, uca war din uřa d ijjen wenni i ɣa issmunen inni yarewřen.  
\v 6 \add Maca\add* awarni as ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n ayt n Ɛammun, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \bd X Idum\bd*  
\m “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Ma war teǧi ɛad tiɣit di Tiyman? Ma ibḍeř ccwar n imiɣisen? Ma tḍeyyeɛ tiɣit nsen? \x ◘ \xo 49:7 \xt Ɛub. 8\x*  
\v 8 Arewřem, dewřem, ffarem deg imucan yuǧɣen, \add kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n Dadan, maɣar Necc ad xas awyeɣ aḍeyyeɛ n Ɛisu, řweqt nni di ad t ɛaqbeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 49:8 \xt Irm. 25:23\x*  
\v 9 Mařa usin-dd ɣarek imeřqaḍ n uḍiř, ma \add xenni\add* war ttejjin ca awarni asen? Mařa \add usin-dd\add* ixewwanen s ǧiřet, ma xenni war ttḍeyyiɛen ař ɣa jjiwnen? \x ◘ \xo 49:9 \xt Ɛub. 5\x*  
\v 10 Necc maca qeccareɣ \add tammurt n\add* Ɛisu, ɛarriɣ x imucan nnes innuffaren ařami war izemmar \add ɛad\add* ad innuffar. Tarwa nnes ttwareddǧen, uřa d aytmas d jjiran nnes, aqa netta war iǧi ɛad.  
\v 11 Ejj iyujiřen nnec, Necc ad ten ḥḍiɣ ad qqimen ddaren, tijjař nnec ejj i-tent ad xafi ttecřent.’  
\v 12 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, inni war t issdiheǧen ad swen zi řkas, ad zzayes swen. U cek \add wenni t issdaheǧen\add*, ma ad tᵉttwabarrid? War tᵉttwabarrid ca ɛemmarṣ, ad zzayes teswed s uɣiř!  
\v 13 Maɣar Necc jjuǧeɣ ɣar ixef inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, aqa Buṣra ad idweř d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d řḥegra, uřa d ict n řxirbet d nneɛřet, uca marra tineddam nnes ad dewřent d řxirbat i řebda.’”   
\m
\v 14 “Necc sřiɣ ijj n řexbar zi SIDI, aqa ittwassekk-dd ijj n ureqqas jar řegnus ḥima ad yini: ‘Smunem, sgeɛɛdem xas, kkarem ɣar umenɣi!’ \x ◘ \xo 49:14 \xt Ɛub. 1\x*  
\v 15 Minzi xzar, Necc ssemẓiyeɣ cek jar řegnus, tᵉttwasseḥqared jar iwdan.  
\v 16 Řeḥkamet nnec issaggʷaden tɣarr i cek uřa d zzɛamet n wuř nnec, \add a cek\add* wenni izeddɣen deg ifeǧiqen n řejruf, wenni ittcebbaren di tqiccet n tewririn! Waxxa teggid řɛucc nnec sennej qaɛ am t ittegg ugider, Necc ad cek dd-ɣeḍřeɣ ssenni, iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 49:16 \xt Irm. 48:29\x*  
\v 17 Idum ad idweř d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ. Kuř ijj wenni dd as i ɣa ikken, ad innexřeɛ u ad iṣeffar \add s wesrubi\add* x marra jjɛayef nnes. \x ◘ \xo 49:17 \xt Irm. 50:13\x*  
\v 18 Am ɣar uneqřeb n Sadum d Ɛamurra d dcurat nnes yudsen, iqqar SIDI, war dinni izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj u war dayes ittɣimi \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj n mmis n bnadem \add d abarrani\add*. \x ◘ \xo 49:18 \xt Amz. 19:25; Irm. 50:40; Ɛam. 4:11\x*  
\v 19 Xzar, am yijj n wayrad ad dd-igeɛɛed zi cbarq iqqnen n L’Urdun ḍidd i tzeddiɣt ijehden, xenni deg wermac n wabřiwen ad t arreɣ ad azzeř ssenni, u wenni umi farzeɣ, ad xas t areccḥeɣ. Maɣar man wen iǧan am Necc, man wen xafi i ɣa iřaɣan i ddeɛwet? Man wen d ameksaw wenni i ɣa iqqimen zzati ibedd? \x ◘ \xo 49:19 \xt Ayub 41:2; Irm. 12:5; 50:44\x*  
\v 20 S uya, sřem i ucawar n SIDI nni iqḍeɛ x Idum, u \add sřem\add* i inwayen nni ixarreṣ x imezdaɣ n Tayman: ‘S tidett, inni imeẓyanen aṭṭas zeg wuǧi ad ten jarren, s tidett, tazeddiɣt nsen ad tᵉttwassnexřeɛ!’ \x ◘ \xo 49:20 \xt Irm. 50:45\x*  
\v 21 Tammurt tᵉttenhezza s řḥess n uweṭṭu nsen, s tɣuyyit i zi ɣa ittwaseř řḥess nnes ař Řebḥar n Telga.  
\v 22 Xzar, ittgeɛɛad am yijj n ugider \add ɣar ujenna\add*, itteḥrara, ittbezzaɛ afriwen nnes tiwa n Buṣra. \bd Deg wass nni\bd* ad yiři wuř n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt n Idum am wuř n ict n temɣart s řeḥriq n tarwa.” \x ◘ \xo 49:22 \xt Irm. 48:40,41\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 \bd X Dimacq\bd*  
\m “Ḥamat d Arfad seḍḥan, maɣar nitni sřin i wareqqas d aɛeffan, fecřen. Ɣar řebḥar tᵉttwaf řeḥṣaret, bnadem war izemmar ad yarsa \add din\add*.\x ◘ \xo 49:23 \xt Ica. 17:1\x*  
\v 24 Tarxu \add tendint\add* n Dimacq, tenneqřeb, maḥend ad tᵉṭṭef di tarewřa. Imneɛ i-tt uqdiddes. Řeḥṣaret d řewjeɛ am n ict temɣart ittarwen ṭṭfen tt. \x ◘ \xo 49:24 \xt Irm. 4:31; 6:24; 30:6\x*  
\v 25 Tandint icennɛen, ma war teggi am tenni ittwajjen, tandint n řefraḥet inu?  
\v 26 S uya ad wḍan iḥudriyyen nnes deg wazzayen u marra iɛeskariyyen ad ttwaseɣden \bd deg wass nni\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat.  
\v 27 Necc ad ssarɣeɣ timessi di řḥiḍ n Dimacq, ad tecc řeqṣur n Binhadad.” \x ◘ \xo 49:27 \xt Ɛam. 1:4, 14\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 \bd X Weɛraben\bd*  
\m \bd X Qidar d tgelditin n Ḥaṣur\bd* nni iɣřeb Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil.  
\m “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Kkarem uca hejmem x Qidar uca areddǧem ayt n ccarq.  
\v 29 Nitni ad asen kksen iqiḍan nsen d wuǧi nsen, tijartiřin n uqiḍan nsen d marra řqecc nsen. Uca uřa d iřeɣman nsen ad ten awyen akidsen. Ad xasen sɣuyen: Asiggʷed mani ma!  
\v 30 Arewřem, beɛɛdem, ffarem deg imucan yuǧɣen, \add kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n Ḥaṣur, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, maɣar Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, iqḍeɛ xawem acawar uca ixarreṣ deg ijj n wenway xawem.  
\v 31 Kkarem, geɛɛdem x ijj n řgens nni izeddɣen di řhudnet u di řaman, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, \add ijj n řgens\add* war ɣares bu tewwura uřa d zzenkrun, wenni izeddɣen weḥḥdes.  
\v 32 Iřeɣman nsen ad ttwaḥewwsen uca abarru n tḥimriwin nsen n řmař ad ttwacarent u Necc ad ten zuzzareɣ ɣar marra iɣezdisen n usemmiḍ, \add marra\add* inni ittḥeffan \add acuwwaf\add* ɣar ṭṭrufa, . Necc ad xasen dd-awyeɣ aḍeyyeɛ zi marra iɣezdisen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 49:32 \xt Lawi 19:27; 21:5; Irm. 9:25; 25:23. \x*  
\v 33 Haṣur ad idweř d tazeddiɣt i wuccanen n řexřa, ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen i řebda. War dayes izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijjen uca uřa d ijj n mmis n bnadem ad din iqqim \add ɛad\add* am ubarrani.’” \x ◘ \xo 49:33 \xt Irm. 9:10; 10:22\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 34 \bd X Ɛilam\bd*  
\m Awař n SIDI i unabi Irmiya x Ɛilam, deg umezwaru n tgelda n Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, inna:  
\v 35 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Xzar, Necc ad arẓeɣ řqews n Ɛilam, amezwaru n tzemmar nsen n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt.  
\v 36 Necc ad dd-ssehwiɣ x Ɛilam arebɛa n isemmiḍen zi arebɛa n tɣemmura n ujenna u ɣar marra tiɣemmura n isemmiḍen ad ten zuzzareɣ. War ittiři bu řgens mani war dd-ttisen inni x uẓẓřen zi Ɛilam.  
\v 37 Necc ad ssnexřɛeɣ \add ayt n\add* Ɛilam zzat i řɛedyan nsen u zzat i yinni yarezzun tudart nsen. Necc ad dd-ɣeḍřeɣ řɣar xasen, řḥaduq n weɣḍab inu, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI. Necc ad asen sseḍfareɣ ssif ař ten teḥḥiɣ.  
\v 38 Necc ad ssbeddeɣ řɛarc inu di Ɛilam uca ad teḥḥiɣ ajeǧid d řḥukkam ssenni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 39 Deg uneggar n wussan ad ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n Ɛilam \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.’” \x ◘ \xo 49:39 \xt Irm. 48:47\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 50
\s1 X Babil  
\m
\v 1 Awař nni issiweř SIDI \bd x Babil, x temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen\bd*, s ufus n unabi Irmiya.   
\m
\v 2 “Barrḥem jar řegnus, jjem ad as sřen, sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant, jjem ad as sřem, war \add tt\add* snuffaram. Inim: ‘\add Tandint n\add* Babil tᵉttwaṭṭef, Bil iseḍḥa, Marudax aqa yarẓa, řexyařat nnes n l’aṣnam ttwabarqen, imeyḍa n \add l’aṣnam nnes\add* ttwařebzen!’ \x ◘ \xo 50:2 \xt Ica. 46:1; Irm. 51:44\x*  
\v 3 Maɣar ihjem-dd xas ijj n řgens zi ccamal, ad yarr tammurt nnes d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ, war dayes izeddeɣ ɛad uřa d ijj, zi bnadem ař řmař arewřen, ffɣen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 4 “Deg wussan nni u di řweqt nni, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, ad dd-asen ayt n Israil munen ak-d ayt n Yahuda. Ad uyuren am ttrun, ad arzun x SIDI, AREBBI nsen.  
\v 5 X Ṣihyun ad sseqsan, aqa ɣar dinni i nḍaren tiṭṭawin nsen. Nitni ad dd-asen uca ad dd-mmarenyen ɣar SIDI s ijj n Řɛahd ittduman nni war ittwattun.  
\v 6 Tuɣa řgens inu d uǧi iweddaren, imeksawen nsen ssuffɣen tent x webrid x idurar ikfaren. Nitni uyurent zeg wedrar ař tewrirt, ttunt amcan n arraḥet nsent.  
\v 7 Marra wi tent yufin, ccin tent uca iɣrimen nsent nnan: ‘Neccin war d aneɣ ittars ḥed, maɣar nitenti xḍant ak-d SIDI, ak-d tzeddiɣt n tsegda, ak-d řayas n řejdud nsent \add ḍidd i\add* SIDI.’ \x ◘ \xo 50:7 \xt Irm. 31:23\x*  
\v 8 Arwřem zi Babil, ffɣem zi temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen, iřim am yiɣayḍen ittizwaren i wuǧi!” \x ◘ \xo 50:8 \xt Ica. 48:20; Irm. 51:6; Asa. 18:4\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Maɣar xzar, Necc simant inu ad dd-ssḥarrceɣ x Babil ijj n ubarru n řegnus imeqqranen zi temmurt n ccamal. Nitni ad ssbedden ixef nsen ḍidd nnes. Ssenni ad tᵉttwaṭṭef \add tandint n Babil\add*. Fřitcat nsen am ayt n bu-teɣřuḍt imeḥḍen, uřa d ict zzaysent ɛemmarṣ war dd-tɛiqqib texwa.  
\v 10 \add Tammurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen ad tedweř d takeccaḍt, marra inni tt i ɣa ikeccḍen, ad jjiwnen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 11 Minzi kenniw tfarḥem, aqa tneggzem s řefraḥet, \add a kenniw\add* inni ikeccḍen tasɣart inu. Kenniw tnedwem am tɛejmiyyin di ddemnet u tessneḥniḥem am \add yeysan\add* ijehden.  
\v 12 Tseḍḥa yemmatwem, tenni kenniw i dd-yurwen, aqa iřqef i-tt useḥcem. Xzar, nettat d taneggarut n řegnus: \add mɣir\add* d řexřa d řekḥeḍ d tanezruft.  
\v 13 Zi ssibbet n uduqqez n weɣḍab n SIDI ad teqqim \add tendint n Babil\add* war tᵉttwazeddeɣ \add ɛad\add*, ad tedweř d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen. Marra wi ɣa iɛdun x Babil ad innexřeɛ, ad iṣeffar \add s uɛeyyeb\add* x marra jjɛayef nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 50:13 \xt Irm. 49:17\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Seddem ixef nwem i umenɣi ak-d Babil ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes, marra inni imeḥḍen řqews, maɣar nettat texḍa ak-d SIDI.  
\v 15 Sɣuyyem xas zi marra iɣezdisen. Aqa nettat tsellem ixef nnes. Wḍan lburjat nnes, hedmen řeḥyuḍ nnes, maɣar wa d nneqmet n SIDI. Xeřfem zzayes, ggem zzayes am mammec i tegga nettat. \x ◘ \xo 50:15 \xt Asa. 18:6\x*  
\v 16 Kksem azarraɛ zi Babil d wenni iṭṭfen amjar di řweqt n tmejra! Zi ssibbet n ssif iqesḥen ad ɛeqben nitni, kuř ijj ɣar řgens nnes, uca ad arewřen, kuř ijj ɣar temmurt nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 “Israil \add am\add* ijjen zeg wuǧi i xef uẓẓřen, tenni x ɛerfen wayraden. Ɣar umezwar isarḍ i-tt ujeǧid n Accur, ɣar uneggar iddez as Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, iɣsan nnes.  
\v 18 S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Xzar, Necc ad xeřfeɣ zeg ujeǧid n Babil d temmurt nnes, am mammec xeřfeɣ zeg ujeǧid n Accur. \x ◘ \xo 50:18 \xt 2 Ij. 19:35, 37; Ica. 37:36, 38\x*  
\v 19 Israil \add maca\add* ad t-i-dd-arreɣ ɣar tzeddiɣt nnes u netta ad yarwes x Karmal d Bacan, ad tejjawen řeɛmar nnes di temmurt n idurar n Ifrayim d Jilɛad.’”   
\m
\v 20 “Deg wussan nni u di řweqt nni, iqqar SIDI, ad arzun x řɛib n Israil, \add maca\add* war ittiři, u x ddnub n Yahuda, \add maca\add* war ten ttifen, minzi inni i dd ɣa arreɣ ad qqimen, Necc ad asen ɣfareɣ.   
\m
\v 21 Geɛɛed ḍidd i temmurt n Maratayim, \add ‘tammurt n Uɣewweɣ Tnayen n Tseqqar’\add*, u ḍidd i imezdaɣ n Faqud, \add ‘tandint n Wexřef’\add*. Areddeǧ u ḥarrem awarni asen marra \add i uteḥḥi\add*, \add ammu\add* i iqqar SIDI, u egg ɛlaḥsab marra minzi cek umureɣ.”   
\m
\v 22 “\add Aqa da, ittwaseř\add* lharaj n umenɣi di temmurt, ict n lmuṣiba tameqqrant.  
\v 23 Mammec ittwaqess u ittwarẓ wefḍis n marra ddunect! Mammec idweř Babil d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ jar řegnus!  
\v 24 Necc ggiɣ am, \add a, tandint n\add* Babil, ijj n řfex uca tejjid ixef nnem ad cem ggen di řeḥbes, waxxa war tucid. Ufin d ṭṭfen uřa d cem, maɣar cem tuɣa tᵉttemɛarrid ak-d SIDI.  
\v 25 SIDI yarzem axxam nnes n txubay uca issuffeɣ-dd dduzan n wesxeḍ nnes, maɣar ta d ict n řxedmet i Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, di temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen.  
\v 26 Azzřem ɣares zi ṭṭarf \add n temmurt\add*, arzmem řexzayen nnes, nḍarem marra x iɛurricen yuɛřan uca ḥarrmem ten \add i uteḥḥi\add*, ḥḍam mliḥ maḥend war zzayes ittɣimi walu.  
\v 27 Nɣem marra ifunasen nnes imeẓyanen s ssif, sehwam ten-dd ɣar tɣarṣt. Uct xasen, maɣar ass nsen yiweḍ-dd, tasaɛɛet n uɛaqeb nsen!  
\v 28 \add Aqa da\add* ijj n řḥess n imarwařen u n yinni inejmen zi temmurt n Babil maḥend ad barrḥen axřaf n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, di Ṣihyun, axřaf di ṭṭweɛ n Zzawect nnes Tameqqrant.”   
\m
\v 29 “Řaɣam i ayt n řqews ɣar Babil, marra inni ijebbden řqews! Ḥṣarem tandint zi marra iɣezdisen, ḥḍam maḥend uřa d ijjen ad injem. Xeřfem tt ɛlaḥsab timegga nnes, ggem zzayes ɛlaḥsab marra min tegga, maɣar nettat tuɣa teffucceḥ ak-d SIDI, ak-d Umqeddes n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 50:29 \xt Asa. 18:6, 7\x*  
\v 30 S uya ad wḍan iḥudriyyen nnes deg wazzayen d marra iɛeskariyyen nnes ad ttwassusmen \bd deg wass nni\bd*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat. \x ◘ \xo 50:30 \xt Irm. 49:26\x*  
\v 31 Xzar, Necc ad ɣarem kkareɣ, \add a cem\add* tenni iffuccḥen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Sidi inu, SIDI n řɛeskarat, minzi ass nnem yiweḍ-dd, tsaɛɛet nni di cem i ɣa xeǧṣeɣ.  
\v 32 Xenni wenni iffuccḥen ad inqarḍ, ad iwḍa, uca uřa d ijj war t issbeddi. Necc ad qqdeɣ timessi di tneddam nnes nni i ɣa iccen marra min d asent-i-dd innḍen.”   
\m
\v 33 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Ttwaḥṣaren ayt n Israil \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ayt n Yahuda. Marra inni ten iḥebbsen, ṭṭfen ten, ugin ad jjen ad asen arxun.  
\v 34 \add Maca\add* Amefdi nsen ijhed, SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes. Netta ggur ad iwwet x ddeɛwet nsen ḥima ad igg řhudnet i temmurt u ḥima ad issarjij imezdaɣ n Babil.’”   
\m
\v 35 “Ssif x Ikaldaniyyen, iqqar SIDI, u x imezdaɣ n Babil, x řḥukkam nnes u x imiɣisen nnes.  
\v 36 Ssif x ayt n bu-ixarriqen maḥend ad dewřen d ibuhařiyyen, ssif x ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnes maḥend ad ttwarẓen.  
\v 37 Ssif x yeysan nnes u x ikarruten nnes u x ubarru n ɛřam kuř ibarraniyyen \add nni iǧan\add* di řwesṭ nnes, maḥend ad dewřen am temɣarin. Ssif x řeknuz nnes maḥend ad ttwacaren.  
\v 38 Řekḥeḍ x waman nnes maḥend ad aẓɣen, maɣar d ict n temmurt teccur s řexyařat ineqcen uca nitni dewřen d ibuhařiyyen zi nnɛawat n l’aṣnam.  
\v 39 S uya ad \add din\add* zedɣen řewḥuc n řexřa ak-d yifisen uca uřa d yessis n nnɛamet ad zedɣent din. I řebda war ittɣimi din uřa d ijj u war \add dayes\add* zeddɣen ɛad zi jjiř ař jjiř. \x ◘ \xo 50:39 \xt [Ica. 13:20]\x*  
\v 40 Am mammec tuɣa issneqřeb AREBBI Sadum d Ɛamurra d dcurat nnes yudsen, \add ammu\add* war dinni izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj u war dayes ittɣimi \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj n mmis n bnadem \add d abarrani\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 50:40 \xt Amz. 19:25; Irm. 49:18\x*   
\m
\v 41 “Xzar, ijj n řgens ad dd-yas zi ccamal, ijj n řgens d ameqqran, uca aṭṭas n ijeǧiden ad ttwaɛarren ad faqen zi tɣemmura n temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 50:41 \xt Irm. 6:22,30\x*  
\v 42 Nitni mennɛen di řqews d fřitca. Nitni ttewɛaren, war arreḥemen. Tmijja nsen am zzhir n řebḥar, nitni nnayen x yeysan. Aqa ttḥezzamen ɣar umenɣi akidem, \add a\add* yeǧis n Babil!  
\v 43 Isřa ujeǧid n Babil řexbar xasen uca dewřen as ifassen ṭṭsen. Teṭṭef i-t i-dd tiggʷudi, \add uřa d\add* řeḥriq am n ict n temɣart ittarwen. \x ◘ \xo 50:43 \xt Irm. 49:24\x*  
\v 44 Xzar, am yijj n wayrad ad dd-igeɛɛed zi cbarq iqqnen n L’Urdun, \add ammu i ɣa igeɛɛed\add* ḍidd i tzeddiɣt ijehden, maɣar deg wermac n wabřiwen ad ten arreɣ ad azzřen ssenni, u wenni umi farzeɣ, ad xas t areccḥeɣ. Maɣar man wen iǧan am Necc, man wen xafi i dd ɣa iřaɣan i ddeɛwet? Man wen d ameksaw wenni i ɣa iqqimen zzati ibedd? \x ◘ \xo 50:44 \xt Ayub 41:2; Irm. 49:19, 22\x*  
\v 45 S uya, sřem i ucawar n SIDI nni iqḍeɛ x Babil u \add sřem\add* i inwayen nnes nni ixarreṣ x temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen: ‘S tidett, inni imeẓyanen aṭṭas zeg wuǧi ad ten jarren, s tidett, tazeddiɣt nsen ad tᵉttwassnexřeɛ!’ \x ◘ \xo 50:45 \xt Irm. 49:20\x*  
\v 46 Tammurt tᵉttenhezza zi řḥess n uṭeffu n Babil uca aɣuyyi nnes ittwaseř ɣar řegnus.” \x ◘ \xo 50:46 \xt Irm. 49:21\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 51
\m
\v 1 “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad dd-ssekkareɣ ijj n buḥbeř n wareddeǧ x Babil u x yinni din izeddɣen deg wuř n iɣrimen inu. \x ◘ \xo 51:1 \xt Irm. 4:11\x*  
\v 2 Necc ad ssekkeɣ ibarraniyyen ɣar Babil, ad tt zuzzaren uca ad farḍen tammurt nnes, minzi deg wass n řɣar ad bedden arendad nnes ɣar marra iɣezdisen. \x ◘ \xo 51:2 \xt Irm. 4:11; 15:7\x*  
\v 3 Ejj amjebbad n řqews ad imḥeḍ řqews nnes ḍidd n wenni imeḥḍen \add řqews\add* u ḍidd n wenni issgeɛɛaden ixef nnes deg werruḍ nnes n wuzzař. War ttḥiwiřem x iḥudriyyen nnes, ḥarrmem marra řɛeskar nnes \add i uteḥḥi\add*.  
\v 4 Inni ittwanɣen wḍan di temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen, u inni ittwassxarrqen aqa aten x ibriden nnes.’” \x ◘ \xo 51:4 \xt Irm. 49:26\x*  
\v 5 “Maɣar Israil d Yahuda war ttwajjen d tajjač zi AREBBI nsen, zi SIDI n řɛeskarat, minzi tammurt n \add Ikaldaniyyen\add* teccur s umarwas ɣar Umqeddas n Israil.”   
\b  
\m
\v 6 “Arewřem zi Babil, ejj ad issenjem kuř ijj tudart nnes, war ttejjim ad ttwassbekkmem \add i řebda\add* s řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, maɣar ta d řweqt n wexřaf n SIDI, Netta ad zzayes ixřef min tesdaheǧ.” \x ◘ \xo 51:6 \xt Irm. 50:8, 15, 28; Asa. 18:4\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Babil tuɣa-tt d ijj n řkas n wureɣ deg ufus n SIDI, iscar marra tammurt. Zi binu nnes swin marra řegnus, x uya iffeɣ řeɛqeř i řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 51:7 \xt Asa. 18\x*  
\v 8 Deɣya tewḍa \add tendint n\add* Babil u tᵉttwahdem. Wtem xas agejdur, awyem as-dd balsam i řeḥriq nnes, ad taɣ ad tᵉttwassgenfa.” \x ◘ \xo 51:8 \xt Ica. 21:9; Irm. 8:22; Asa. 14:8; 18:2\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Neccin nexs ad nawi agenfu i Babil, maca war ɣares agenfu. Jjem \add tandint nni\add*, u ejj kuř ijj zzayneɣ ad iraḥ ɣar temmurt nnes, maɣar řḥukm xas yiweḍ ař ajenna, igeɛɛed ař iseynuten.”\x ◘ \xo 51:9 \xt Irm. 46:11\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 “SIDI issiweḍ-dd řmuɛṣiyyet nneɣ \add ɣar tfawt\add*. Asem-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nɛawed di Ṣihyun min igga SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Sqeḍɛem fřitcat, ṭṭfem tiseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add*. SIDI issekkar-dd buḥbeř n ijeǧiden n Maday, minzi Netta iɛewweř ad ihdem Babil, maɣar wa d axřaf n SIDI, axřaf i Zzawect nnes Tameqqrant. \x ◘ \xo 51:11 \xt Irm. 46:4; 50:28\x*  
\v 12 Sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant x řeḥyuḍ n Babil, zeyyarem taɛessast, sbeddem iɛessasen, ggem řefxux, maɣar ɛlaḥsab aɛewweř n SIDI, ammu i ɣa yegg \add marra\add* min inna x imezdaɣ n Babil.  
\v 13 Cem, a tenni izeddɣen ɣar mani wesɛen waman, tenni ɣar iǧa waṭṭas n wagřa, qeṭṭu nnem yiweḍ-dd, aqa iccur řqedd n ṭṭmeɛ nnem.  
\v 14 Ijjuǧ SIDI n řɛeskarat ɣar yixef nnes: Waxxa Necc ccureɣ cem s iwdan am tmurɣi, ɛad ad xam dd-řaɣan s ict n tɣuyyit n usřiwřew!” \x ◘ \xo 51:14 \xt Ɛam. 6:8\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 15 “Netta igga tammurt s jjhed nnes, igga ddunect zi tiɣit nnes u ibezzeɛ ajenna s řefhamet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 51:15 \xt Amz. 1:1; Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2; Ica. 40:22; 44:24; 51:13; Irm. 10:12\x*  
\v 16 Řami ittejja tmijja nnes ad tt sřen, \add xenni tegga\add* am ucarcur n waman deg ujenna. Iseynuten issgeɛɛad i-ten zeg ineggura n ddunect, ittegg assamen ak-d wenẓar uca issekka-dd asemmiḍ zeg ixxamen nnes n txubay. \x ◘ \xo 51:16 \xt Irm. 10:13\x*  
\v 17 Kuř bnadem d agarruḍ, břa tussna, kuř amziř n wureɣ ittseḍḥa zi ssibbet n řexyař \add i igga\add*, maɣar řexyař nnes ifesyen d ixarriqen, war dayes \add iǧi\add* buḥbeř.  
\v 18 Aqa-tent d \add l’aṣnam\add* ibeṭṭřen, aqa atent d řeqcuɛ n tseḍḥact! Di řweqt n wexřaf nsent, ad fnant.”   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “Tasɣart n Yaɛqub war teǧi am \add tesɣart\add* nsent, minzi Netta d wenni iggin marra, uca Israil d taqbič n tesɣart nnes, aqa SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.”\x ◘ \xo 51:19 \xt Irm. 10:16\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 “Cek teggid ayi am yijj n ccaqur, řesnaḥ inu i umenɣi. Zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ řegnus, zzayek i ɣa ɣeḍřeɣ tigeldiwin. \x ◘ \xo 51:20 \xt Irm. 50:23\x*  
\v 21 Zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ ayis d wenni xas inyin u zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ akarru n umenɣi d wenni t ineddhen,  
\v 22 zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ aryaz d temɣart, zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ awessar d uḥuḍri u zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ abřiɣ d tebřiɣt,  
\v 23 zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ ameksaw d tḥimart nnes, zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ afeǧaḥ d zzayřet nnes \add ak-d iyenduzen\add*, u zzayek i ɣa řebzeɣ lwulat d imseyyaren \add n temmurt\add*,  
\v 24 \add maca\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem ad xeřfeɣ Necc zi Babil u zi marra imezdaɣ n \add temmurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen x marra řɣar i ggin di Ṣihyun, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 25 “Xzar, Necc ad kidek dd-řhiɣ, \add cek\add* adrar n Wareddeǧ, iqqar SIDI, cek d wenni yareddǧen marra tammurt. Necc ad xak dd-swiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu u ad cek sseqnunnyeɣ zi řejruf u ad cek ggeɣ d adrar icemmḍen. \x ◘ \xo 51:25 \xt 2 Ij. 23:13\x*  
\v 26 Ɛemmarṣ war zzayek ttawyen \add ɛad\add* aẓru i weẓru n teɣmart uřa d aẓru i dsusa, maɣar ad tdewřed i řxirbat i řebda, iqqar SIDI.”   
\m
\v 27 “Sgeɛɛdem taɛeǧant di temmurt, suḍem deg uyicc n icarri jar řegnus, farzem řegnus ḍidd nnes, řaɣam ḍidd nnes i tgeldiwin n Araraṭ, Minni d Ackanaz, ggem ijj n řɛeskar ḍidd nnes, jjem iysan ad ffɣen am \add ijj n weyřaf n tmuɣri\add* iṣarrḍen iqesḥen.  
\v 28 Farzem řegnus ḍidd nnes, ijeǧiden n Maday ak-d lwulat nnes d marra imseyyaren nnes, marra tammurt \add i x teǧa\add* ṣṣulṭa nnes.  
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* ad tenhezz temmurt uca ad tfarɣ s řeḥriq, minzi inwayen n SIDI bedden nican maḥend ad arren tammurt n Babil d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ, war dayes izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj.  
\v 30 Ayt n bu-teɣruḍt n Babil semḥen deg umenɣi, qqimen di lqelɛat nsen. Tefceř tzemmar nsen, nitni dewřen d timɣarin. Nitni qqden i tzeddiɣin nsen uca iɛumad nsen i ubelleɛ ttwarẓen. \x ◘ \xo 51:30 \xt Irm. 50:37\x*  
\v 31 Amsazzař \add nni\add* x umsazzař \add nneɣni\add* ittazzeř-dd, areqqas \add nni\add* x ureqqas \add nneɣni\add*, ḥima ad ḥajan i ujeǧid n Babil, aqa tandint nnes tᵉttwaṭṭef zi marra iɣezdisen,  
\v 32 aqa imucan n uẓekkwu ttwamenɛen, iyyaren n uɣanim ttwacemḍen s tmessi uca iɛeskariyyen ttwanhezzen.  
\v 33 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n Israil: Yeǧis n Babil tegga am unedrar, aqa tiweḍ-dd řweqt ḥima ad xas ɛefsen. Ɛad drus \add i iqqimen\add*, \add xenni\add* tiweḍ-dd řweqt n tmejra i nettat.”   
\m
\v 34 “Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, icca ayi, iřbez ayi, igga ayi d ijj n weqdiḥ ixwan, isarḍ ayi am řhaycet, iɛemmar aɛeddis nnes s řeḥzut inu uca yuẓẓeř xafi.  
\v 35 \add Ejj ad dd-yas\add* x Babil lɛunf i d ayi iggin u deg yinni \add i iǧan d\add* ddat inu, \add ammu i\add* teqqar tenni izeddɣen di Ṣihyun. ‘\add Ejj ad dd-asen\add* idammen inu x imezdaɣ n \add temmurt n\add* Ikaldaniyyen \add ammu i\add* teqqar Urcalim.”   
\m
\v 36 “S uya, ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Necc simant inu ttedɛiɣ ddɛawi nnem u ad zzayem xeřfeɣ. Necc ad ssiẓɣeɣ řebḥar nnes u ad jjeɣ tařa nnes ad taẓeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 51:36 \xt Irm. 50:38\x*  
\v 37 Babil ad tedweř \add mɣir\add* d řxirbat, ict n tzeddiɣt n wuccanen n řexřa, \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ d usemẓi maḥend war \add dayes ittɣimi\add* izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijjen.’”   
\m
\v 38 “Marra idsen ad zehharen am wayraden, ad ssmiɛɛriwen am wayraden imeẓyanen.  
\v 39 Xmi ɣa yiřin ḥman, ad ssarseɣ zzatsen tasessit nsen. Necc ad ten ssᵉscareɣ ař ɣa dewwxen uca ad ṭṭṣen iḍeṣ n řebda, ɛemmarṣ ad faqen \add ɛad\add*, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 40 Necc ad ten dd-ssehwiɣ am yizemrawen ɣar tɣarṣt, am yicarriyyen ak-d iɣayḍen.  
\v 41 Mammec ittwaṭṭef Cicak u \add mammec\add* ittwaṭṭef řɛezz n marra tammurt! Mammec tedweř \add tendint n\add* Babil d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ jar řegnus! \x ◘ \xo 51:41 \xt Ica. 13:19; Irm. 25:26\x*  
\v 42 Igeɛɛed-dd řebḥar x \add tendint n\add* Babil, s ubarru n řemwaj nnes tᵉttwadeř nettat.  
\v 43 Tineddam nnes dewřent d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ, \add tammurt tedweř d\add* tammurt yuẓɣen d tnezruft d ict n temmurt mani war izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj u mani war ittcuqi uřa d ijj n mmis n bnadem.  
\v 44 Necc ad xeřfeɣ zi Bil di Babil, ad kkseɣ zi tmijja nnes min tuɣa isarḍ. Řegnus war ɣares ttazzřen ɛad. Ɛad řḥiḍ n Babil ad iwḍa.”   
\m
\v 45 “Ffeɣ zzayes, \add a\add* řgens inu, ejj kuř ijj ad issenjem tudart nnes zi řḥaduq n weɣḍab n SIDI.  
\v 46 Mařa lla xenni ad ḍeɛfen wuřawen nwem uca ad ggʷeden zi řexbar nni i ɣa sřen di temmurt, maɣar ijj n řexbar ad ittwaseř deg ijj n useggʷas uca awarni i yijj n useggʷas \add nneɣni\add* ad dd-yas ijj n řexbar \add nneɣni\add*. Ad din yiři lɛunf di temmurt, \add ijj n\add* řḥakem ad dd-ikkar x ijj n řḥakem \add nneɣni\add*.”   
\m
\v 47 “S uyenni xzar, ad dd-asen wussan nni di ɣa xeřfeɣ zi Babil zi ssibbet n řexyařat ineqcen uca marra tammurt nnes ad tennefḍeḥ u marra inni ittwanɣen ad wḍan di řwesṭ nnes.  
\v 48 Ajenna d temmurt d marra min daysen ad sřiweřwen x Babil. Maɣar ad ɣares dd-asen imteḥḥayyen zi ccamal, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.  
\v 49 Am mammec tuɣa Babil d ssibbet n uweṭṭu n yinni ittwanɣen n Israil, \add ammu\add* i ɣa wḍan marra inni ittwanɣen zi marra tammurt ɣar \add tendint n\add* Babil.”   
\b  
\m
\v 50 “\add Kenniw\add*, inni inejmen i ssif, ffɣem, war sbeddam ixef nwem! Xemmem-dd zi řaggʷaj di SIDI u jjem Urcalim ad dd-tas ɣar řbař nwem. \f ◼ \fr 51:50 \ft \+fk ɣar řbař nwem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar wuřawen nwem’.\f*  
\v 51 Neccin nseḍḥa, maɣar nesřa x useḥqar, tezweɣ n řeḥya tedřa aɣembub nneɣ, maɣar ibarraniyyen geɛɛden x Tzawiyyin Iqeddsen n Taddart n SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 52 “S uya xzar, ad dd-asen wussan, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI, Necc ad xeřfeɣ zi řexyařat nnes ineqcen uca di marra tammurt nnes ad ttwazbaren inni ittwanɣen.  
\v 53 Waxxa mařa \add tandint n\add* Babil tgeɛɛed ař ajenna, waxxa tegga lbaraj nnes ijehden yuɛřan ař mani war yiwiḍ uřa d ijj, waxxa amenni ad ɣares dd-asen imteḥḥayen zzayi, \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 54 “\add Iffeɣ-dd\add* řḥess n tɣuyyit tameqqrant zi Babil, \add amecnaw\add* n ict n lmuṣiba d tameqqrant zi temmurt n Ikaldaniyyen.  
\v 55 Maɣar SIDI igga ad ixarreb Babil u ad iqḍa x ddriz nnes ameqqran, minzi řemwaj nsen ad zehharen am waman imeqqranen, ddriz n uzehhar nsen ad ittwaseř.  
\v 56 Minzi ad xas dd-asen imteḥḥayen, x Babil, uca ttwaḥebbsen ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnes, řeqwas nsen ad ttwarẓen, maɣar SIDI aqa-t d Arebbi n wexřaf, ad \add zzayes\add* ixřef nican.”   
\m
\v 57 “Ad ssᵉscareɣ řḥukkam nnes d imiɣisen nnes d lwulat nnes d imseyyaren nnes d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nnes uca nitni ad ɣeḍṣen deg yiḍeṣ n řebda u ɛemmarṣ ad faqen, \add ammu i\add* iqqar Ujeǧid, SIDI n řɛeskarat d Isem nnes.”  
\v 58 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: “Ad arren řeḥyuḍ imiriwen n Babil ad seḍḥan aṭṭas uca tiwwura nnes yuɛřan ad \add tent\add* qedden s tmessi. Řegnus ad aḥřen baṭeř u ccuɛub ssiḥřen ixef nsen di ṭṭweɛ n tmessi.”   
\b  
\m
\v 59 Awař nni yumur unabi Irmiya i Saraya, mmis n Niri-Yah, mmis n Maḥsiyya, umi wanita yuyur zi Ṣidqiya, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar Babil, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n řeḥkamet nnes. Tuɣa Saraya d řḥakem x řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.   
\m
\v 60 Irmiya yura marra řɣar i dd ɣa yasen x Babil deg ijj n wedlis ittwannḍen, marra awařen nni ittwarin x Babil.  
\v 61 \add Xenni\add* inna Irmiya i Saraya: “Xmi dd ɣa tased ɣar Babil, xzar mammec ɣa tegged ad tbarrḥed s marra awařen-a,  
\v 62 ad tinid: ‘\add A\add* SIDI, Cek simant nnec teqqared x wemcan-a belli ad \add zzayes\add* tekksed imezdaɣ, maḥend war dayes izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj, řa bnadem uřa d řmař, u belli \add amcan-a\add* ad yiři d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen!’  
\v 63 Xmi i ɣa tkemmřed zeg uɣari n wedlis ittwannḍen, ad ɣares teqqned ijj n weẓru, ad t tenḍared di řwesṭ n \add yeɣzar n\add* Lfuraṭ.  
\v 64 ad tinid: ‘Ammu i ɣa tɣebba \add tendint n\add* Babil u war tgiɛɛid \add ɛad\add* zi ssibbet n řɣar i xas dd-ssehwiɣ. Nitni ad sřawen.’” Ař da i yiwḍen wawařen n Irmiya. \x ◘ \xo 51:64 \xt Asa. 18:21\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 52
\s1 Actab n Urcalim  
\m
\v 1 Ṣidqiya \add tuɣa\add* ɣares waḥit u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem ḥiṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Ḥamutal, yeǧis n Irmiya zi Libna. \x ◘ \xo 52:1 \xt 2 Ij. 24:18\x*  
\v 2 Netta igga min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, nican am mammec t igga Yahuyaqim.  
\v 3 Maɣar axeyyeq n SIDI tuɣa yarsa x Urcalim d Yahuda, ařami ten inḍar zi zzat n wudem nnes. \add Xenni\add* tuɣa Ṣidqiya iɣewweɣ x ujeǧid n Babil.   
\m
\v 4 Deg useggʷas wiss tesɛa n řeḥkamet nnes, deg wass wiss ɛecra n uyur wiss ɛecra, iffeɣ-dd Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, s marra řɛeskar nnes ɣar Urcalim, Nitni nnḍen as-dd uca qewwaren as s jjehd ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 52:4 \xt 2 Ij. 25:1; Irm. 39:1\x*  
\v 5 Ammu i tᵉttwaḥsar tendint ař aseggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n ujeǧid Ṣidqiya.  
\v 6 Deg uyur wiss arebɛa, deg wass wiss tesɛa n uyur, řami idweř řaẓ imeqqar di tendint uca řgens n temmurt war ɣares iqqim bu weɣrum \add ɛad\add*,  
\v 7 aqa tᵉttwarẓ tendint u marra iɛeskariyyen arewřen, ffɣen s ǧiřet x webrid n tewwart \add i iǧan\add* jar tnayen n řeḥyuḍ nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar weḥwic n ujeǧid, \add umi\add* Ikaldaniyyen tuɣa quwwaren i tendint. Uca ajeǧid yuyur x webrid n Řewḍa.  
\v 8 Řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen iḍfar ajeǧid uca nitni ḥarten x Ṣidqiya di řwaṭat n Ariḥa. Marra řɛeskar nnes ttwassebḍan xas.  
\v 9 Nitni ṭṭfen ajeǧid uca iwyen t ɣar Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil, ɣar Ribla di temmurt n Ḥamat uca wanita iḥkem xas.  
\v 10 Ajeǧid n Babil inɣa iḥenjiren n Ṣidqiya zzat i ṭṭitawin nnes. Uřa d marra řḥukkam n Yahuda inɣa i-ten di Ribla.  
\v 11 Issdarɣeř tiṭṭawin n Ṣidqiya uca iqqen i-t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnḥas. \add Ammu\add* i t yiwi ujeǧid n Babil ɣar Babil uca igga i-t di řeḥbes ař ass umi immut.   
\m
\v 12 Deg uyur wiss xemsa, deg wass wiss ɛecra n uyur - tuɣa aseggʷas d aseggʷas wiss tseɛṭac n ujeǧid Nabuxadraṣṣar, ajeǧid n Babil - xmi dd-yusa Nabuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet wenni tuɣa isexxar zzat i wudem n ujeǧid n Babil, ɣar Urcalim, \f ◼ \fr 52:12 \ft \+fk isexxar\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ibedd’.\f*  
\v 13 issarɣ netta Taddart n SIDI d taddart n ujeǧid d marra tudrin n Urcalim d marra tudrin n imcennɛen issarɣ i-tent \add ɛawed\add* s tmessi.  
\v 14 Marra řɛeskar n Ikaldaniyyen, inni dd-yusin ak-d řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, aqa arẓin marra řeḥyuḍ n Urcalim i d as dd-innḍen.  
\v 15 Imezřaḍ qaɛ n řgens d min iceṭṭen n řgens nni ittwajjen di tendint d inni iffɣen ɣar ujeǧid n Babil uca dewřen ɣares uřa d min iceṭṭen n řɣaci, indeh i-ten Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, di lmenfa.  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* zeg imezřaḍ n temmurt ijja Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, ijj n drus am yimeřqaḍ n tzayart u am yifeǧaḥen.   
\m
\v 17 \add Uca\add* arẓin Ikaldaniyyen ipilaren n nnḥas di Taddart n SIDI, tikarrutin d trimant n nnḥas \add i tuɣa iǧan\add* di Taddart n SIDI uca ksin marra nnḥas akidsen ɣar Babil. \f ◼ \fr 52:17 \ft \+fk tarimant\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řebḥar’ niɣ ‘il’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 52:17 \xt Irm. 27:19\x*  
\v 18 Uřa d tiydurin d iɣenjayen d tjeqqaḍin d ṭṭawyat i urucci d tɣenjayin d marra řeqcuɛ n nnḥas i zi ttsexxaren, ksin ten.  
\v 19 Ammu i iksi řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet ṭṭbaṣa d ṭṭawyat i urucci d teydurin d řeqnadeř d tɣenjayin d řkisan, \add marra\add* min tuɣa iǧan n wureɣ qaɛ niɣ n nnuqart qaɛ.  
\v 20 \add X\add* tnayen n ipilaren d trimant d tenɛac n ifunasen n nnḥas nni tuɣa \add iǧan\add* sadu nnes uřa x tkarrutin nni igga ujeǧid i Taddart n SIDI: aqa nnḥas n marra řeqcuɛ-a war zemmaren ad weznen \add marra aya\add*.  
\v 21 \add X\add* ipilaren: tuɣa řuɛřa n ijj n upilar dayes tmenṭac n iɣaǧen uca ijj n ufiřu n \add řeɛbar\add* n tenɛac n iɣaǧen izemmar ad as inneḍ. Tuɣa řgedran nnes dayes arebɛa n iḍewḍan uca \add ɣar daxeř\add* tuɣa-t ixwa.\x ◘ \xo 52:21 \xt 1 Ij. 7:15; 2 Ij. 25:17; 2 Im. 3:15\x*  
\v 22 Ttaj sennej nnes \add tuɣa-t\add* n nnḥas. Řuɛřa n ijj n ttaj tuɣa xemsa n iɣaǧen u x ttaj \add tuɣa xas\add* tracca d tremmamin i d as dd-innḍen. Tuɣa marra n nnḥas. Am tuɣa wanita, ammu tuɣa uřa d apilar nneɣni d tremmanin nnes.  
\v 23 Tiremmanin tuɣa atent di setta u-tesɛin ɣar marra iɣezdisen n usemmiḍ. Marra tiremmanin tuɣa atent di mya x tracca i d as dd-innḍen.   
\m
\v 24 Řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet yiwi-dd akides uřa d akehhan ameqqran Saraya, akehhan wiss tnayen Ṣafanya d třata n iɛessasen n tewwart. \f ◼ \fr 52:24 \ft \+fk Ṣafanya\ft  - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni t issnuffaren SIDI’.\f*  
\v 25 Zi tendint iksi netta ijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ wenni tuɣa x iɛeskariyyen, řa d sebɛa n yeryazen nni izemmaren ad ẓaren udem n ujeǧid d yinni ittwafen di tendint, řa d amarir n ukumandar n řɛeskar nni tuɣa izemmen řgens n temmurt i umenɣi, uřa d settin n yeryazen zi řgens n temmurt nni ittwafen di řwest n tendint.  
\v 26 Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, iṭṭef i-ten uca yiwi ten ɣar ujeǧid n Babil, ɣar Ribla.  
\v 27 Ajeǧid n Babil iwta i-ten uca inɣa i-ten di Ribla, di temmurt n Ḥamat. \add Ammu i\add* ittwandeh Yahuda zi temmurt nnes ɣar lmenfa.   
\b  
\m
\v 28 Wa d řgens nni indeh Nabuxadraṣṣar di lmenfa:  
\m deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa \add indeh\add* teřt-ařaf u-třata u-ɛicrin n ayt n Yahuda.   
\m
\v 29 deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n Nabuxadraṣṣar, yiwi temnem-mya u-tnayen u-třatin n iwdan zi Urcalim.   
\m
\v 30 deg useggʷas wiss třata u-ɛicrin n Nabuxadraṣṣar indeh Nebuzaradan, řqebṭan n iɛessasen n arrimet, sebɛa-mya u-xemsa u-rebɛin n ayt n Yahuda ɣar lmenfa.  
\m Marra \add jmiɛ\add* tuɣa aten di arebɛa-ařaf u-setta-mya n iwdan. \f ◼ \fr 52:30 \ft \+fk iwdan\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmur’.\f*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Ajeǧid Yahuyakin ittaf řxaḍar di tiṭṭawin n ujeǧid n Babil  
\m
\v 31 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-třatin n tmeḥbast n Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda, deg uyur wiss tenɛac, deg wass wiss xemsa u-ɛicrin n uyur, issgeɛɛed Awil-Marudax, ajeǧid n Babil, deg useggʷas amezwaru n tgelda nnes, azeǧif n Yahuyakin, ajeǧid n Yahuda, uca issuffeɣ i-t-i-dd zi řeḥbes. \x ◘ \xo 52:31 \xt 2 Ij. 25:27-30\x*  
\v 32 Netta iɛdeř akides, iwca as řkursi nnes tiwa i řekrasi n ijeǧiden nneɣni inni tuɣa ɣares di Babil.  
\v 33 Issars Yahuyakin arruḍ nnes n řeḥbes uca idweř ittett ɣares, min ikka iddar.  
\v 34 X řmeɛteq nnes: řebda immewc as řmeɛteq nnes s ufus n ujeǧid n Babil, kuř ass min dd-ikkaren n wass nni ař ass n řmewt nnes, min ikka iddar. \f ◼ \fr 52:34 \ft \+fk min ikka iddar\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘marra ussan n tudart nnes’.\f*   